            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">for Jessica, who loves stories, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">for Anne, who loved them too, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">and for Di, who heard this one first. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\"> </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\"> </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER ONE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Boy Who Lived </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr and Mrs Dursley, of number four, Privet Drive, were proud to say that they were perfectly normal, thank you very much. They were the last people you’d expect to be involved in anything strange or mysterious, because they just didn’t hold with such nonsense. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Dursley was the director of a firm called Grunnings, which made drills. He was a big, beefy man with hardly any neck, although he did have a very large moustache. Mrs Dursley was thin and blonde and had nearly twice the usual amount of neck, which came in very useful as she spent so much of her time craning over garden fences, spying on the neighbours. The Dursleys had a small son called Dudley and in their opinion there was no finer boy anywhere. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dursleys had everything they wanted, but they also had a secret, and their greatest fear was that somebody would discover it. They didn’t think they could bear it if anyone found out about the Potters. Mrs Potter was Mrs Dursley’s sister, but they hadn’t met for several years; in fact, Mrs Dursley pretended she didn’t have a sister, because her sister and her good-for-nothing husband were as unDursleyish as it was possible to be. The Dursleys shuddered to think what the neighbours would say if the Potters arrived in the street. The Dursleys knew that the Potters had a small son, too, but they had never even seen him. This boy was another good reason for keeping the Potters away; they didn’t want Dudley mixing with a child like that. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Mr and Mrs Dursley woke up on the dull, grey Tuesday our story starts, there was nothing about the cloudy sky outside to suggest that strange and mysterious things would soon be happening all over the country. Mr Dursley hummed as he picked out his most boring tie for work and Mrs Dursley gossiped away </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>8 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">happily as she wrestled a screaming Dudley into his high chair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">None of them noticed a large tawny owl flutter past the window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At half past eight, Mr Dursley picked up his briefcase, pecked Mrs Dursley on the cheek and tried to kiss Dudley goodbye but missed, because Dudley was now having a tantrum and throwing his cereal at the walls. ‘Little tyke,’ chortled Mr Dursley as he left the house. He got into his car and backed out of number four’s drive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was on the corner of the street that he noticed the first sign of something peculiar – a cat reading a map. For a second, Mr Dursley didn’t realise what he had seen – then he jerked his head around to look again. There was a tabby cat standing on the corner of Privet Drive, but there wasn’t a map in sight. What could he have been thinking of? It must have been a trick of the light. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Dursley blinked and stared at the cat. It stared back. As Mr Dursley drove around the corner and up the road, he watched the cat in his mirror. It was now reading the sign that said  <i class=\"calibre3\">Privet Drive</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– no,  <i class=\"calibre3\">looking</i> at the sign; cats couldn’t read maps  <i class=\"calibre3\">or</i> signs. Mr Dursley gave himself a little shake and put the cat out of his mind. As he drove towards town he thought of nothing except a large order of drills he was hoping to get that day. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But on the edge of town, drills were driven out of his mind by something else. As he sat in the usual morning traffic jam, he couldn’t help noticing that there seemed to be a lot of strangely dressed people about. People in cloaks. Mr Dursley couldn’t bear people who dressed in funny clothes – the get-ups you saw on young people! He supposed this was some stupid new fashion. He drummed his fingers on the steering wheel and his eyes fell on a huddle of these weirdos standing quite close by. They were whispering excitedly together. Mr Dursley was enraged to see that a couple of them weren’t young at all; why, that man had to be older than he was, and wearing an emerald-green cloak! The nerve of him! But then it struck Mr Dursley that this was probably some silly stunt – these people were obviously collecting for something </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… yes, that would be it. The traffic moved on, and a few minutes later, Mr Dursley arrived in the Grunnings car park, his mind back on drills. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Dursley always sat with his back to the window in his office on the ninth floor. If he hadn’t, he might have found it harder to concentrate on drills that morning.  <i class=\"calibre3\">He</i> didn’t see the owls </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boy Who Lived 9 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">swooping past in broad daylight, though people down in the street did; they pointed and gazed open-mouthed as owl after owl sped overhead. Most of them had never seen an owl even at night-time. Mr Dursley, however, had a perfectly normal, owl-free morning. He yelled at five different people. He made several important telephone calls and shouted a bit more. He was in a very good mood until lunch-time, when he thought he’d stretch his legs and walk across the road to buy himself a bun from the baker’s opposite. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He’d forgotten all about the people in cloaks until he passed a group  of  them  next  to  the  baker’s.  He  eyed  them  angrily  as  he passed. He didn’t know why, but they made him uneasy. This lot were whispering excitedly, too, and he couldn’t see a single collecting tin. It was on his way back past them, clutching a large doughnut in a bag, that he caught a few words of what they were saying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Potters, that’s right, that’s what I heard –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– yes, their son, Harry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Dursley stopped dead. Fear flooded him. He looked back at the whisperers as if he wanted to say something to them, but thought better of it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He dashed back across the road, hurried up to his office, snapped at his secretary not to disturb him, seized his telephone and had almost finished dialling his home number when he changed his mind. He put the receiver back down and stroked his moustache, thinking … no, he was being stupid. Potter wasn’t such an unusual name. He was sure there were lots of people called Potter who had a son called Harry. Come to think of it, he wasn’t even sure his nephew  <i class=\"calibre3\">was</i> called Harry. He’d never even seen the boy. It might have been Harvey. Or Harold. There was no point in worrying Mrs Dursley, she always got so upset at any mention of her sister. He didn’t blame her – if  <i class=\"calibre3\">he’d</i> had a sister like that … but all the same, those people in cloaks … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He found it a lot harder to concentrate on drills that afternoon, and when he left the building at five o’clock, he was still so worried that he walked straight into someone just outside the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry,’ he grunted, as the tiny old man stumbled and almost fell. It was a few seconds before Mr Dursley realised that the man was wearing a violet cloak. He didn’t seem at all upset at being almost knocked to the ground. On the contrary, his face split into </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>10 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">a wide smile and he said in a squeaky voice that made passers-by stare: ‘Don’t be sorry, my dear sir, for nothing could upset me today! Rejoice, for You-Know-Who has gone at last! Even Muggles like yourself should be celebrating, this happy, happy day!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And the old man hugged Mr Dursley around the middle and walked off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Dursley stood rooted to the spot. He had been hugged by a complete stranger. He also thought he had been called a Muggle, whatever that was. He was rattled. He hurried to his car and set off home, hoping he was imagining things, which he had never hoped before, because he didn’t approve of imagination. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As he pulled into the driveway of number four, the first thing he saw – and it didn’t improve his mood – was the tabby cat he’d spotted that morning. It was now sitting on his garden wall. He was sure it was the same one; it had the same markings around its eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shoo!’ said Mr Dursley loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The cat didn’t move. It just gave him a stern look. Was this normal cat behaviour, Mr Dursley wondered. Trying to pull himself together, he let himself into the house. He was still determined not to mention anything to his wife. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Dursley had had a nice, normal day. She told him over dinner all about Mrs Next Door’s problems with her daughter and how Dudley had learnt a new word (‘Shan’t!’). Mr Dursley tried to act normally. When Dudley had been put to bed, he went into the living-room in time to catch the last report on the evening news: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And finally, bird-watchers everywhere have reported that the nation’s owls have been behaving very unusually today. Although owls normally hunt at night and are hardly ever seen in daylight, there have been hundreds of sightings of these birds flying in every direction since sunrise. Experts are unable to explain why the owls have suddenly changed their sleeping pattern.’ The news reader allowed himself a grin. ‘Most mysterious. And now, over to Jim McGuffin with the weather. Going to be any more showers of owls tonight, Jim?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, Ted,’ said the weatherman, ‘I don’t know about that, but it’s not only the owls that have been acting oddly today. Viewers as far apart as Kent, Yorkshire and Dundee have been phoning in to tell me that instead of the rain I promised yesterday, they’ve had a downpour of shooting stars! Perhaps people have been </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boy Who Lived 11 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">celebrating Bonfire Night early – it’s not until next week, folks! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But I can promise a wet night tonight.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Dursley sat frozen in his armchair. Shooting stars all over Britain? Owls flying by daylight? Mysterious people in cloaks all over the place? And a whisper, a whisper about the Potters … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Dursley came into the living-room carrying two cups of tea. It was no good. He’d have to say something to her. He cleared his throat nervously. ‘Er – Petunia, dear – you haven’t heard from your sister lately, have you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As he had expected, Mrs Dursley looked shocked and angry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After all, they normally pretended she didn’t have a sister. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ she said sharply. ‘Why?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Funny stuff on the news,’ Mr Dursley mumbled. ‘Owls … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">shooting stars … and there were a lot of funny-looking people in town today …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">So? </i>’ snapped Mrs Dursley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I just thought … maybe … it was something to do with … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you know …  <i class=\"calibre3\">her lot. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Dursley sipped her tea through pursed lips. Mr Dursley wondered whether he dared tell her he’d heard the name ‘Potter’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He decided he didn’t dare. Instead he said, as casually as he could, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Their son – he’d be about Dudley’s age now, wouldn’t he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I suppose so,’ said Mrs Dursley stiffly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s his name again? Howard, isn’t it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry. Nasty, common name, if you ask me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yes,’ said Mr Dursley, his heart sinking horribly. ‘Yes, I quite agree.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He didn’t say another word on the subject as they went upstairs to bed. While Mrs Dursley was in the bathroom, Mr Dursley crept to the bedroom window and peered down into the front garden. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The cat was still there. It was staring down Privet Drive as though it was waiting for something. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Was he imagining things? Could all this have anything to do with the Potters? If it did … if it got out that they were related to a pair of – well, he didn’t think he could bear it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dursleys got into bed. Mrs Dursley fell asleep quickly but Mr Dursley lay awake, turning it all over in his mind. His last, comforting thought before he fell asleep was that even if the Potters  <i class=\"calibre3\">were</i> involved, there was no reason for them to come near him and Mrs Dursley. The Potters knew very well what he and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>12 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Petunia thought about them and their kind … He couldn’t see how he and Petunia could get mixed up in anything that might be going on. He yawned and turned over. It couldn’t affect  <i class=\"calibre3\">them …</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">How very wrong he was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Dursley might have been drifting into an uneasy sleep, but the cat on the wall outside was showing no sign of sleepiness. It was sitting as still as a statue, its eyes fixed unblinkingly on the far corner of Privet Drive. It didn’t so much as quiver when a car door slammed in the next street, nor when two owls swooped overhead. In fact, it was nearly midnight before the cat moved at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A man appeared on the corner the cat had been watching, appeared so suddenly and silently you’d have thought he’d just popped out of the ground. The cat’s tail twitched and its eyes narrowed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nothing like this man had ever been seen in Privet Drive. He was tall, thin and very old, judging by the silver of his hair and beard, which were both long enough to tuck into his belt. He was wearing long robes, a purple cloak which swept the ground and high-heeled, buckled boots. His blue eyes were light, bright and sparkling behind half-moon spectacles and his nose was very long and crooked, as though it had been broken at least twice. This man’s name was Albus Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Albus Dumbledore didn’t seem to realise that he had just arrived in a street where everything from his name to his boots was unwelcome. He was busy rummaging in his cloak, looking for something. But he did seem to realise he was being watched, because he looked up suddenly at the cat, which was still staring at him from the other end of the street. For some reason, the sight of the cat seemed to amuse him. He chuckled and muttered, ‘I should have known.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had found what he was looking for in his inside pocket. It seemed to be a silver cigarette lighter. He flicked it open, held it up in the air and clicked it. The nearest street lamp went out with a little pop. He clicked it again – the next lamp flickered into darkness. Twelve times he clicked the Put-Outer, until the only lights left in the whole street were two tiny pinpricks in the distance, which were the eyes of the cat watching him. If anyone looked out of their window now, even beady-eyed Mrs Dursley, they wouldn’t be able to see anything that was happening down on the pavement. Dumbledore slipped the Put-Outer back inside </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boy Who Lived 13 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">his cloak and set off down the street towards number four, where he sat down on the wall next to the cat. He didn’t look at it, but after a moment he spoke to it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fancy seeing you here, Professor McGonagall.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned to smile at the tabby, but it had gone. Instead he was smiling at a rather severe-looking woman who was wearing square glasses exactly the shape of the markings the cat had had around its eyes. She, too, was wearing a cloak, an emerald one. Her black hair was drawn into a tight bun. She looked distinctly ruffled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did you know it was me?’ she asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear Professor, I’ve never seen a cat sit so stiffly.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d be stiff if you’d been sitting on a brick wall all day,’ said Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All day? When you could have been celebrating? I must have passed a dozen feasts and parties on my way here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall sniffed angrily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh yes, everyone’s celebrating, all right,’ she said impatiently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d think they’d be a bit more careful, but no – even the Muggles have noticed something’s going on. It was on their news.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She jerked her head back at the Dursleys’ dark living-room window. ‘I heard it. Flocks of owls … shooting stars … Well, they’re not completely stupid. They were bound to notice something. Shooting stars down in Kent – I’ll bet that was Dedalus Diggle. He never had much sense.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can’t blame them,’ said Dumbledore gently. ‘We’ve had precious little to celebrate for eleven years.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know that,’ said Professor McGonagall irritably. ‘But that’s no reason to lose our heads. People are being downright careless, out on the streets in broad daylight, not even dressed in Muggle clothes, swapping rumours.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She threw a sharp, sideways glance at Dumbledore here, as though hoping he was going to tell her something, but he didn’t, so she went on: ‘A fine thing it would be if, on the very day You-Know-Who seems to have disappeared at last, the Muggles found out about us all. I suppose he really  <i class=\"calibre3\">has</i> gone, Dumbledore?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It certainly seems so,’ said Dumbledore. ‘We have much to be thankful for. Would you care for a sherbet lemon?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A  <i class=\"calibre3\">what? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A sherbet lemon. They’re a kind of Muggle sweet I’m rather fond of.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>14 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, thank you,’ said Professor McGonagall coldly, as though she didn’t think this was the moment for sherbet lemons. ‘As I say, even if You-Know-Who  <i class=\"calibre3\">has</i> gone –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear Professor, surely a sensible person like yourself can call him by his name? All this “You-Know-Who” nonsense – for eleven years I have been trying to persuade people to call him by his proper name:  <i class=\"calibre3\">Voldemort. </i>’ Professor McGonagall flinched, but Dumbledore, who was unsticking two sherbet lemons, seemed not to notice. ‘It all gets so confusing if we keep saying “You-Know-Who”.’ I have never seen any reason to be frightened of saying Voldemort’s name.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know you haven’t,’ said Professor McGonagall, sounding half-exasperated, half-admiring. ‘But you’re different. Everyone knows you’re the only one You-Know – oh, all right,  <i class=\"calibre3\">Voldemort</i> – was frightened of.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You flatter me,’ said Dumbledore calmly. ‘Voldemort had powers I will never have.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Only because you’re too – well –  <i class=\"calibre3\">noble</i> to use them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s lucky it’s dark. I haven’t blushed so much since Madam Pomfrey told me she liked my new earmuffs.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall shot a sharp look at Dumbledore and said, ‘The owls are nothing to the  <i class=\"calibre3\">rumours</i> that are flying around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You know what everyone’s saying? About why he’s disappeared? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">About what finally stopped him?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It seemed that Professor McGonagall had reached the point she was most anxious to discuss, the real reason she had been waiting on a cold hard wall all day, for neither as a cat nor as a woman had she fixed Dumbledore with such a piercing stare as she did now. It was plain that whatever ‘everyone’ was saying, she was not going to believe it until Dumbledore told her it was true. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore, however, was choosing another sherbet lemon and did not answer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What they’re  <i class=\"calibre3\">saying</i>,’ she pressed on, ‘is that last night Voldemort turned  up  in  Godric’s  Hollow.  He  went  to  find  the  Potters.  The rumour is that Lily and James Potter are – are – that they’re – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">dead. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore bowed his head. Professor McGonagall gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lily and James … I can’t believe it … I didn’t want to believe it </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… Oh, Albus …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore reached out and patted her on the shoulder. ‘I </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boy Who Lived 15 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">know … I know …’ he said heavily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall’s voice trembled as she went on. ‘That’s not all. They’re saying he tried to kill the Potters’ son, Harry. But – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he couldn’t. He couldn’t kill that little boy. No one knows why, or how, but they’re saying that when he couldn’t kill Harry Potter, Voldemort’s power somehow broke – and that’s why he’s gone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore nodded glumly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s – it’s  <i class=\"calibre3\">true? </i>’ faltered Professor McGonagall. ‘After all he’s done … all the people he’s killed … he couldn’t kill a little boy? It’s just astounding … of all the things to stop him … but how in the name of heaven did Harry survive?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can only guess,’ said Dumbledore. ‘We may never know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall pulled out a lace handkerchief and dabbed at her eyes beneath her spectacles. Dumbledore gave a great sniff as he took a golden watch from his pocket and examined it. It was a very odd watch. It had twelve hands but no numbers; instead, little planets were moving around the edge. It must have made sense to Dumbledore, though, because he put it back in his pocket and said, ‘Hagrid’s late. I suppose it was he who told you I’d be here, by the way?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘And I don’t suppose you’re going to tell me  <i class=\"calibre3\">why</i> you’re here, of all places?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve come to bring Harry to his aunt and uncle. They’re the only family he has left now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t mean – you  <i class=\"calibre3\">can’t</i> mean the people who live  <i class=\"calibre3\">here? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">cried Professor McGonagall, jumping to her feet and pointing at number four. ‘Dumbledore – you can’t. I’ve been watching them all day. You couldn’t find two people who are less like us. And they’ve got this son – I saw him kicking his mother all the way up the street, screaming for sweets. Harry Potter come and live here!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s the best place for him,’ said Dumbledore firmly. ‘His aunt and uncle will be able to explain everything to him when he’s older. I’ve written them a letter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A letter?’ repeated Professor McGonagall faintly, sitting back down on the wall. ‘Really, Dumbledore, you think you can explain all this in a letter? These people will never understand him! He’ll be famous – a legend – I wouldn’t be surprised if today was known as Harry Potter Day in future – there will be books written about Harry – every child in our world will know his name!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Exactly,’ said Dumbledore, looking very seriously over the top </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>16 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">of his half-moon glasses. ‘It would be enough to turn any boy’s head. Famous before he can walk and talk! Famous for something he won’t even remember! Can’t you see how much better off he’ll be, growing up away from all that until he’s ready to take it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall opened her mouth, changed her mind, swallowed and then said, ‘Yes – yes, you’re right, of course. But how is the boy getting here, Dumbledore?’ She eyed his cloak suddenly as though she thought he might be hiding Harry underneath it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid’s bringing him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You think it –  <i class=\"calibre3\">wise</i> – to trust Hagrid with something as important as this?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I would trust Hagrid with my life,’ said Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not saying his heart isn’t in the right place,’ said Professor McGonagall grudgingly, ‘but you can’t pretend he’s not careless. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He does tend to – what was that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A low rumbling sound had broken the silence around them. It grew steadily louder as they looked up and down the street for some sign of a headlight; it swelled to a roar as they both looked up at the sky – and a huge motorbike fell out of the air and landed on the road in front of them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">If the motorbike was huge, it was nothing to the man sitting astride it. He was almost twice as tall as a normal man and at least five times as wide. He looked simply too big to be allowed, and so <i class=\"calibre3\">wild</i> – long tangles of bushy black hair and beard hid most of his face, he had hands the size of dustbin lids and his feet in their leather boots were like baby dolphins. In his vast, muscular arms he was holding a bundle of blankets. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid,’ said Dumbledore, sounding relieved. ‘At last. And where did you get that motorbike?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Borrowed it, Professor Dumbledore, sir,’ said the giant, climbing carefully off the motorbike as he spoke. ‘Young Sirius Black lent it me. I’ve got him, sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No problems, were there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, sir – house was almost destroyed but I got him out all right before the Muggles started swarmin’ around. He fell asleep as we was flyin’ over Bristol.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore and Professor McGonagall bent forward over the bundle of blankets. Inside, just visible, was a baby boy, fast asleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Under a tuft of jet-black hair over his forehead they could see a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boy Who Lived 17 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">curiously shaped cut, like a bolt of lightning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is that where –?’ whispered Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Dumbledore. ‘He’ll have that scar for ever.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Couldn’t you do something about it, Dumbledore?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Even if I could, I wouldn’t. Scars can come in useful. I have one myself above my left knee which is a perfect map of the London Underground. Well – give him here, Hagrid – we’d better get this over with.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore took Harry in his arms and turned towards the Dursleys’ house. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Could I – could I say goodbye to him, sir?’ asked Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He bent his great, shaggy head over Harry and gave him what must have been a very scratchy, whiskery kiss. Then, suddenly, Hagrid let out a howl like a wounded dog. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shhh!’ hissed Professor McGonagall. ‘You’ll wake the Muggles!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘S-s-sorry,’ sobbed Hagrid, taking out a large spotted handkerchief and burying his face in it. ‘But I c-c-can’t stand it – Lily an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">James dead – an’ poor little Harry off ter live with Muggles –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, yes, it’s all very sad, but get a grip on yourself, Hagrid, or we’ll be found,’ Professor McGonagall whispered, patting Hagrid gingerly on the arm as Dumbledore stepped over the low garden wall and walked to the front door. He laid Harry gently on the doorstep, took a letter out of his cloak, tucked it inside Harry’s blankets and then came back to the other two. For a full minute the three of them stood and looked at the little bundle; Hagrid’s shoulders shook, Professor McGonagall blinked furiously and the twinkling light that usually shone from Dumbledore’s eyes seemed to have gone out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Dumbledore finally, ‘that’s that. We’ve no business staying here. We may as well go and join the celebrations.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Hagrid in a very muffled voice. ‘I’d best get this bike away. G’night, Professor McGonagall – Professor Dumbledore, sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wiping his streaming eyes on his jacket sleeve, Hagrid swung himself on to the motorbike and kicked the engine into life; with a roar it rose into the air and off into the night. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I shall see you soon, I expect, Professor McGonagall,’ said Dumbledore, nodding to her. Professor McGonagall blew her nose in reply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore turned and walked back down the street. On the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>18 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">corner he stopped and took out the silver Put-Outer. He clicked it once and twelve balls of light sped back to their street lamps so that Privet Drive glowed suddenly orange and he could make out a tabby cat slinking around the corner at the other end of the street. He could just see the bundle of blankets on the step of number four. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good luck, Harry,’ he murmured. He turned on his heel and with a swish of his cloak he was gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A breeze ruffled the neat hedges of Privet Drive, which lay silent and tidy under the inky sky, the very last place you would expect astonishing things to happen. Harry Potter rolled over inside his blankets without waking up. One small hand closed on the letter beside him and he slept on, not knowing he was special, not knowing he was famous, not knowing he would be woken in a few hours’ time by Mrs Dursley’s scream as she opened the front door to put out the milk bottles, nor that he would spend the next few weeks being prodded and pinched by his cousin Dudley … He couldn’t know that at this very moment, people meeting in secret all over the country were holding up their glasses and saying in hushed voices: ‘To Harry Potter – the boy who lived!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER TWO — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Vanishing Glass </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nearly ten years had passed since the Dursleys had woken up to find their nephew on the front step, but Privet Drive had hardly changed at all. The sun rose on the same tidy front gardens and lit up the brass number four on the Dursleys’ front door; it crept into their living-room, which was almost exactly the same as it had been on the night when Mr Dursley had seen that fateful news report about the owls. Only the photographs on the mantelpiece really showed how much time had passed. Ten years ago, there had been lots of pictures of what looked like a large pink beach ball wearing different-coloured bobble hats – but Dudley Dursley was no longer a baby, and now the photographs showed a large, blond boy riding his first bicycle, on a roundabout at the fair, playing a computer game with his father, being hugged and kissed by his mother. The room held no sign at all that another boy lived in the house, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Yet Harry Potter was still there, asleep at the moment, but not for long. His Aunt Petunia was awake and it was her shrill voice which made the first noise of the day. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Up! Get up! Now!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry woke with a start. His aunt rapped on the door again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Up!’ she screeched. Harry heard her walking towards the kitchen and then the sound of the frying pan being put on the cooker. He rolled on to his back and tried to remember the dream he had been having. It had been a good one. There had been a flying motorbike in it. He had a funny feeling he’d had the same dream before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His aunt was back outside the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you up yet?’ she demanded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nearly,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, get a move on, I want you to look after the bacon. And </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>20 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">don’t you dare let it burn, I want everything perfect on Duddy’s birthday.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry groaned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What did you say?’ his aunt snapped through the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing, nothing …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley’s birthday – how could he have forgotten? Harry got slowly out of bed and started looking for socks. He found a pair under his bed and, after pulling a spider off one of them, put them on. Harry was used to spiders, because the cupboard under the stairs was full of them, and that was where he slept. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When he was dressed he went down the hall into the kitchen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The table was almost hidden beneath all Dudley’s birthday presents. It looked as though Dudley had got the new computer he wanted, not to mention the second television and the racing bike. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Exactly why Dudley wanted a racing bike was a mystery to Harry, as Dudley was very fat and hated exercise – unless of course it involved punching somebody. Dudley’s favourite punch-bag was Harry, but he couldn’t often catch him. Harry didn’t look it, but he was very fast. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps it had something to do with living in a dark cupboard, but Harry had always been small and skinny for his age. He looked even smaller and skinnier than he really was because all he had to wear were old clothes of Dudley’s and Dudley was about four times bigger than he was. Harry had a thin face, knobbly knees, black hair and bright-green eyes. He wore round glasses held together with a lot of Sellotape because of all the times Dudley had punched him on the nose. The only thing Harry liked about his own appearance was a very thin scar on his forehead which was shaped like a bolt of lightning. He had had it as long as he could remember and the first question he could ever remember asking his Aunt Petunia was how he had got it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In the car crash when your parents died,’ she had said. ‘And don’t ask questions.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Don’t ask questions</i> – that was the first rule for a quiet life with the Dursleys. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon entered the kitchen as Harry was turning over the bacon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Comb your hair!’ he barked, by way of a morning greeting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">About once a week, Uncle Vernon looked over the top of his newspaper and shouted that Harry needed a haircut. Harry must </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Vanishing Glass 21 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">have had more haircuts than the rest of the boys in his class put together, but it made no difference, his hair simply grew that way </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– all over the place. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was frying eggs by the time Dudley arrived in the kitchen with his mother. Dudley looked a lot like Uncle Vernon. He had a large, pink face, not much neck, small, watery blue eyes and thick, blond hair that lay smoothly on his thick, fat head. Aunt Petunia often said that Dudley looked like a baby angel – Harry often said that Dudley looked like a pig in a wig. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry put the plates of egg and bacon on the table, which was difficult as there wasn’t much room. Dudley, meanwhile, was counting his presents. His face fell. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thirty-six,’ he said, looking up at his mother and father. ‘That’s two less than last year.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Darling, you haven’t counted Auntie Marge’s present, see, it’s here under this big one from Mummy and Daddy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, thirty-seven then,’ said Dudley, going red in the face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who could see a huge Dudley tantrum coming on, began wolfing down his bacon as fast as possible in case Dudley turned the table over. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Petunia obviously scented danger too, because she said quickly, ‘And we’ll buy you another  <i class=\"calibre3\">two</i> presents while we’re out today. How’s that, popkin?  <i class=\"calibre3\">Two</i> more presents. Is that all right?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley thought for a moment. It looked like hard work. Finally he said slowly, ‘So I’ll have thirty … thirty …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thirty-nine, sweetums,’ said Aunt Petunia. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh.’ Dudley sat down heavily and grabbed the nearest parcel. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right then.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon chuckled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Little tyke wants his money’s worth, just like his father. Atta boy, Dudley!’ He ruffled Dudley’s hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment the telephone rang and Aunt Petunia went to answer it while Harry and Uncle Vernon watched Dudley unwrap the racing bike, a cine-camera, a remote-control aeroplane, sixteen new computer games and a video recorder. He was ripping the paper off a gold wristwatch when Aunt Petunia came back from the telephone, looking both angry and worried. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bad news, Vernon,’ she said. ‘Mrs Figg’s broken her leg. She can’t take him.’ She jerked her head in Harry’s direction. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley’s mouth fell open in horror but Harry’s heart gave a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>22 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">leap. Every year on Dudley’s birthday his parents took him and a friend out for the day, to adventure parks, hamburger bars or the cinema. Every year, Harry was left behind with Mrs Figg, a mad old lady who lived two streets away. Harry hated it there. The whole house smelled of cabbage and Mrs Figg made him look at photographs of all the cats she’d ever owned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now what?’ said Aunt Petunia, looking furiously at Harry as though he’d planned this. Harry knew he ought to feel sorry that Mrs Figg had broken her leg, but it wasn’t easy when he reminded himself it would be a whole year before he had to look at Tibbles, Snowy, Mr Paws and Tufty again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We could phone Marge,’ Uncle Vernon suggested. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be silly, Vernon, she hates the boy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dursleys often spoke about Harry like this, as though he wasn’t there – or rather, as though he was something very nasty that couldn’t understand them, like a slug. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about what’s-her-name, your friend – Yvonne?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘On holiday in Majorca,’ snapped Aunt Petunia. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You could just leave me here,’ Harry put in hopefully (he’d be able to watch what he wanted on television for a change and maybe even have a go on Dudley’s computer). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Petunia looked as though she’d just swallowed a lemon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And come back and find the house in ruins?’ she snarled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I won’t blow up the house,’ said Harry, but they weren’t listening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I suppose we could take him to the zoo,’ said Aunt Petunia slowly, ‘… and leave him in the car …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That car’s new, he’s not sitting in it alone …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley began to cry loudly. In fact, he wasn’t really crying, it had been years since he’d really cried, but he knew that if he screwed up his face and wailed, his mother would give him anything he wanted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dinky Duddydums, don’t cry, Mummy won’t let him spoil your special day!’ she cried, flinging her arms around him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I … don’t … want … him … t-t-to come!’ Dudley yelled between huge pretend sobs. ‘He always sp-spoils everything!’ He shot Harry a nasty grin through the gap in his mother’s arms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Just then, the doorbell rang – ‘Oh, Good Lord, they’re here!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Aunt Petunia frantically – and a moment later, Dudley’s best friend, Piers Polkiss, walked in with his mother. Piers was a scrawny boy with a face like a rat. He was usually the one who </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Vanishing Glass 23 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">held people’s arms behind their backs while Dudley hit them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley stopped pretending to cry at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Half an hour later, Harry, who couldn’t believe his luck, was sitting in the back of the Dursleys’ car with Piers and Dudley, on the way to the zoo for the first time in his life. His aunt and uncle hadn’t  been  able  to  think  of  anything  else  to  do  with  him,  but before they’d left, Uncle Vernon had taken Harry aside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m warning you,’ he had said, putting his large purple face right up close to Harry’s, ‘I’m warning you now, boy – any funny business, anything at all – and you’ll be in that cupboard from now until Christmas.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not going to do anything,’ said Harry, ‘honestly …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Uncle Vernon didn’t believe him. No one ever did. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The problem was, strange things often happened around Harry and it was just no good telling the Dursleys he didn’t make them happen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Once, Aunt Petunia, tired of Harry coming back from the bar-ber’s looking as though he hadn’t been at all, had taken a pair of kitchen scissors and cut his hair so short he was almost bald except for his fringe, which she left ‘to hide that horrible scar’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley had laughed himself silly at Harry, who spent a sleepless night imagining school the next day, where he was already laughed at for his baggy clothes and Sellotaped glasses. Next morning, however, he had got up to find his hair exactly as it had been before Aunt Petunia had sheared it off. He had been given a week in his cupboard for this, even though he had tried to explain that he  <i class=\"calibre3\">couldn’t</i> explain how it had grown back so quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Another time, Aunt Petunia had been trying to force him into a revolting old jumper of Dudley’s (brown with orange bobbles). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The harder she tried to pull it over his head, the smaller it seemed to become, until finally it might have fitted a glove puppet, but certainly wouldn’t fit Harry. Aunt Petunia had decided it must have  shrunk  in  the  wash  and,  to  his  great  relief,  Harry  wasn’t punished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On the other hand, he’d got into terrible trouble for being found on the roof of the school kitchens. Dudley’s gang had been chasing him as usual when, as much to Harry’s surprise as anyone else’s, there he was sitting on the chimney. The Dursleys had received a very angry letter from Harry’s headmistress telling them Harry had been climbing school buildings. But all he’d tried to do </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>24 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">(as he shouted at Uncle Vernon through the locked door of his cupboard) was jump behind the big bins outside the kitchen doors. Harry supposed that the wind must have caught him in mid-jump. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But today, nothing was going to go wrong. It was even worth being with Dudley and Piers to be spending the day somewhere that wasn’t school, his cupboard or Mrs Figg’s cabbage-smelling living-room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">While he drove, Uncle Vernon complained to Aunt Petunia. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He liked to complain about things: people at work, Harry, the council, Harry, the bank and Harry were just a few of his favourite subjects. This morning, it was motorbikes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ … roaring along like maniacs, the young hoodlums,’ he said, as a motorbike overtook them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I had a dream about a motorbike,’ said Harry, remembering suddenly. ‘It was flying.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon nearly crashed into the car in front. He turned right around in his seat and yelled at Harry, his face like a gigantic beetroot with a moustache, ‘MOTORBIKES DON’T FLY!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley and Piers sniggered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know they don’t,’ said Harry. ‘It was only a dream.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he wished he hadn’t said anything. If there was one thing the Dursleys hated even more than his asking questions, it was his talking about anything acting in a way it shouldn’t, no matter if it was in a dream or even a cartoon – they seemed to think he might get dangerous ideas. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a very sunny Saturday and the zoo was crowded with families. The Dursleys bought Dudley and Piers large chocolate ice-creams at the entrance and then, because the smiling lady in the van had asked Harry what he wanted before they could hurry him away, they bought him a cheap lemon ice lolly. It wasn’t bad either, Harry thought, licking it as they watched a gorilla scratching its head and looking remarkably like Dudley, except that it wasn’t blond. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had the best morning he’d had in a long time. He was careful to walk a little way apart from the Dursleys so that Dudley and Piers, who were starting to get bored with the animals by lunch-time, wouldn’t fall back on their favourite hobby of hitting him. They ate in the zoo restaurant and when Dudley had a tantrum because his knickerbocker glory wasn’t big enough, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Vanishing Glass 25 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon bought him another one and Harry was allowed to finish the first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt, afterwards, that he should have known it was all too good to last. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After lunch they went to the reptile house. It was cool and dark in here, with lit windows all along the walls. Behind the glass, all sorts of lizards and snakes were crawling and slithering over bits of wood and stone. Dudley and Piers wanted to see huge, poison-ous cobras and thick, man-crushing pythons. Dudley quickly found the largest snake in the place. It could have wrapped its body twice around Uncle Vernon’s car and crushed it into a dustbin – but at the moment it didn’t look in the mood. In fact, it was fast asleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley stood with his nose pressed against the glass, staring at the glistening brown coils. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Make it move,’ he whined at his father. Uncle Vernon tapped on the glass, but the snake didn’t budge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do it again,’ Dudley ordered. Uncle Vernon rapped the glass smartly with his knuckles, but the snake just snoozed on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is boring,’ Dudley moaned. He shuffled away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry moved in front of the tank and looked intently at the snake. He wouldn’t have been surprised if it had died of boredom itself – no company except stupid people drumming their fingers on the glass trying to disturb it all day long. It was worse than having a cupboard as a bedroom, where the only visitor was Aunt Petunia hammering on the door to wake you up – at least he got to visit the rest of the house. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The snake suddenly opened its beady eyes. Slowly, very slowly, it raised its head until its eyes were on a level with Harry’s. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">It winked. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared. Then he looked quickly around to see if anyone was watching. They weren’t. He looked back at the snake and winked, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The snake jerked its head towards Uncle Vernon and Dudley, then raised its eyes to the ceiling. It gave Harry a look that said quite plainly: ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">I get that all the time. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know,’ Harry murmured through the glass, though he wasn’t sure the snake could hear him. ‘It must be really annoying.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The snake nodded vigorously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where do you come from, anyway?’ Harry asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>26 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The snake jabbed its tail at a little sign next to the glass. Harry peered at it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Boa Constrictor</i>,  <i class=\"calibre3\"> Brazil. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Was it nice there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The boa constrictor jabbed its tail at the sign again and Harry read on:  <i class=\"calibre3\">This specimen was bred in the zoo. </i> ‘Oh, I see – so you’ve never been to Brazil?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the snake shook its head, a deafening shout behind Harry made both of them jump. ‘DUDLEY! MR DURSLEY! COME AND </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">LOOK AT THIS SNAKE! YOU WON’T  <i class=\"calibre3\">BELIEVE</i> WHAT IT’S </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">DOING!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley came waddling towards them as fast as he could. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Out of the way, you,’ he said, punching Harry in the ribs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Caught by surprise, Harry fell hard on the concrete floor. What came next happened so fast no one saw how it happened – one second, Piers and Dudley were leaning right up close to the glass, the next, they had leapt back with howls of horror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat up and gasped; the glass front of the boa constrictor’s tank had vanished. The great snake was uncoiling itself rapidly, slithering out on to the floor – people throughout the reptile house screamed and started running for the exits. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the snake slid swiftly past him, Harry could have sworn a low, hissing voice said, ‘Brazil, here I come … Thanksss, amigo.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The keeper of the reptile house was in shock. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But the glass,’ he kept saying, ‘where did the glass go?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The zoo director himself made Aunt Petunia a cup of strong sweet tea while he apologised over and over again. Piers and Dudley could only gibber. As far as Harry had seen, the snake hadn’t done anything except snap playfully at their heels as it passed, but by the time they were all back in Uncle Vernon’s car, Dudley was telling them how it had nearly bitten off his leg, while Piers was swearing it had tried to squeeze him to death. But worst of all, for Harry at least, was Piers calming down enough to say, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry was talking to it, weren’t you, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon waited until Piers was safely out of the house before starting on Harry. He was so angry he could hardly speak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He managed to say, ‘Go – cupboard – stay – no meals,’ before he collapsed into a chair and Aunt Petunia had to run and get him a large brandy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Vanishing Glass 27 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry lay in his dark cupboard much later, wishing he had a watch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He  didn’t  know  what  time  it  was  and  he  couldn’t  be  sure  the Dursleys were asleep yet. Until they were, he couldn’t risk sneaking to the kitchen for some food. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He’d lived with the Dursleys almost ten years, ten miserable years, as long as he could remember, ever since he’d been a baby and his parents had died in that car crash. He couldn’t remember being in the car when his parents had died. Sometimes, when he strained his memory during long hours in his cupboard, he came up with a strange vision: a blinding flash of green light and a burning pain on his forehead. This, he supposed, was the crash, though he couldn’t imagine where all the green light came from. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He couldn’t remember his parents at all. His aunt and uncle never spoke about them, and of course he was forbidden to ask questions. There were no photographs of them in the house. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When he had been younger, Harry had dreamed and dreamed of some unknown relation coming to take him away, but it had never happened; the Dursleys were his only family. Yet sometimes he thought (or maybe hoped) that strangers in the street seemed to know him. Very strange strangers they were, too. A tiny man in a violet top hat had bowed to him once while out shopping with Aunt Petunia and Dudley. After asking Harry furiously if he knew the man, Aunt Petunia had rushed them out of the shop without buying anything. A wild-looking old woman dressed all in green had waved merrily at him once on a bus. A bald man in a very long purple coat had actually shaken his hand in the street the other day and then walked away without a word. The weirdest thing about all these people was the way they seemed to vanish the second Harry tried to get a closer look. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At school, Harry had no one. Everybody knew that Dudley’s gang hated that odd Harry Potter in his baggy old clothes and broken glasses, and nobody liked to disagree with Dudley’s gang. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER THREE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Letters from No One </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The escape of the Brazilian boa constrictor earned Harry his longest-ever punishment. By the time he was allowed out of his cupboard again, the summer holidays had started and Dudley had already broken his new cine-camera, crashed his remote-control aeroplane and, first time on his racing bike, knocked down old Mrs Figg as she crossed Privet Drive on her crutches. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was glad school was over, but there was no escaping Dudley’s gang, who visited the house every single day. Piers, Dennis, Malcolm and Gordon were all big and stupid, but as Dudley was the biggest and stupidest of the lot, he was the leader. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rest of them were all quite happy to join in Dudley’s favourite sport: Harry-hunting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This was why Harry spent as much time as possible out of the house, wandering around and thinking about the end of the holidays, where he could see a tiny ray of hope. When September came he would be going off to secondary school and, for the first time in his life, he wouldn’t be with Dudley. Dudley had a place at Uncle Vernon’s old school, Smeltings. Piers Polkiss was going there, too. Harry, on the other hand, was going to Stonewall High, the local comprehensive. Dudley thought this was very funny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They stuff people’s heads down the toilet first day at Stonewall,’ he told Harry. ‘Want to come upstairs and practise?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No thanks,’ said Harry. ‘The poor toilet’s never had anything as horrible as your head down it – it might be sick.’ Then he ran, before Dudley could work out what he’d said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One day in July, Aunt Petunia took Dudley to London to buy his Smeltings uniform, leaving Harry at Mrs Figg’s. Mrs Figg wasn’t as bad as usual. It turned out she’d broken her leg tripping over one of her cats and she didn’t seem quite as fond of them as before. She let Harry watch television and gave him a bit of </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Letters from No One 29 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">chocolate cake that tasted as though she’d had it for several years. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">That evening, Dudley paraded around the living-room for the family in his brand-new uniform. Smeltings boys wore maroon tailcoats, orange knickerbockers and flat straw hats called boaters. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They also carried knobbly sticks, used for hitting each other while the teachers weren’t looking. This was supposed to be good training for later life. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As  he  looked  at  Dudley  in  his  new  knickerbockers,  Uncle Vernon said gruffly that it was the proudest moment of his life. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Petunia burst into tears and said she couldn’t believe it was her Ickle Dudleykins, he looked so handsome and grown-up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t trust himself to speak. He thought two of his ribs might already have cracked from trying not to laugh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a horrible smell in the kitchen next morning when Harry went in for breakfast. It seemed to be coming from a large metal tub in the sink. He went to have a look. The tub was full of what looked like dirty rags swimming in grey water. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s this?’ he asked Aunt Petunia. Her lips tightened as they always did if he dared to ask a question. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your new school uniform,’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked in the bowl again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ he said. ‘I didn’t realise it had to be so wet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be stupid,’ snapped Aunt Petunia. ‘I’m dyeing some of Dudley’s old things grey for you. It’ll look just like everyone else’s when I’ve finished.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry seriously doubted this, but thought it best not to argue. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He sat down at the table and tried not to think about how he was going to look on his first day at Stonewall High – like he was wearing bits of old elephant skin, probably. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley and Uncle Vernon came in, both with wrinkled noses because of the smell from Harry’s new uniform. Uncle Vernon opened his newspaper as usual and Dudley banged his Smeltings stick, which he carried everywhere, on the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They heard the click of the letter-box and flop of letters on the doormat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get the post, Dudley,’ said Uncle Vernon from behind his paper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Make Harry get it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get the post, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Make Dudley get it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>30 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Poke him with your Smeltings stick, Dudley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dodged the Smeltings stick and went to get the post. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Three things lay on the doormat: a postcard from Uncle Vernon’s sister Marge, who was holidaying on the Isle of Wight, a brown envelope that looked like a bill and –  <i class=\"calibre3\">a letter for Harry. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry picked it up and stared at it, his heart twanging like a giant elastic band. No one, ever, in his whole life, had written to him. Who would? He had no friends, no other relatives – he didn’t belong to the library so he’d never even got rude notes asking for books back. Yet here it was, a letter, addressed so plainly there could be no mistake: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Mr H. Potter </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Cupboard under the Stairs </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">4 Privet Drive </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Little Whinging </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Surrey </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The envelope was thick and heavy, made of yellowish parchment, and the address was written in emerald-green ink. There was no stamp. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Turning the envelope over, his hand trembling, Harry saw a purple wax seal bearing a coat of arms; a lion, an eagle, a badger and a snake surrounding a large letter ‘H’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hurry up, boy!’ shouted Uncle Vernon from the kitchen. ‘What are you doing, checking for letter-bombs?’ He chuckled at his own joke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went back to the kitchen, still staring at his letter. He handed Uncle Vernon the bill and the postcard, sat down and slowly began to open the yellow envelope. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon ripped open the bill, snorted in disgust and flipped over the postcard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Marge’s ill,’ he informed Aunt Petunia. ‘Ate a funny whelk …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dad!’ said Dudley suddenly. ‘Dad, Harry’s got something!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was on the point of unfolding his letter, which was written on the same heavy parchment as the envelope, when it was jerked sharply out of his hand by Uncle Vernon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s  <i class=\"calibre3\">mine! </i>’ said Harry, trying to snatch it back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’d be writing to you?’ sneered Uncle Vernon, shaking the letter open with one hand and glancing at it. His face went from </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Letters from No One 31 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">red to green faster than a set of traffic lights. And it didn’t stop there. Within seconds it was the greyish white of old porridge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘P-P-Petunia!’ he gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley tried to grab the letter to read it, but Uncle Vernon held it high out of his reach. Aunt Petunia took it curiously and read the first line. For a moment it looked as though she might faint. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She clutched her throat and made a choking noise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Vernon! Oh my goodness – Vernon!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They stared at each other, seeming to have forgotten that Harry and Dudley were still in the room. Dudley wasn’t used to being ignored. He gave his father a sharp tap on the head with his Smeltings stick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I want to read that letter,’ he said loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">I</i> want to read it,’ said Harry furiously, ‘as it’s  <i class=\"calibre3\">mine. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out, both of you,’ croaked Uncle Vernon, stuffing the letter back inside its envelope. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I WANT MY LETTER!’ he shouted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let  <i class=\"calibre3\">me</i> see it!’ demanded Dudley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OUT!’ roared Uncle Vernon, and he took both Harry and Dudley by the scruffs of their necks and threw them into the hall, slamming the kitchen door behind them. Harry and Dudley promptly had a furious but silent fight over who would listen at the keyhole; Dudley won, so Harry, his glasses dangling from one ear, lay flat on his stomach to listen at the crack between door and floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Vernon,’ Aunt Petunia was saying in a quivering voice, ‘look at the address – how could they possibly know where he sleeps? You don’t think they’re watching the house?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Watching – spying – might be following us,’ muttered Uncle Vernon wildly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But what should we do, Vernon? Should we write back? Tell them we don’t want –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could see Uncle Vernon’s shiny black shoes pacing up and down the kitchen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ he said finally. ‘No, we’ll ignore it. If they don’t get an answer … yes, that’s best … we won’t do anything …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not having one in the house, Petunia! Didn’t we swear when we took him in we’d stamp out that dangerous nonsense?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>32 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">That evening when he got back from work, Uncle Vernon did something he’d never done before; he visited Harry in his cupboard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s my letter?’ said Harry, the moment Uncle Vernon had squeezed through the door. ‘Who’s writing to me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one. It was addressed to you by mistake,’ said Uncle Vernon shortly. ‘I have burned it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was  <i class=\"calibre3\">not</i> a mistake,’ said Harry angrily. ‘It had my cupboard on it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘SILENCE!’ yelled Uncle Vernon, and a couple of spiders fell from the ceiling. He took a few deep breaths and then forced his face into a smile, which looked quite painful. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – yes, Harry – about this cupboard. Your aunt and I have been thinking … you’re really getting a bit big for it … we think it might be nice if you moved into Dudley’s second bedroom.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t ask questions!’ snapped his uncle. ‘Take this stuff upstairs, now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dursleys’ house had four bedrooms: one for Uncle Vernon and Aunt Petunia, one for visitors (usually Uncle Vernon’s sister, Marge), one where Dudley slept and one where Dudley kept all the toys and things that wouldn’t fit into his first bedroom. It only took Harry one trip upstairs to move everything he owned from the cupboard to this room. He sat down on the bed and stared around him. Nearly everything in here was broken. The month-old cine-camera was lying on top of a small, working tank Dudley had once driven over next door’s dog; in the corner was Dudley’s first-ever television set, which he’d put his foot through when his favourite programme had been cancelled; there was a large bird-cage which had once held a parrot that Dudley had swapped at school for a real air-rifle, which was up on a shelf with the end all bent because Dudley had sat on it. Other shelves were full of books. They were the only things in the room that looked as though they’d never been touched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">From downstairs came the sound of Dudley bawling at his mother: ‘I don’t  <i class=\"calibre3\">want</i> him in there … I  <i class=\"calibre3\">need</i> that room … make him get out …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sighed and stretched out on the bed. Yesterday he’d have given anything to be up here. Today he’d rather be back in his cupboard with that letter than up here without it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Next morning at breakfast, everyone was rather quiet. Dudley was </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Letters from No One 33 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">in shock. He’d screamed, whacked his father with his Smeltings stick, been sick on purpose, kicked his mother and thrown his tortoise through the greenhouse roof and he still didn’t have his room back. Harry was thinking about this time yesterday and bitterly wishing he’d opened the letter in the hall. Uncle Vernon and Aunt Petunia kept looking at each other darkly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When the post arrived, Uncle Vernon, who seemed to be trying to be nice to Harry, made Dudley go and get it. They heard him banging things with his Smeltings stick all the way down the hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he shouted, ‘There’s another one!  <i class=\"calibre3\">Mr H. Potter, The Smallest</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Bedroom, 4 Privet Drive</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a strangled cry, Uncle Vernon leapt from his seat and ran down the hall, Harry right behind him. Uncle Vernon had to wrestle Dudley to the ground to get the letter from him, which was made difficult by the fact that Harry had grabbed Uncle Vernon around the neck from behind. After a minute of confused fighting, in which everyone got hit a lot by the Smeltings stick, Uncle Vernon straightened up, gasping for breath, with Harry’s letter clutched in his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go to your cupboard – I mean, your bedroom,’ he wheezed at Harry. ‘Dudley – go – just go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry walked round and round his new room. Someone knew he had moved out of his cupboard and they seemed to know he hadn’t received his first letter. Surely that meant they’d try again? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And this time he’d make sure they didn’t fail. He had a plan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The repaired alarm clock rang at six o’clock the next morning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned it off quickly and dressed silently. He mustn’t wake the Dursleys. He stole downstairs without turning on any of the lights. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was going to wait for the postman on the corner of Privet Drive and get the letters for number four first. His heart hammered as he crept across the dark hall towards the front door – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘AAAAARRRGH!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry leapt into the air – he’d trodden on something big and squashy on the doormat – something  <i class=\"calibre3\">alive! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lights clicked on upstairs and to his horror Harry realised that the big squashy something had been his uncle’s face. Uncle Vernon had been lying at the foot of the front door in a sleeping bag, clearly making sure that Harry didn’t do exactly what he’d </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>34 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">been trying to do. He shouted at Harry for about half an hour and then told him to go and make a cup of tea. Harry shuffled miserably off into the kitchen, and by the time he got back, the post had arrived, right into Uncle Vernon’s lap. Harry could see three letters addressed in green ink. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I want –’ he began, but Uncle Vernon was tearing the letters into pieces before his eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon didn’t go to work that day. He stayed at home and nailed up the letter-box. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See,’ he explained to Aunt Petunia through a mouthful of nails, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘if they can’t  <i class=\"calibre3\">deliver</i> them they’ll just give up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not sure that’ll work, Vernon.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, these people’s minds work in strange ways, Petunia, they’re not like you and me,’ said Uncle Vernon, trying to knock in a nail with the piece of fruit cake Aunt Petunia had just brought him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On Friday, no fewer than twelve letters arrived for Harry. As they couldn’t go through the letter-box they had been pushed under the door, slotted through the sides and a few even forced through the small window in the downstairs toilet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon stayed at home again. After burning all the letters, he got out a hammer and nails and boarded up the cracks around the front and back doors so no one could go out. He hummed </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tiptoe through the Tulips’ as he worked, and jumped at small noises. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On Saturday, things began to get out of hand. Twenty-four letters to Harry found their way into the house, rolled up and hidden inside each of the two dozen eggs that their very confused milk-man had handed Aunt Petunia through the living-room window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">While Uncle Vernon made furious telephone calls to the post office and the dairy trying to find someone to complain to, Aunt Petunia shredded the letters in her food mixer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who on earth wants to talk to  <i class=\"calibre3\">you</i> this badly?’ Dudley asked Harry in amazement. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On Sunday morning, Uncle Vernon sat down at the breakfast table looking tired and rather ill, but happy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No post on Sundays,’ he reminded them happily as he spread </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Letters from No One 35 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">marmalade on his newspapers, ‘no damn letters today –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something came whizzing down the kitchen chimney as he spoke and caught him sharply on the back of the head. Next moment, thirty or forty letters came pelting out of the fireplace like bullets. The Dursleys ducked, but Harry leapt into the air trying to catch one – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Out! OUT!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon seized Harry around the waist and threw him into the hall. When Aunt Petunia and Dudley had run out with their arms over their faces, Uncle Vernon slammed the door shut. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They could hear the letters still streaming into the room, bouncing off the walls and floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That does it,’ said Uncle Vernon, trying to speak calmly but pulling great tufts out of his moustache at the same time. ‘I want you all back here in five minutes, ready to leave. We’re going away. Just pack some clothes. No arguments!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked so dangerous with half his moustache missing that no one dared argue. Ten minutes later they had wrenched their way through the boarded-up doors and were in the car, speeding towards the motorway. Dudley was sniffling in the back seat; his father had hit him round the head for holding them up while he tried to pack his television, video and computer in his sports bag. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They drove. And they drove. Even Aunt Petunia didn’t dare ask where they were going. Every now and then Uncle Vernon would take a sharp turning and drive in the opposite direction for a while. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shake ’em off … shake ’em off,’ he would mutter whenever he did this. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They didn’t stop to eat or drink all day. By nightfall Dudley was howling. He’d never had such a bad day in his life. He was hungry, he’d missed five television programmes he’d wanted to see and he’d never gone so long without blowing up an alien on his computer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon stopped at last outside a gloomy-looking hotel on the outskirts of a big city. Dudley and Harry shared a room with twin beds and damp, musty sheets. Dudley snored but Harry stayed awake, sitting on the window-sill, staring down at the lights of passing cars and wondering … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>36 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They ate stale cornflakes and cold tinned tomatoes on toast for breakfast next day. They had just finished when the owner of the hotel came over to their table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Scuse me, but is one of you Mr H. Potter? Only I got about an </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">’undred of these at the front desk.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She held up a letter so they could read the green ink address: <i class=\"calibre3\">Mr H. Potter </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Room 17 </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Railview Hotel </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Cokeworth </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry made a grab for the letter but Uncle Vernon knocked his hand out of the way. The woman stared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll take them,’ said Uncle Vernon, standing up quickly and following her from the dining-room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wouldn’t it be better just to go home, dear?’ Aunt Petunia suggested timidly, hours later, but Uncle Vernon didn’t seem to hear her. Exactly what he was looking for, none of them knew. He drove them into the middle of a forest, got out, looked around, shook his head, got back in the car and off they went again. The same thing happened in the middle of a ploughed field, halfway across a suspension bridge and at the top of a multi-storey car park. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Daddy’s gone mad, hasn’t he?’ Dudley asked Aunt Petunia dully late that afternoon. Uncle Vernon had parked at the coast, locked them all inside the car and disappeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It started to rain. Great drops beat on the roof of the car. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley snivelled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s Monday,’ he told his mother. ‘The Great Humberto’s on tonight. I want to stay somewhere with a  <i class=\"calibre3\">television. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Monday. This reminded Harry of something. If it  <i class=\"calibre3\">was</i> Monday – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and you could usually count on Dudley to know the days of the week, because of television – then tomorrow, Tuesday, was Harry’s eleventh birthday. Of course, his birthdays were never exactly fun </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– last year, the Dursleys had given him a coat-hanger and a pair of Uncle Vernon’s old socks. Still, you weren’t eleven every day. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon was back and he was smiling. He was also carrying a long, thin package and didn’t answer Aunt Petunia when she </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Letters from No One 37 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">asked what he’d bought. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Found the perfect place!’ he said. ‘Come on! Everyone out!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was very cold outside the car. Uncle Vernon was pointing at what looked like a large rock way out to sea. Perched on top of the rock was the most miserable little shack you could imagine. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One thing was certain, there was no television in there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Storm forecast for tonight!’ said Uncle Vernon gleefully, clapping his hands together. ‘And this gentleman’s kindly agreed to lend us his boat!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A toothless old man came ambling up to them, pointing, with a rather wicked grin, at an old rowing boat bobbing in the iron-grey water below them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve already got us some rations,’ said Uncle Vernon, ‘so all aboard!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was freezing in the boat. Icy sea spray and rain crept down their necks and a chilly wind whipped their faces. After what seemed like hours they reached the rock, where Uncle Vernon, slipping and sliding, led the way to the broken-down house. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The inside was horrible; it smelled strongly of seaweed, the wind whistled through the gaps in the wooden walls and the fireplace was damp and empty. There were only two rooms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon’s rations turned out to be a packet of crisps each and four bananas. He tried to start a fire but the empty crisp packets just smoked and shrivelled up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Could do with some of those letters now, eh?’ he said cheerfully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was in a very good mood. Obviously he thought nobody stood a chance of reaching them here in a storm to deliver post. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry privately agreed, though the thought didn’t cheer him up at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As night fell, the promised storm blew up around them. Spray from the high waves splattered the walls of the hut and a fierce wind rattled the filthy windows. Aunt Petunia found a few mouldy blankets in the second room and made up a bed for Dudley on the moth-eaten sofa. She and Uncle Vernon went off to the lumpy bed next door and Harry was left to find the softest bit of floor he could and to curl up under the thinnest, most ragged blanket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The storm raged more and more ferociously as the night went on. Harry couldn’t sleep. He shivered and turned over, trying to </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>38 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">get comfortable, his stomach rumbling with hunger. Dudley’s snores were drowned by the low rolls of thunder that started near midnight. The lighted dial of Dudley’s watch, which was dangling over the edge of the sofa on his fat wrist, told Harry he’d be eleven in ten minutes’ time. He lay and watched his birthday tick nearer, wondering if the Dursleys would remember at all, wondering where the letter-writer was now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Five minutes to go. Harry heard something creak outside. He hoped the roof wasn’t going to fall in, although he might be warmer if it did. Four minutes to go. Maybe the house in Privet Drive would be so full of letters when they got back that he’d be able to steal one somehow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Three minutes to go. Was that the sea, slapping hard on the rock like that? And (two minutes to go) what was that funny crunching noise? Was the rock crumbling into the sea? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One minute to go and he’d be eleven. Thirty seconds … twenty </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… ten – nine – maybe he’d wake Dudley up, just to annoy him – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">three – two – one – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">BOOM. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The whole shack shivered and Harry sat bolt upright, staring at the door. Someone was outside, knocking to come in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER FOUR — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Keeper of the Keys </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">BOOM. They knocked again. Dudley jerked awake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s the cannon?’ he said stupidly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a crash behind them and Uncle Vernon came skid-ding into the room. He was holding a rifle in his hands – now they knew what had been in the long, thin package he had brought with them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s there?’ he shouted. ‘I warn you – I’m armed!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a pause. Then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">SMASH! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door was hit with such force that it swung clean off its hinges and with a deafening crash landed flat on the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A giant of a man was standing in the doorway. His face was almost completely hidden by a long, shaggy mane of hair and a wild, tangled beard, but you could make out his eyes, glinting like black beetles under all the hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The giant squeezed his way into the hut, stooping so that his head just brushed the ceiling. He bent down, picked up the door and fitted it easily back into its frame. The noise of the storm outside dropped a little. He turned to look at them all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Couldn’t make us a cup o’ tea, could yeh? It’s not been an easy journey …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He strode over to the sofa where Dudley sat frozen with fear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Budge up, yeh great lump,’ said the stranger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley squeaked and ran to hide behind his mother, who was crouching, terrified, behind Uncle Vernon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An’ here’s Harry!’ said the giant. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up into the fierce, wild, shadowy face and saw that the beetle eyes were crinkled in a smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Las’ time I saw you, you was only a baby,’ said the giant. ‘Yeh look a lot like yer dad, but yeh’ve got yer mum’s eyes.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>40 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon made a funny rasping noise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I demand that you leave at once, sir!’ he said. ‘You are breaking and entering!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, shut up, Dursley, yeh great prune,’ said the giant. He reached over the back of the sofa, jerked the gun out of Uncle Vernon’s hands, bent it into a knot as easily as if it had been made of rubber, and threw it into a corner of the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon made another funny noise, like a mouse being trodden on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyway – Harry,’ said the giant, turning his back on the Dursleys, ‘a very happy birthday to yeh. Got summat fer yeh here  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– I mighta sat on it at some point, but it’ll taste all right.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">From an inside pocket of his black overcoat he pulled a slightly squashed box. Harry opened it with trembling fingers. Inside was a large, sticky chocolate cake with  <i class=\"calibre3\">Happy Birthday Harry</i> written on it in green icing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up at the giant. He meant to say thank you, but the words got lost on the way to his mouth, and what he said instead was, ‘Who are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The giant chuckled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘True, I haven’t introduced meself. Rubeus Hagrid, Keeper of Keys and Grounds at Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He held out an enormous hand and shook Harry’s whole arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about that tea then, eh?’ he said, rubbing his hands together. ‘I’d not say no ter summat stronger if yeh’ve got it, mind.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His eyes fell on the empty grate with the shrivelled crisp packets  in  it  and  he  snorted.  He  bent down over the fireplace; they couldn’t see what he was doing but when he drew back a second later, there was a roaring fire there. It filled the whole damp hut with flickering light and Harry felt the warmth wash over him as though he’d sunk into a hot bath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The giant sat back down on the sofa, which sagged under his weight, and began taking all sorts of things out of the pockets of his coat: a copper kettle, a squashy package of sausages, a poker, a teapot, several chipped mugs and a bottle of some amber liquid which  he  took  a  swig  from  before  starting  to  make  tea.  Soon  the hut was full of the sound and smell of sizzling sausage. Nobody said a thing while the giant was working, but as he slid the first six fat, juicy, slightly burnt sausages from the poker, Dudley </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Keeper of the Keys 41 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">fidgeted a little. Uncle Vernon said sharply, ‘Don’t touch anything he gives you, Dudley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The giant chuckled darkly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yer great puddin’ of a son don’ need fattenin’ any more, Dursley, don’ worry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He passed the sausages to Harry, who was so hungry he had never tasted anything so wonderful, but he still couldn’t take his eyes off the giant. Finally, as nobody seemed about to explain anything, he said, ‘I’m sorry, but I still don’t really know who you are.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The giant took a gulp of tea and wiped his mouth with the back of his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Call me Hagrid,’ he said, ‘everyone does. An’ like I told yeh, I’m Keeper of Keys at Hogwarts – yeh’ll know all about Hogwarts, o’ course.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – no,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid looked shocked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry,’ Harry said quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Sorry? </i>’ barked Hagrid, turning to stare at the Dursleys, who shrank back into the shadows. ‘It’s them as should be sorry! I knew yeh weren’t gettin’ yer letters but I never thought yeh wouldn’t even know abou’ Hogwarts, fer cryin’ out loud! Did yeh never wonder where yer parents learnt it all?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All what?’ asked Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ALL WHAT?’ Hagrid thundered. ‘Now wait jus’ one second!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had leapt to his feet. In his anger he seemed to fill the whole hut. The Dursleys were cowering against the wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you mean ter tell me,’ he growled at the Dursleys, ‘that this boy – this boy! – knows nothin’ abou’ – about ANYTHING?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry thought this was going a bit far. He had been to school, after all, and his marks weren’t bad. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know  <i class=\"calibre3\">some</i> things,’ he said. ‘I can, you know, do maths and stuff.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hagrid simply waved his hand and said, ‘About  <i class=\"calibre3\">our</i> world, I mean.  <i class=\"calibre3\">Your</i> world.  <i class=\"calibre3\">My</i> world.  <i class=\"calibre3\">Yer parents’ world. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What world?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid looked as if he was about to explode. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘DURSLEY!’ he boomed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon, who had gone very pale, whispered something that sounded like ‘Mimblewimble’. Hagrid stared wildly at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But yeh must know about yer mum and dad,’ he said. ‘I mean, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>42 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they’re  <i class=\"calibre3\">famous. You’re</i> famous.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What? My – my mum and dad weren’t famous, were they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh don’ know … yeh don’ know …’ Hagrid ran his fingers through his hair, fixing Harry with a bewildered stare. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh don’ know what yeh  <i class=\"calibre3\">are? </i>’ he said finally. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon suddenly found his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop!’ he commanded. ‘Stop right there, sir! I forbid you to tell the boy anything!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A braver man than Vernon Dursley would have quailed under the furious look Hagrid now gave him; when Hagrid spoke, his every syllable trembled with rage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You never told him? Never told him what was in the letter Dumbledore left fer him? I was there! I saw Dumbledore leave it, Dursley! An’ you’ve kept it from him all these years?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Kept  <i class=\"calibre3\">what</i> from me?’ said Harry eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘STOP! I FORBID YOU!’ yelled Uncle Vernon in panic. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Petunia gave a gasp of horror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, go boil yer heads, both of yeh,’ said Hagrid. ‘Harry – yer a wizard.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was silence inside the hut. Only the sea and the whistling wind could be heard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m a  <i class=\"calibre3\">what? </i>’ gasped Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A wizard, o’ course,’ said Hagrid, sitting back down on the sofa, which groaned and sank even lower, ‘an’ a thumpin’ good’un, I’d say, once yeh’ve been trained up a bit. With a mum an’ dad like yours, what else would yeh be? An’ I reckon it’s abou’ time yeh read yer letter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stretched out his hand at last to take the yellowish envelope, addressed in emerald green to  <i class=\"calibre3\">Mr H. Potter, The Floor,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Hut-on-the-Rock, The Sea. </i> He pulled out the letter and read: <i class=\"calibre3\">HOGWARTS SCHOOL OF WITCHCRAFT AND WIZARDRY</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Headmaster: Albus Dumbledore</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">(Order of Merlin, First Class, Grand Sorc., Chf. Warlock,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Supreme Mugwump, International Confed. of Wizards)</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\"> </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Dear Mr Potter, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">We are pleased to inform you that you have a place at</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. Please find</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Keeper of the Keys 43 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">enclosed a list of all necessary books and equipment. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Term begins on 1 September. We await your owl by no later</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">than 31 July. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Yours sincerely, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Minerva McGonagall </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Deputy Headmistress</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Questions exploded inside Harry’s head like fireworks and he couldn’t decide which to ask first. After a few minutes he stammered, ‘What does it mean, they await my owl?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gallopin’ Gorgons, that reminds me,’ said Hagrid, clapping a hand to his forehead with enough force to knock over a cart horse, and from yet another pocket inside his overcoat he pulled an owl – a real, live, rather ruffled-looking owl – a long quill and a roll of parchment. With his tongue between his teeth he scribbled a note which Harry could read upside-down: <i class=\"calibre3\">Dear Mr Dumbledore, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Given Harry his letter. Taking him to buy his things tomorrow. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Weather’s horrible. Hope you’re well. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Hagrid</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid rolled up the note, gave it to the owl, which clamped it in its beak, went to the door and threw the owl out into the storm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he came back and sat down as though this was as normal as talking on the telephone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry realised his mouth was open and closed it quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where was I?’ said Hagrid, but at that moment, Uncle Vernon, still ashen-faced but looking very angry, moved into the firelight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s not going,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid grunted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’d like ter see a great Muggle like you stop him,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A what?’ said Harry, interested. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A Muggle,’ said Hagrid. ‘It’s what we call non-magic folk like them. An’ it’s your bad luck you grew up in a family o’ the biggest Muggles I ever laid eyes on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We swore when we took him in we’d put a stop to that rubbish,’ said Uncle Vernon, ‘swore we’d stamp it out of him! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>44 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wizard, indeed!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You  <i class=\"calibre3\">knew? </i>’ said Harry. ‘You  <i class=\"calibre3\">knew</i> I’m a – a wizard?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Knew!’ shrieked Aunt Petunia suddenly. ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Knew! </i>  Of  course  we knew! How could you not be, my dratted sister being what she was? Oh, she got a letter just like that and disappeared off to that  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– that  <i class=\"calibre3\">school</i> – and came home every holiday with her pockets full of frog-spawn, turning teacups into rats. I was the only one who saw her for what she was – a freak! But for my mother and father, oh no, it was Lily this and Lily that, they were proud of having a witch in the family!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She stopped to draw a deep breath and then went ranting on. It seemed she had been wanting to say all this for years. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then she met that Potter at school and they left and got married and had you, and of course I knew you’d be just the same, just as strange, just as – as –  <i class=\"calibre3\">abnormal</i> – and then, if you please, she went and got herself blown up and we got landed with you!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had gone very white. As soon as he found his voice he said, ‘Blown up? You told me they died in a car crash!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘CAR CRASH!’ roared Hagrid, jumping up so angrily that the Dursleys scuttled back to their corner. ‘How could a car crash kill Lily an’ James Potter? It’s an outrage! A scandal! Harry Potter not knowin’ his own story when every kid in our world knows his name!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But why? What happened?’ Harry asked urgently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The anger faded from Hagrid’s face. He looked suddenly anxious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I never expected this,’ he said, in a low, worried voice. ‘I had no idea, when Dumbledore told me there might be trouble gettin’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">hold of yeh, how much yeh didn’t know. Ah, Harry, I don’ know if I’m the right person ter tell yeh – but someone’s gotta – yeh can’t go off ter Hogwarts not knowin’.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He threw a dirty look at the Dursleys. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, it’s best yeh know as much as I can tell yeh – mind, I can’t tell yeh everythin’, it’s a great myst’ry, parts of it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He sat down, stared into the fire for a few seconds and then said, ‘It begins, I suppose, with – with a person called – but it’s incredible yeh don’t know his name, everyone in our world knows –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – I don’ like sayin’ the name if I can help it. No one does.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Keeper of the Keys 45 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why not?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gulpin’ gargoyles, Harry, people are still scared. Blimey, this is difficult. See, there was this wizard who went … bad. As bad as you could go. Worse. Worse than worse. His name was …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid gulped, but no words came out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Could you write it down?’ Harry suggested. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nah – can’t spell it. All right –  <i class=\"calibre3\">Voldemort</i>.’ Hagrid shuddered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’ make me say it again. Anyway, this – this wizard, about twenty years ago now, started lookin’ fer followers. Got ’em, too – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">some were afraid, some just wanted a bit o’ his power, ’cause he was gettin’ himself power, all right. Dark days, Harry. Didn’t know who ter trust, didn’t dare get friendly with strange wizards or witches … Terrible things happened. He was takin’ over. ’Course, some stood up to him – an’ he killed ’em. Horribly. One o’ the only safe places left was Hogwarts. Reckon Dumbledore’s the only one You-Know-Who was afraid of. Didn’t dare try takin’ the school, not jus’ then, anyway. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, yer mum an’ dad were as good a witch an’ wizard as I ever knew. Head Boy an’ Girl at Hogwarts in their day! Suppose the myst’ry is why You-Know-Who never tried to get ’em on his side before … probably knew they were too close ter Dumbledore ter want anythin’ ter do with the Dark Side. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe he thought he could persuade ’em … maybe he just wanted ’em outta the way. All anyone knows is, he turned up in the village where you was all living, on Hallowe’en ten years ago. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You was just a year old. He came ter yer house an’ – an’ –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid suddenly pulled out a very dirty, spotted handkerchief and blew his nose with a sound like a foghorn. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry,’ he said. ‘But it’s that sad – knew yer mum an’ dad, an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">nicer people yeh couldn’t find – anyway – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You-Know-Who killed ’em. An’ then – an’ this is the real myst’ry of the thing – he tried to kill you, too. Wanted ter make a clean job of it, I suppose, or maybe he just liked killin’ by then. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he couldn’t do it. Never wondered how you got that mark on yer forehead? That was no ordinary cut. That’s what yeh get when a powerful, evil curse touches yeh – took care of yer mum an’ dad an’ yer house, even – but it didn’t work on you, an’ that’s why yer famous, Harry. No one ever lived after he decided ter kill ’em, no one except you, an’ he’d killed some o’ the best witches an’  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">wizards of the age – the McKinnons, the Bones, the Prewetts – an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>46 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you was only a baby, an’ you lived.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something very painful was going on in Harry’s mind. As Hagrid’s story came to a close, he saw again the blinding flash of green light, more clearly than he had ever remembered it before – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and he remembered something else, for the first time in his life – a high, cold, cruel laugh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was watching him sadly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Took yeh from the ruined house myself, on Dumbledore’s orders. Brought yeh ter this lot …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Load of old tosh,’ said Uncle Vernon. Harry jumped, he had almost forgotten that the Dursleys were there. Uncle Vernon certainly seemed to have got back his courage. He was glaring at Hagrid and his fists were clenched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, you listen here, boy,’ he snarled. ‘I accept there’s something strange about you, probably nothing a good beating wouldn’t have cured – and as for all this about your parents, well, they were weirdos, no denying it, and the world’s better off without them in my opinion – asked for all they got, getting mixed up with these wizarding types – just what I expected, always knew they’d come to a sticky end –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But at that moment, Hagrid leapt from the sofa and drew a battered pink umbrella from inside his coat. Pointing this at Uncle Vernon like a sword, he said, ‘I’m warning you, Dursley – I’m warning you – one more word …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In danger of being speared on the end of an umbrella by a bearded giant, Uncle Vernon’s courage failed again; he flattened himself against the wall and fell silent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s better,’ said Hagrid, breathing heavily and sitting back down on the sofa, which this time sagged right down to the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, meanwhile, still had questions to ask, hundreds of them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But what happened to Vol– sorry – I mean, You-Know-Who?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good question, Harry. Disappeared. Vanished. Same night he tried ter kill you. Makes yeh even more famous. That’s the biggest myst’ry, see … he was gettin’ more an’ more powerful – why’d he go? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Some say he died. Codswallop, in my opinion. Dunno if he had enough human left in him to die. Some say he’s still out there, bidin’ his time, like, but I don’ believe it. People who was on his side came back ter ours. Some of ’em came outta kinda trances. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Don’ reckon they could’ve done if he was comin’ back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Keeper of the Keys 47 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Most of us reckon he’s still out there somewhere but lost his powers. Too weak to carry on. ’Cause somethin’ about you finished him, Harry. There was somethin’ goin’ on that night he hadn’t counted on –  <i class=\"calibre3\">I</i> dunno what it was, no one does – but somethin’ about you stumped him, all right.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid looked at Harry with warmth and respect blazing in his eyes, but Harry, instead of feeling pleased and proud, felt quite sure there had been a horrible mistake. A wizard? Him? How could he possibly be? He’d spent his life being clouted by Dudley and bullied by Aunt Petunia and Uncle Vernon; if he was really a wizard, why hadn’t they been turned into warty toads every time they’d tried to lock him in his cupboard? If he’d once defeated the greatest sorcerer in the world, how come Dudley had always been able to kick him around like a football? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid,’ he said quietly, ‘I think you must have made a mistake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I don’t think I can be a wizard.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">To his surprise, Hagrid chuckled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not a wizard, eh? Never made things happen when you was scared, or angry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked into the fire. Now he came to think about it … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">every odd thing that had ever made his aunt and uncle furious with him had happened when he, Harry, had been upset or angry </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… chased by Dudley’s gang, he had somehow found himself out of their reach … dreading going to school with that ridiculous haircut, he’d managed to make it grow back … and the very last time Dudley had hit him, hadn’t he got his revenge, without even realising he was doing it? Hadn’t he set a boa constrictor on him? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked back at Hagrid, smiling, and saw that Hagrid was positively beaming at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See?’ said Hagrid. ‘Harry Potter, not a wizard – you wait, you’ll be right famous at Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Uncle Vernon wasn’t going to give in without a fight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Haven’t I told you he’s not going?’ he hissed. ‘He’s going to Stonewall High and he’ll be grateful for it. I’ve read those letters and he needs all sorts of rubbish – spell books and wands and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If he wants ter go, a great Muggle like you won’t stop him,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">growled Hagrid. ‘Stop Lily an’ James Potter’s son goin’ ter Hogwarts! Yer mad. His name’s been down ever since he was born. He’s off ter the finest school of witchcraft and wizardry in the world. Seven years there and he won’t know himself. He’ll be </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>48 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">with youngsters of his own sort, fer a change, an’ he’ll be under the greatest Headmaster Hogwarts ever had, Albus Dumbled–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I AM NOT PAYING FOR SOME CRACKPOT OLD FOOL TO </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">TEACH HIM MAGIC TRICKS!’ yelled Uncle Vernon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he had finally gone too far. Hagrid seized his umbrella and whirled it over his head. ‘NEVER –’ he thundered, ‘– INSULT – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ALBUS – DUMBLEDORE – IN – FRONT – OF – ME!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He brought the umbrella swishing down through the air to point at Dudley – there was a flash of violet light, a sound like a firecracker, a sharp squeal and next second, Dudley was dancing on the spot with his hands clasped over his fat bottom, howling in pain. When he turned his back on them, Harry saw a curly pig’s tail poking through a hole in his trousers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon roared. Pulling Aunt Petunia and Dudley into the other room, he cast one last terrified look at Hagrid and slammed the door behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid looked down at his umbrella and stroked his beard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shouldn’ta lost me temper,’ he said ruefully, ‘but it didn’t work anyway. Meant ter turn him into a pig, but I suppose he was so much like a pig anyway there wasn’t much left ter do.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He cast a sideways look at Harry under his bushy eyebrows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Be grateful if yeh didn’t mention that ter anyone at Hogwarts,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he said. ‘I’m – er – not supposed ter do magic, strictly speakin’. I was allowed ter do a bit ter follow yeh an’ get yer letters to yeh an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">stuff – one o’ the reasons I was so keen ter take on the job –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why aren’t you supposed to do magic?’ asked Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, well – I was at Hogwarts meself but I – er – got expelled, ter tell yeh the truth. In me third year. They snapped me wand in half an’ everything. But Dumbledore let me stay on as gamekeeper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Great man, Dumbledore.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why were you expelled?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s gettin’ late and we’ve got lots ter do tomorrow,’ said Hagrid loudly. ‘Gotta get up ter town, get all yer books an’ that.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He took off his thick black coat and threw it to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can kip under that,’ he said. ‘Don’ mind if it wriggles a bit, I think I still got a couple o’ dormice in one o’ the pockets.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER FIVE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Diagon Alley </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry woke early the next morning. Although he could tell it was daylight, he kept his eyes shut tight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was a dream,’ he told himself firmly. ‘I dreamed a giant called Hagrid came to tell me I was going to a school for wizards. When I open my eyes I’ll be at home in my cupboard.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was suddenly a loud tapping noise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And there’s Aunt Petunia knocking on the door,’ Harry thought, his heart sinking. But he still didn’t open his eyes. It had been such a good dream. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Tap. Tap. Tap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right,’ Harry mumbled, ‘I’m getting up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He sat up and Hagrid’s heavy coat fell off him. The hut was full of sunlight, the storm was over, Hagrid himself was asleep on the collapsed sofa and there was an owl rapping its claw on the window, a newspaper held in its beak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry scrambled to his feet, so happy he felt as though a large balloon was swelling inside him. He went straight to the window and jerked it open. The owl swooped in and dropped the newspaper on top of Hagrid, who didn’t wake up. The owl then fluttered on to the floor and began to attack Hagrid’s coat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t do that.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to wave the owl out of the way, but it snapped its beak fiercely at him and carried on savaging the coat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid!’ said Harry loudly. ‘There’s an owl –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pay him,’ Hagrid grunted into the sofa. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He wants payin’ fer deliverin’ the paper. Look in the pockets.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s coat seemed to be made of nothing  <i class=\"calibre3\">but</i> pockets – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">bunches of keys, slug pellets, balls of string, mint humbugs, tea-bags … finally, Harry pulled out a handful of strange-looking coins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>50 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Give him five Knuts,’ said Hagrid sleepily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Knuts?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The little bronze ones.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry counted out five little bronze coins and the owl held out its leg so he could put the money into a small leather pouch tied to it. Then it flew off through the open window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid yawned loudly, sat up and stretched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Best be off, Harry, lots ter do today, gotta get up ter London an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">buy all yer stuff fer school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was turning over the wizard coins and looking at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had just thought of something which made him feel as though the happy balloon inside him had got a puncture. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Um – Hagrid?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mm?’ said Hagrid, who was pulling on his huge boots. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I haven’t got any money – and you heard Uncle Vernon last night – he won’t pay for me to go and learn magic.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t worry about that,’ said Hagrid, standing up and scratching his head. ‘D’yeh think yer parents didn’t leave yeh anything?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if their house was destroyed –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They didn’ keep their gold in the house, boy! Nah, first stop fer us is Gringotts. Wizards’ bank. Have a sausage, they’re not bad cold – an’ I wouldn’ say no teh a bit o’ yer birthday cake, neither.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wizards have  <i class=\"calibre3\">banks? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just the one. Gringotts. Run by goblins.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dropped the bit of sausage he was holding. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Goblins? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah – so yeh’d be mad ter try an’ rob it, I’ll tell yeh that. Never mess with goblins, Harry. Gringotts is the safest place in the world fer anything yeh want ter keep safe – ’cept maybe Hogwarts. As a matter o’ fact, I gotta visit Gringotts anyway. Fer Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hogwarts business.’ Hagrid drew himself up proudly. ‘He usually gets me ter do important stuff fer him. Fetchin’ you – gettin’  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">things from Gringotts – knows he can trust me, see. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Got everythin’? Come on, then.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry followed Hagrid out on to the rock. The sky was quite clear now and the sea gleamed in the sunlight. The boat Uncle Vernon had hired was still there, with a lot of water in the bottom after the storm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did you get here?’ Harry asked, looking around for another boat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Diagon Alley 51 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Flew,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Flew? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah – but we’ll go back in this. Not s’pposed ter use magic now I’ve got yeh.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They settled down in the boat, Harry still staring at Hagrid, trying to imagine him flying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Seems a shame ter row, though,’ said Hagrid, giving Harry another of his sideways looks. ‘If I was ter – er – speed things up a bit, would yeh mind not mentionin’ it at Hogwarts?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course not,’ said Harry, eager to see more magic. Hagrid pulled out the pink umbrella again, tapped it twice on the side of the boat and they sped off towards land. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why would you be mad to try and rob Gringotts?’ Harry asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Spells – enchantments,’ said Hagrid, unfolding his newspaper as he spoke. ‘They say there’s dragons guardin’ the high-security vaults. And then yeh gotta find yer way – Gringotts is hundreds of miles under London, see. Deep under the Underground. Yeh’d die of hunger tryin’ ter get out, even if yeh did manage ter get yer hands on summat.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat and thought about this while Hagrid read his newspaper, the  <i class=\"calibre3\">Daily Prophet</i>. Harry had learnt from Uncle Vernon that people liked to be left alone while they did this, but it was very difficult, he’d never had so many questions in his life. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ministry o’ Magic messin’ things up as usual,’ Hagrid muttered, turning the page. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s a Ministry of Magic?’ Harry asked, before he could stop himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Course,’ said Hagrid. ‘They wanted Dumbledore fer Minister, o’ course, but he’d never leave Hogwarts, so old Cornelius Fudge got the job. Bungler if ever there was one. So he pelts Dumbledore with owls every morning, askin’ fer advice.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But what does a Ministry of Magic  <i class=\"calibre3\">do? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, their main job is to keep it from the Muggles that there’s still witches an’ wizards up an’ down the country.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Why? </i> Blimey, Harry, everyone’d be wantin’ magic solutions to their problems. Nah, we’re best left alone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At this moment the boat bumped gently into the harbour wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid folded up his newspaper and they clambered up the stone steps on to the street. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>52 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Passers-by stared a lot at Hagrid as they walked through the little town to the station. Harry couldn’t blame them. Not only was Hagrid twice as tall as anyone else, he kept pointing at perfectly ordinary things like parking meters and saying loudly, ‘See that, Harry? Things these Muggles dream up, eh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid,’ said Harry, panting a bit as he ran to keep up, ‘did you say there are  <i class=\"calibre3\">dragons</i> at Gringotts?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, so they say,’ said Hagrid. ‘Crikey, I’d like a dragon.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d  <i class=\"calibre3\">like</i> one?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wanted one ever since I was a kid – here we go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had reached the station. There was a train to London in five minutes’ time. Hagrid, who didn’t understand ‘Muggle money’, as he called it, gave the notes to Harry so he could buy their tickets. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">People stared more than ever on the train. Hagrid took up two seats and sat knitting what looked like a canary-yellow circus tent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Still got yer letter, Harry?’ he asked as he counted stitches. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took the parchment envelope out of his pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good,’ said Hagrid. ‘There’s a list there of everything yeh need.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry unfolded a second piece of paper he hadn’t noticed the night before and read: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">HOGWARTS SCHOOL OF WITCHCRAFT AND WIZARDRY </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uniform </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">First-year students will require:</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">1. Three sets of plain work robes (black)</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">2. One plain pointed hat (black) for day wear</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">3. One pair of protective gloves (dragon hide or similar)</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">4. One winter cloak (black, silver fastenings)</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Please note that all pupils’ clothes should carry name tags</i> Set Books </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">All students should have a copy of each of the following:</i> The Standard Book of Spells (Grade 1)  <i class=\"calibre3\">by Miranda Goshawk</i> A History of Magic  <i class=\"calibre3\">by Bathilda Bagshot</i> Magical Theory  <i class=\"calibre3\">by Adalbert Waffling</i> A Beginner’s Guide to Transfiguration  <i class=\"calibre3\">by Emeric Switch</i> One Thousand Magical Herbs and Fungi  <i class=\"calibre3\">by Phyllida Spore</i> Magical Drafts and Potions  <i class=\"calibre3\">by Arsenius Jigger</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Diagon Alley 53 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them  <i class=\"calibre3\">by Newt Scamander</i> The Dark Forces: A Guide to Self-Protection  <i class=\"calibre3\">by Quentin Trimble</i> Other Equipment </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">1 wand</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">1 cauldron (pewter, standard size 2)</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">1 set glass or crystal phials </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">1 telescope </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">1 set brass scales</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Students may also bring an owl OR a cat OR a toad</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">PARENTS ARE REMINDED THAT FIRST-YEARS ARE NOT </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">ALLOWED THEIR OWN BROOMSTICKS</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can we buy all this in London?’ Harry wondered aloud. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If yeh know where to go,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had never been to London before. Although Hagrid seemed to know where he was going, he was obviously not used to getting there in an ordinary way. He got stuck in the ticket barrier on the Underground and complained loudly that the seats were too small and the trains too slow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know how the Muggles manage without magic,’ he said, as they climbed a broken-down escalator which led up to a bustling road lined with shops. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was so huge that he parted the crowd easily; all Harry had to do was keep close behind him. They passed book shops and music stores, hamburger bars and cinemas, but nowhere that looked as if it could sell you a magic wand. This was just an ordinary street full of ordinary people. Could there really be piles of wizard gold buried miles beneath them? Were there really shops that sold spell books and broomsticks? Might this not all be some huge joke that the Dursleys had cooked up? If Harry hadn’t known that the Dursleys had no sense of humour, he might have thought so; yet somehow, even though everything Hagrid had told him so far was unbelievable, Harry couldn’t help trusting him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is it,’ said Hagrid, coming to a halt, ‘the Leaky Cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It’s a famous place.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a tiny, grubby-looking pub. If Hagrid hadn’t pointed it </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>54 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">out, Harry wouldn’t have noticed it was there. The people hurrying by didn’t glance at it. Their eyes slid from the big book shop on one side to the record shop on the other as if they couldn’t see the Leaky Cauldron at all. In fact, Harry had the most peculiar feeling that only he and Hagrid could see it. Before he could mention this, Hagrid had steered him inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a famous place, it was very dark and shabby. A few old women were sitting in a corner, drinking tiny glasses of sherry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One of them was smoking a long pipe. A little man in a top hat was talking to the old barman, who was quite bald and looked like a gummy walnut. The low buzz of chatter stopped when they walked in. Everyone seemed to know Hagrid; they waved and smiled at him, and the barman reached for a glass, saying, ‘The usual, Hagrid?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t, Tom, I’m on Hogwarts business,’ said Hagrid, clapping his great hand on Harry’s shoulder and making Harry’s knees buckle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good Lord,’ said the barman, peering at Harry, ‘is this – can this be –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Leaky Cauldron had suddenly gone completely still and silent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bless my soul,’ whispered the old barman. ‘Harry Potter … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">what an honour.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He hurried out from behind the bar, rushed towards Harry and seized his hand, tears in his eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Welcome back, Mr Potter, welcome back.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry  didn’t  know  what  to  say.  Everyone  was  looking  at  him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The old woman with the pipe was puffing on it without realising it had gone out. Hagrid was beaming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then there was a great scraping of chairs and, next moment, Harry found himself shaking hands with everyone in the Leaky Cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Doris Crockford, Mr Potter, can’t believe I’m meeting you at last.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So proud, Mr Potter, I’m just so proud.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Always wanted to shake your hand – I’m all of a flutter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Delighted, Mr Potter, just can’t tell you. Diggle’s the name, Dedalus Diggle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve seen you before!’ said Harry, as Dedalus Diggle’s top hat fell off in his excitement. ‘You bowed to me once in a shop.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Diagon Alley 55 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He remembers!’ cried Dedalus Diggle, looking around at everyone. ‘Did you hear that? He remembers me!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shook hands again and again – Doris Crockford kept coming back for more. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A pale young man made his way forward, very nervously. One of his eyes was twitching. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Quirrell!’ said Hagrid. ‘Harry, Professor Quirrell will be one of your teachers at Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘P-P-Potter,’ stammered Professor Quirrell, grasping Harry’s hand, ‘c-can’t t-tell you how p-pleased I am to meet you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What sort of magic do you teach, Professor Quirrell?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D-Defence Against the D-D-Dark Arts,’ muttered Professor Quirrell, as though he’d rather not think about it. ‘N-not that you n-need it, eh, P-P-Potter?’ He laughed nervously. ‘You’ll be g-getting all your equipment, I suppose? I’ve g-got to p-pick up a new b-book on vampires, m-myself.’ He looked terrified at the very thought. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the others wouldn’t let Professor Quirrell keep Harry to himself. It took almost ten minutes to get away from them all. At last, Hagrid managed to make himself heard over the babble. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Must get on – lots ter buy. Come on, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Doris Crockford shook Harry’s hand one last time and Hagrid led them through the bar and out into a small, walled courtyard, where there was nothing but a dustbin and a few weeds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid grinned at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Told yeh, didn’t I? Told yeh you was famous. Even Professor Quirrell was tremblin’ ter meet yeh – mind you, he’s usually tremblin’.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is he always that nervous?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yeah. Poor bloke. Brilliant mind. He was fine while he was studyin’ outta books but then he took a year off ter get some first-hand experience … They say he met vampires in the Black Forest and there was a nasty bit o’ trouble with a hag – never been the same since. Scared of the students, scared of his own subject – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">now, where’s me umbrella?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Vampires? Hags? Harry’s head was swimming. Hagrid, meanwhile, was counting bricks in the wall above the dustbin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Three up … two across …’ he muttered. ‘Right, stand back, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He tapped the wall three times with the point of his umbrella. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The brick he had touched quivered – it wriggled – in the middle, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>56 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">a small hole appeared – it grew wider and wider – a second later they were facing an archway large enough even for Hagrid, an archway on to a cobbled street which twisted and turned out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Welcome,’ said Hagrid, ‘to Diagon Alley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He grinned at Harry’s amazement. They stepped through the archway. Harry looked quickly over his shoulder and saw the archway shrink instantly back into solid wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The sun shone brightly on a stack of cauldrons outside the nearest shop.  <i class=\"calibre3\">Cauldrons – All Sizes – Copper, Brass, Pewter, Silver – </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Self-Stirring – Collapsible</i> said a sign hanging over them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, you’ll be needin’ one,’ said Hagrid, ‘but we gotta get yer money first.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wished he had about eight more eyes. He turned his head in every direction as they walked up the street, trying to look at everything at once: the shops, the things outside them, the people doing their shopping. A plump woman outside an apothecary’s was shaking her head as they passed, saying, ‘Dragon liver, sixteen Sickles an ounce, they’re mad …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A low, soft hooting came from a dark shop with a sign saying <i class=\"calibre3\">Eeylops Owl Emporium – Tawny, Screech, Barn, Brown and Snowy. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Several boys of about Harry’s age had their noses pressed against a window with broomsticks in it. ‘Look,’ Harry heard one of them say, ‘the new Nimbus Two Thousand – fastest ever –’ There were shops selling robes, shops selling telescopes and strange silver instruments Harry had never seen before, windows stacked with barrels of bat spleens and eels’ eyes, tottering piles of spell books, quills and rolls of parchment, potion bottles, globes of the moon … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gringotts,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had reached a snowy-white building which towered over the other little shops. Standing beside its burnished bronze doors, wearing a uniform of scarlet and gold, was – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, that’s a goblin,’ said Hagrid quietly as they walked up the white stone steps towards him. The goblin was about a head shorter than Harry. He had a swarthy, clever face, a pointed beard and, Harry noticed, very long fingers and feet. He bowed as they walked inside. Now they were facing a second pair of doors, silver this time, with words engraved upon them: <i class=\"calibre3\">Enter, stranger, but take heed </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Of what awaits the sin of greed, </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Diagon Alley 57 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">For those who take, but do not earn,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Must pay most dearly in their turn,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">So if you seek beneath our floors</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">A treasure that was never yours, </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Thief, you have been warned, beware</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Of finding more than treasure there. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Like I said, yeh’d be mad ter try an’ rob it,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A pair of goblins bowed them through the silver doors and they were in a vast marble hall. About a hundred more goblins were sitting on high stools behind a long counter, scribbling in large ledgers, weighing coins on brass scales, examining precious stones through eyeglasses. There were too many doors to count leading off the hall, and yet more goblins were showing people in and out of these. Hagrid and Harry made for the counter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Morning,’ said Hagrid to a free goblin. ‘We’ve come ter take some money outta Mr Harry Potter’s safe.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You have his key, sir?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Got it here somewhere,’ said Hagrid and he started emptying his pockets on to the counter, scattering a handful of mouldy dog-biscuits over the goblin’s book of numbers. The goblin wrinkled his nose. Harry watched the goblin on their right weighing a pile of rubies as big as glowing coals. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Got it,’ said Hagrid at last, holding up a tiny golden key. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The goblin looked at it closely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That seems to be in order.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An’ I’ve also got a letter here from Professor Dumbledore,’ said Hagrid importantly, throwing out his chest. ‘It’s about the You-Know-What in vault seven hundred and thirteen.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The goblin read the letter carefully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very well,’ he said, handing it back to Hagrid, ‘I will have someone take you down to both vaults. Griphook!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Griphook was yet another goblin. Once Hagrid had crammed all the dog-biscuits back inside his pockets, he and Harry followed Griphook towards one of the doors leading off the hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the You-Know-What in vault seven hundred and thirteen?’ Harry asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t tell yeh that,’ said Hagrid mysteriously. ‘Very secret. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hogwarts business. Dumbledore’s trusted me. More’n my job’s worth ter tell yeh that.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>58 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Griphook held the door open for them. Harry, who had expected more marble, was surprised. They were in a narrow stone passageway lit with flaming torches. It sloped steeply downwards and there were little railway tracks on the floor. Griphook whistled and a small cart came hurtling up the tracks towards them. They climbed in – Hagrid with some difficulty – and were off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At first they just hurtled through a maze of twisting passages. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to remember, left, right, right, left, middle fork, right, left, but it was impossible. The rattling cart seemed to know its own way, because Griphook wasn’t steering. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s eyes stung as the cold air rushed past them, but he kept them wide open. Once, he thought he saw a burst of fire at the end of a passage and twisted around to see if it was a dragon, but too late </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– they plunged even deeper, passing an underground lake where huge stalactites and stalagmites grew from the ceiling and floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I never know,’ Harry called to Hagrid over the noise of the cart, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘what’s the difference between a stalagmite and a stalactite?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stalagmite’s got an “m” in it,’ said Hagrid. ‘An’ don’ ask me questions just now, I think I’m gonna be sick.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He did look very green and when the cart stopped at last beside a small door in the passage wall, Hagrid got out and had to lean against the wall to stop his knees trembling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Griphook unlocked the door. A lot of green smoke came billowing out, and as it cleared, Harry gasped. Inside were mounds of gold coins. Columns of silver. Heaps of little bronze Knuts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All yours,’ smiled Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All Harry’s – it was incredible. The Dursleys couldn’t have known about this or they’d have had it from him faster than blinking. How often had they complained how much Harry cost them to keep? And all the time there had been a small fortune belonging to him, buried deep under London. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid helped Harry pile some of it into a bag. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The gold ones are Galleons,’ he explained. ‘Seventeen silver Sickles to a Galleon and twenty-nine Knuts to a Sickle, it’s easy enough. Right, that should be enough fer a couple o’ terms, we’ll keep  the  rest  safe  for  yeh.’  He  turned  to  Griphook.  ‘Vault  seven hundred and thirteen now, please, and can we go more slowly?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘One speed only,’ said Griphook. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were going even deeper now and gathering speed. The air became colder and colder as they hurtled round tight corners. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Diagon Alley 59 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They went rattling over an underground ravine and Harry leant over the side to try and see what was down at the dark bottom but Hagrid groaned and pulled him back by the scruff of his neck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Vault seven hundred and thirteen had no keyhole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stand back,’ said Griphook importantly. He stroked the door gently with one of his long fingers and it simply melted away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If anyone but a Gringotts goblin tried that, they’d be sucked through the door and trapped in there,’ said Griphook. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How often do you check to see if anyone’s inside?’ Harry asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘About once every ten years,’ said Griphook, with a rather nasty grin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something really extraordinary had to be inside this top-security vault, Harry was sure, and he leant forward eagerly, expecting to see fabulous jewels at the very least – but at first he thought it was empty. Then he noticed a grubby little package wrapped up in brown paper lying on the floor. Hagrid picked it up and tucked it deep inside his coat. Harry longed to know what it was, but knew better than to ask. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, back in this infernal cart, and don’t talk to me on the way back, it’s best if I keep me mouth shut,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One wild cart-ride later they stood blinking in the sunlight outside Gringotts. Harry didn’t know where to run first now that he had a bag full of money. He didn’t have to know how many Galleons there were to a pound to know that he was holding more money than he’d had in his whole life – more money than even Dudley had ever had. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Might as well get yer uniform,’ said Hagrid, nodding towards <i class=\"calibre3\">Madam Malkin’s Robes for All Occasions. </i> ‘Listen, Harry, would yeh mind if I slipped off fer a pick-me-up in the Leaky Cauldron? I hate them Gringotts carts.’ He did still look a bit sick, so Harry entered Madam Malkin’s shop alone, feeling nervous. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Malkin was a squat, smiling witch dressed all in mauve. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hogwarts, dear?’ she said, when Harry started to speak. ‘Got the lot here – another young man being fitted up just now, in fact.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In the back of the shop, a boy with a pale, pointed face was standing on a footstool while a second witch pinned up his long black robes. Madam Malkin stood Harry on a stool next to him, slipped a long robe over his head and began to pin it to the right length. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>60 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hullo,’ said the boy, ‘Hogwarts too?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My father’s next door buying my books and mother’s up the street looking at wands,’ said the boy. He had a bored, drawling voice. ‘Then I’m going to drag them off to look at racing brooms. I don’t see why first-years can’t have their own. I think I’ll bully father into getting me one and I’ll smuggle it in somehow.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was strongly reminded of Dudley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have  <i class=\"calibre3\">you</i> got your own broom?’ the boy went on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Play Quidditch at all?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ Harry said again, wondering what on earth Quidditch could be. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">I</i> do – Father says it’s a crime if I’m not picked to play for my house, and I must say, I agree. Know what house you’ll be in yet?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry, feeling more stupid by the minute. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, no one really knows until they get there, do they, but I know I’ll be in Slytherin, all our family have been – imagine being in Hufflepuff, I think I’d leave, wouldn’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mmm,’ said Harry, wishing he could say something a bit more interesting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I  say,  look  at  that  man!’  said  the  boy  suddenly,  nodding towards the front window. Hagrid was standing there, grinning at Harry and pointing at two large ice-creams to show he couldn’t come in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s Hagrid,’ said Harry, pleased to know something the boy didn’t. ‘He works at Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ said the boy, ‘I’ve heard of him. He’s a sort of servant, isn’t he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s the gamekeeper,’ said Harry. He was liking the boy less and less every second. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, exactly. I heard he’s a sort of  <i class=\"calibre3\">savage</i> – lives in a hut in the school grounds and every now and then he gets drunk, tries to do magic and ends up setting fire to his bed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think he’s brilliant,’ said Harry coldly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Do</i> you?’ said the boy, with a slight sneer. ‘Why is he with you? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Where are your parents?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re dead,’ said Harry shortly. He didn’t feel much like going into the matter with this boy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, sorry,’ said the other, not sounding sorry at all. ‘But they </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Diagon Alley 61 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">were  <i class=\"calibre3\">our</i> kind, weren’t they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They were a witch and wizard, if that’s what you mean.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I really don’t think they should let the other sort in, do you? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They’re just not the same, they’ve never been brought up to know our ways. Some of them have never even heard of Hogwarts until they get the letter, imagine. I think they should keep it in the old wizarding families. What’s your surname, anyway?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But before Harry could answer, Madam Malkin said, ‘That’s you done, my dear,’ and Harry, not sorry for an excuse to stop talking to the boy, hopped down from the footstool. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I’ll see you at Hogwarts, I suppose,’ said the drawling boy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was rather quiet as he ate the ice-cream Hagrid had bought him (chocolate and raspberry with chopped nuts). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s up?’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing,’ Harry lied. They stopped to buy parchment and quills. Harry cheered up a bit when he found a bottle of ink that changed colour as you wrote. When they had left the shop, he said, ‘Hagrid, what’s Quidditch?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Blimey, Harry, I keep forgettin’ how little yeh know – not knowin’ about Quidditch!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t make me feel worse,’ said Harry. He told Hagrid about the pale boy in Madam Malkin’s. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– and he said people from Muggle families shouldn’t even be allowed in –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yer not  <i class=\"calibre3\">from</i> a Muggle family. If he’d known who yeh  <i class=\"calibre3\">were</i> – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he’s grown up knowin’ yer name if his parents are wizardin’ folk – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you saw ’em in the Leaky Cauldron. Anyway, what does he know about it, some o’ the best I ever saw were the only ones with magic in ’em in a long line o’ Muggles – look at yer mum! Look what she had fer a sister!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So what  <i class=\"calibre3\">is</i> Quidditch?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s our sport. Wizard sport. It’s like – like football in the Muggle world – everyone follows Quidditch – played up in the air on broomsticks and there’s four balls – sorta hard ter explain the rules.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what are Slytherin and Hufflepuff?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘School houses. There’s four. Everyone says Hufflepuff are a lot o’ duffers, but –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I bet I’m in Hufflepuff,’ said Harry gloomily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Better Hufflepuff than Slytherin,’ said Hagrid darkly. ‘There’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>62 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">not a single witch or wizard who went bad who wasn’t in Slytherin. You-Know-Who was one.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Vol– sorry – You-Know-Who was at Hogwarts?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Years an’ years ago,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They bought Harry’s school books in a shop called Flourish and Blotts where the shelves were stacked to the ceiling with books as large as paving stones bound in leather; books the size of postage stamps in covers of silk; books full of peculiar symbols and a few books with nothing in them at all. Even Dudley, who never read anything, would have been wild to get his hands on some of these. Hagrid almost had to drag Harry away from  <i class=\"calibre3\">Curses and</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Counter-Curses  </i>( <i class=\"calibre3\">Bewitch your Friends and Befuddle your Enemies</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">with the Latest Revenges: Hair Loss, Jelly-Legs, Tongue-Tying and</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">much, much more</i>) by Professor Vindictus Viridian. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I was trying to find out how to curse Dudley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not sayin’ that’s not a good idea, but yer not ter use magic in the Muggle world except in very special circumstances,’ said Hagrid. ‘An’ anyway, yeh couldn’ work any of them curses yet, yeh’ll need a lot more study before yeh get ter that level.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid wouldn’t let Harry buy a solid gold cauldron, either (‘It says pewter on yer list’), but they got a nice set of scales for weighing potion ingredients and a collapsible brass telescope. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then they visited the apothecary’s, which was fascinating enough to make up for its horrible smell, a mixture of bad eggs and rotted cabbages. Barrels of slimy stuff stood on the floor, jars of herbs, dried roots and bright powders lined the walls, bundles of feathers, strings of fangs and snarled claws hung from the ceiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">While Hagrid asked the man behind the counter for a supply of some basic potion ingredients for Harry, Harry himself examined silver unicorn horns at twenty-one Galleons each and minuscule, glittery black beetle eyes (five Knuts a scoop). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Outside the apothecary’s, Hagrid checked Harry’s list again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just yer wand left – oh yeah, an’ I still haven’t got yeh a birthday present.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt himself go red. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t have to –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know I don’t have to. Tell yeh what, I’ll get yer animal. Not a toad, toads went outta fashion years ago, yeh’d be laughed at – an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I don’ like cats, they make me sneeze. I’ll get yer an owl. All the kids want owls, they’re dead useful, carry yer post an’ everythin’.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Diagon Alley 63 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Twenty minutes later, they left Eeylops Owl Emporium, which had been dark and full of rustling and flickering, jewel-bright eyes. Harry now carried a large cage which held a beautiful snowy owl, fast asleep with her head under her wing. He couldn’t stop stammering his thanks, sounding just like Professor Quirrell. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’ mention it,’ said Hagrid gruffly. ‘Don’ expect you’ve had a lotta presents from them Dursleys. Just Ollivanders left now –  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">only place fer wands, Ollivanders, and yeh gotta have the best wand.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A magic wand … this was what Harry had been really looking forward to. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The last shop was narrow and shabby. Peeling gold letters over the door read  <i class=\"calibre3\">Ollivanders: Makers of Fine Wands since 382 BC. </i> A single wand lay on a faded purple cushion in the dusty window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A tinkling bell rang somewhere in the depths of the shop as they stepped inside. It was a tiny place, empty except for a single spindly chair which Hagrid sat on to wait. Harry felt strangely as though he had entered a very strict library; he swallowed a lot of new questions which had just occurred to him and looked instead at the thousands of narrow boxes piled neatly right up to the ceiling. For some reason, the back of his neck prickled. The very dust and silence in here seemed to tingle with some secret magic. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good afternoon,’ said a soft voice. Harry jumped. Hagrid must have jumped, too, because there was a loud crunching noise and he got quickly off the spindly chair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">An old man was standing before them, his wide, pale eyes shining like moons through the gloom of the shop. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello,’ said Harry awkwardly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah yes,’ said the man. ‘Yes, yes. I thought I’d be seeing you soon. Harry Potter.’ It wasn’t a question. ‘You have your mother’s eyes. It seems only yesterday she was in here herself, buying her first wand. Ten and a quarter inches long, swishy, made of willow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nice wand for charm work.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Ollivander moved closer to Harry. Harry wished he would blink. Those silvery eyes were a bit creepy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your father, on the other hand, favoured a mahogany wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Eleven inches. Pliable. A little more power and excellent for transfiguration. Well, I say your father favoured it – it’s really the wand that chooses the wizard, of course.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Ollivander had come so close that he and Harry were  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>64 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">almost nose to nose. Harry could see himself reflected in those misty eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And that’s where …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Ollivander touched the lightning scar on Harry’s forehead with a long, white finger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sorry to say I sold the wand that did it,’ he said softly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thirteen and a half inches. Yew. Powerful wand, very powerful, and in the wrong hands … Well, if I’d known what that wand was going out into the world to do …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He shook his head and then, to Harry’s relief, spotted Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rubeus! Rubeus Hagrid! How nice to see you again … Oak, sixteen inches, rather bendy, wasn’t it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was, sir, yes,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good wand, that one. But I suppose they snapped it in half when you got expelled?’ said Mr Ollivander, suddenly stern. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – yes, they did, yes,’ said Hagrid, shuffling his feet. ‘I’ve still got the pieces, though,’ he added brightly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you don’t  <i class=\"calibre3\">use</i> them?’ said Mr Ollivander sharply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, no, sir,’ said Hagrid quickly. Harry noticed he gripped his pink umbrella very tightly as he spoke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hmmm,’ said Mr Ollivander, giving Hagrid a piercing look. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, now – Mr Potter. Let me see.’ He pulled a long tape measure with silver markings out of his pocket. ‘Which is your wand arm?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – well, I’m right-handed,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hold out your arm. That’s it.’ He measured Harry from shoulder to finger, then wrist to elbow, shoulder to floor, knee to armpit and round his head. As he measured, he said, ‘Every Ollivander wand has a core of a powerful magical substance, Mr Potter. We use unicorn hairs, phoenix tail feathers and the heartstrings of dragons. No two Ollivander wands are the same, just as no two unicorns, dragons or phoenixes are quite the same. And of course, you will never get such good results with another wizard’s wand.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry suddenly realised that the tape measure, which was measuring between his nostrils, was doing this on its own. Mr Ollivander was flitting around the shelves, taking down boxes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That will do,’ he said, and the tape measure crumpled into a heap on the floor. ‘Right then, Mr Potter. Try this one. Beechwood and dragon heartstring. Nine inches. Nice and flexible. Just take it and give it a wave.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took the wand and (feeling foolish) waved it around a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Diagon Alley 65 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">bit, but Mr Ollivander snatched it out of his hand almost at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maple and phoenix feather. Seven inches. Quite whippy. Try –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried – but he had hardly raised the wand when it, too, was snatched back by Mr Ollivander. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, no – here, ebony and unicorn hair, eight and a half inches, springy. Go on, go on, try it out.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried. And tried. He had no idea what Mr Ollivander was waiting for. The pile of tried wands was mounting higher and higher on the spindly chair, but the more wands Mr Ollivander pulled from the shelves, the happier he seemed to become. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tricky customer, eh? Not to worry, we’ll find the perfect match here somewhere – I wonder, now – yes, why not – unusual combi-nation – holly and phoenix feather, eleven inches, nice and supple.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took the wand. He felt a sudden warmth in his fingers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He raised the wand above his head, brought it swishing down through the dusty air and a stream of red and gold sparks shot from the end like a firework, throwing dancing spots of light on to the walls. Hagrid whooped and clapped and Mr Ollivander cried, ‘Oh, bravo! Yes, indeed, oh, very good. Well, well, well … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">how curious … how very curious …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He put Harry’s wand back into its box and wrapped it in brown paper, still muttering, ‘Curious … curious …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry,’ said Harry, ‘but  <i class=\"calibre3\">what’s</i> curious?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Ollivander fixed Harry with his pale stare. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I remember every wand I’ve ever sold, Mr Potter. Every single wand. It so happens that the phoenix whose tail feather is in your wand, gave another feather – just one other. It is very curious indeed that you should be destined for this wand when its brother </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– why, its brother gave you that scar.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry swallowed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, thirteen and a half inches. Yew. Curious indeed how these things happen. The wand chooses the wizard, remember … I think we must expect great things from you, Mr Potter … After all, He Who Must Not Be Named did great things – terrible, yes, but great.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shivered. He wasn’t sure he liked Mr Ollivander too much. He paid seven gold Galleons for his wand and Mr Ollivander bowed them from his shop. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The late-afternoon sun hung low in the sky as Harry and Hagrid made their way back down Diagon Alley, back through the wall, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>66 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">back through the Leaky Cauldron, now empty. Harry didn’t speak at all as they walked down the road; he didn’t even notice how much people were gawping at them on the Underground, laden as they were with all their funny-shaped packages, with the sleeping snowy owl on Harry’s lap. Up another escalator, out into Paddington station; Harry only realised where they were when Hagrid tapped him on the shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Got time fer a bite to eat before yer train leaves,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He bought Harry a hamburger and they sat down on plastic seats to eat them. Harry kept looking around. Everything looked so strange, somehow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You all right, Harry? Yer very quiet,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wasn’t sure he could explain. He’d just had the best birthday of his life – and yet – he chewed his hamburger, trying to find the words. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone thinks I’m special,’ he said at last. ‘All those people in the Leaky Cauldron, Professor Quirrell, Mr Ollivander … but I don’t know anything about magic at all. How can they expect great things? I’m famous and I can’t even remember what I’m famous  for.  I  don’t  know  what  happened  when  Vol–  sorry  –  I mean, the night my parents died.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid leant across the table. Behind the wild beard and eyebrows he wore a very kind smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’ you worry, Harry. You’ll learn fast enough. Everyone starts at the beginning at Hogwarts, you’ll be just fine. Just be yerself. I know it’s hard. Yeh’ve been singled out, an’ that’s always hard. But yeh’ll have a great time at Hogwarts – I did – still do, ’smatter of fact.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid helped Harry on to the train that would take him back to the Dursleys, then handed him an envelope. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yer ticket fer Hogwarts,’ he said. ‘First o’ September – King’s Cross – it’s all on yer ticket. Any problems with the Dursleys, send me a letter with yer owl, she’ll know where to find me … See yeh soon, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The train pulled out of the station. Harry wanted to watch Hagrid until he was out of sight; he rose in his seat and pressed his nose against the window, but he blinked and Hagrid had gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER SIX — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Journey from Platform </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Nine and Three-Quarters </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s last month with the Dursleys wasn’t fun. True, Dudley was now so scared of Harry he wouldn’t stay in the same room, while Aunt Petunia and Uncle Vernon didn’t shut Harry in his cupboard, force him to do anything or shout at him – in fact, they didn’t speak to him at all. Half-terrified, half-furious, they acted as though any chair with Harry in it was empty. Although this was an improvement in many ways, it did become a bit depressing after a while. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry kept to his room, with his new owl for company. He had decided to call her Hedwig, a name he had found in  <i class=\"calibre3\">A History of</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Magic. </i> His school books were very interesting. He lay on his bed reading late into the night, Hedwig swooping in and out of the open window as she pleased. It was lucky that Aunt Petunia didn’t come in to hoover any more, because Hedwig kept bringing back dead mice. Every night before he went to sleep, Harry ticked off another day on the piece of paper he had pinned to the wall, counting down to September the first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On  the  last  day  of  August  he  thought he’d better speak to his aunt and uncle about getting to King’s Cross station next day, so he went down to the living-room, where they were watching a quiz show on television. He cleared his throat to let them know he was there, and Dudley screamed and ran from the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – Uncle Vernon?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon grunted to show he was listening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – I need to be at King’s Cross tomorrow to – to go to Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon grunted again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Would it be all right if you gave me a lift?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>68 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Grunt. Harry supposed that meant yes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was about to go back upstairs when Uncle Vernon actually spoke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Funny way to get to a wizards’ school, the train. Magic carpets all got punctures, have they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t say anything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is this school, anyway?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know,’ said Harry, realising this for the first time. He pulled the ticket Hagrid had given him out of his pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I just take the train from platform nine and three-quarters at eleven o’clock,’ he read. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His aunt and uncle stared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Platform what?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nine and three-quarters.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t talk rubbish,’ said Uncle Vernon, ‘there is no platform nine and three-quarters.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s on my ticket.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Barking,’ said Uncle Vernon, ‘howling mad, the lot of them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You’ll see. You just wait. All right, we’ll take you to King’s Cross. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">We’re going up to London tomorrow anyway, or I wouldn’t bother.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why are you going to London?’ Harry asked, trying to keep things friendly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Taking Dudley to hospital,’ growled Uncle Vernon. ‘Got to have that ruddy tail removed before he goes to Smeltings.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry woke at five o’clock the next morning and was too excited and  nervous  to  go  back  to  sleep.  He  got  up  and  pulled  on  his jeans because he didn’t want to walk into the station in his wizard’s robes – he’d change on the train. He checked his Hogwarts list yet again to make sure he had everything he needed, saw that Hedwig was shut safely in her cage and then paced the room, waiting for the Dursleys to get up. Two hours later, Harry’s huge, heavy trunk had been loaded into the Dursleys’ car, Aunt Petunia had talked Dudley into sitting next to Harry and they had set off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They reached King’s Cross at half past ten. Uncle Vernon dumped Harry’s trunk on to a trolley and wheeled it into the station for him. Harry thought this was strangely kind until Uncle Vernon stopped dead, facing the platforms with a nasty grin on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Journey from Platform Nine and Three-Quarters 69 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, there you are, boy. Platform nine – platform ten. Your platform should be somewhere in the middle, but they don’t seem to have built it yet, do they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was quite right, of course. There was a big plastic number nine over one platform and a big plastic number ten over the one next to it, and in the middle, nothing at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have a good term,’ said Uncle Vernon with an even nastier smile. He left without another word. Harry turned and saw the Dursleys drive away. All three of them were laughing. Harry’s mouth went rather dry. What on earth was he going to do? He was starting to attract a lot of funny looks, because of Hedwig. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He’d have to ask someone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stopped a passing guard, but didn’t dare mention platform nine and three-quarters. The guard had never heard of Hogwarts and when Harry couldn’t even tell him what part of the country it was in, he started to get annoyed, as though Harry was being stupid on purpose. Getting desperate, Harry asked for the train that left at eleven o’clock, but the guard said there wasn’t one. In the end the guard strode away, muttering about time-wasters. Harry was now trying hard not to panic. According to the large clock over the arrivals board, he had ten minutes left to get on the train to Hogwarts and he had no idea how to do it; he was stranded in the middle of a station with a trunk he could hardly lift, a pocket full of wizard money and a large owl. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid must have forgotten to tell him something you had to do, like tapping the third brick on the left to get into Diagon Alley. He wondered if he should get out his wand and start tapping the ticket box between platforms nine and ten. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment a group of people passed just behind him and he caught a few words of what they were saying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– packed with Muggles, of course –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry swung round. The speaker was a plump woman who was talking to four boys, all with flaming red hair. Each of them was pushing a trunk like Harry’s in front of him – and they had an <i class=\"calibre3\">owl. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Heart hammering, Harry pushed his trolley after them. They stopped and so did he, just near enough to hear what they were saying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, what’s the platform number?’ said the boys’ mother. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nine and three-quarters!’ piped a small girl, also red-headed, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>70 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">who was holding her hand. ‘Mum, can’t I go …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re not old enough, Ginny, now be quiet. All right, Percy, you go first.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What looked like the oldest boy marched towards platforms nine and ten. Harry watched, careful not to blink in case he missed it – but just as the boy reached the divide between the two platforms, a large crowd of tourists came swarming in front of him, and by the time the last rucksack had cleared away, the boy had vanished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fred, you next,’ the plump woman said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not Fred, I’m George,’ said the boy. ‘Honestly, woman, call yourself our mother? Can’t you  <i class=\"calibre3\">tell</i> I’m George?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry, George, dear.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Only joking, I am Fred,’ said the boy, and off he went. His twin called after him to hurry up, and he must have done, because a second later, he had gone – but how had he done it? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Now the third brother was walking briskly towards the ticket barrier – he was almost there – and then, quite suddenly, he wasn’t anywhere. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was nothing else for it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excuse me,’ Harry said to the plump woman. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hullo, dear,’ she said. ‘First time at Hogwarts? Ron’s new, too.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She pointed at the last and youngest of her sons. He was tall, thin and gangling, with freckles, big hands and feet and a long nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry. ‘The thing is – the thing is, I don’t know how to –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How to get on to the platform?’ she said kindly, and Harry nodded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not to worry,’ she said. ‘All you have to do is walk straight at the barrier between platforms nine and ten. Don’t stop and don’t be scared you’ll crash into it, that’s very important. Best do it at a bit of a run if you’re nervous. Go on, go now before Ron.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – OK,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pushed his trolley round and stared at the barrier. It looked very solid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He started to walk towards it. People jostled him on their way to platforms nine and ten. Harry walked more quickly. He was going to smash right into that ticket box and then he’d be in trouble – leaning forward on his trolley he broke into a heavy  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Journey from Platform Nine and Three-Quarters 71 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">run – the barrier was coming nearer and nearer – he wouldn’t be able to stop – the trolley was out of control – he was a foot away – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he closed his eyes ready for the crash – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It didn’t come … he kept on running … he opened his eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A scarlet steam engine was waiting next to a platform packed with people. A sign overhead said  <i class=\"calibre3\">Hogwarts Express, 11 o’clock. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked behind him and saw a wrought-iron archway where the ticket box had been, with the words  <i class=\"calibre3\">Platform Nine and Three-Quarters</i> on it. He had done it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Smoke from the engine drifted over the heads of the chattering crowd, while cats of every colour wound here and there between their legs. Owls hooted to each other in a disgruntled sort of way over the babble and the scraping of heavy trunks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The first few carriages were already packed with students, some hanging out of the window to talk to their families, some fighting over seats. Harry pushed his trolley off down the platform in search of an empty seat. He passed a round-faced boy who was saying, ‘Gran, I’ve lost my toad again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,  <i class=\"calibre3\">Neville</i>,’ he heard the old woman sigh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A boy with dreadlocks was surrounded by a small crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Give us a look, Lee, go on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The boy lifted the lid of a box in his arms and the people around him shrieked and yelled as something inside poked out a long, hairy leg. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pressed on through the crowd until he found an empty compartment near the end of the train. He put Hedwig inside first and then started to shove and heave his trunk towards the train door. He tried to lift it up the steps but could hardly raise one end and twice he dropped it painfully on his foot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Want a hand?’ It was one of the red-haired twins he’d followed through the ticket box. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, please,’ Harry panted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oy, Fred! C’mere and help!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With the twins’ help, Harry’s trunk was at last tucked away in a corner of the compartment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thanks,’ said Harry, pushing his sweaty hair out of his eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ said one of the twins suddenly, pointing at Harry’s lightning scar. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Blimey,’ said the other twin. ‘Are you –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He  <i class=\"calibre3\">is, </i>’ said the first twin. ‘Aren’t you?’ he added to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>72 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Harry Potter, </i>’ chorused the twins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, him,’ said Harry. ‘I mean, yes, I am.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The two boys gawped at him and Harry felt himself going red. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, to his relief, a voice came floating in through the train’s open door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fred? George? Are you there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Coming, Mum.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a last look at Harry, the twins hopped off the train. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat down next to the window where, half-hidden, he could watch the red-haired family on the platform and hear what they were saying. Their mother had just taken out her handkerchief. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron, you’ve got something on your nose.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The youngest boy tried to jerk out of the way, but she grabbed him and began rubbing the end of his nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Mum</i> – geroff.’ He wriggled free. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aaah, has ickle Ronnie got somefink on his nosie?’ said one of the twins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s Percy?’ said their mother. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s coming now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The oldest boy came striding into sight. He had already changed into his billowing black Hogwarts robes and Harry noticed a shiny red and gold badge on his chest with the letter  <i class=\"calibre3\">P</i> on it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t stay long, Mother,’ he said. ‘I’m up front, the Prefects have got two compartments to themselves –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, are you a  <i class=\"calibre3\">Prefect</i>, Percy?’ said one of the twins, with an air of  great  surprise.  ‘You  should  have  said  something,  we  had  no idea.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hang on, I think I remember him saying something about it,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said the other twin. ‘Once –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Or twice –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A minute –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All summer –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, shut up,’ said Percy the Prefect. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How come Percy gets new robes, anyway?’ said one of the twins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because he’s a  <i class=\"calibre3\">Prefect</i>,’ said their mother fondly. ‘All right, dear, well, have a good term – send me an owl when you get there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Journey from Platform Nine and Three-Quarters 73 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She kissed Percy on the cheek and he left. Then she turned to the twins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, you two – this year, you behave yourselves. If I get one more owl telling me you’ve – you’ve blown up a toilet or –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Blown up a toilet? We’ve never blown up a toilet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Great idea though, thanks, Mum.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s  <i class=\"calibre3\">not funny</i>. And look after Ron.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t worry, ickle Ronniekins is safe with us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up,’ said Ron again. He was almost as tall as the twins already and his nose was still pink where his mother had rubbed it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hey, Mum, guess what? Guess who we just met on the train?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry leant back quickly so they couldn’t see him looking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know that black-haired boy who was near us in the station? Know who he is?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Harry Potter! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry heard the little girl’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, Mum, can I go on the train and see him, Mum, oh please …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve already seen him, Ginny, and the poor boy isn’t something you goggle at in a zoo. Is he really, Fred? How do you know?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Asked him. Saw his scar. It’s really there – like lightning.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Poor  <i class=\"calibre3\">dear</i> – no wonder he was alone. I wondered. He was ever so polite when he asked how to get on to the platform.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Never mind that, do you think he remembers what You-Know-Who looks like?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Their mother suddenly became very stern. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I forbid you to ask him, Fred. No, don’t you dare. As though he needs reminding of that on his first day at school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, keep your hair on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A whistle sounded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hurry up!’ their mother said, and the three boys clambered on to the train. They leant out of the window for her to kiss them goodbye and their younger sister began to cry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t, Ginny, we’ll send you loads of owls.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll send you a Hogwarts toilet seat.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">George! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Only joking, Mum.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The train began to move. Harry saw the boys’ mother waving </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>74 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and their sister, half laughing, half crying, running to keep up with the train until it gathered too much speed; then she fell back and waved. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry watched the girl and her mother disappear as the train rounded the corner. Houses flashed past the window. Harry felt a great leap of excitement. He didn’t know what he was going to – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">but it had to be better than what he was leaving behind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door of the compartment slid open and the youngest red-headed boy came in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyone sitting there?’ he asked, pointing at the seat opposite Harry. ‘Everywhere else is full.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shook his head and the boy sat down. He glanced at Harry and then looked quickly out of the window, pretending he hadn’t looked. Harry saw he still had a black mark on his nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hey, Ron.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The twins were back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Listen, we’re going down the middle of the train – Lee Jordan’s got a giant tarantula down there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ mumbled Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ said the other twin, ‘did we introduce ourselves? Fred and George Weasley. And this is Ron, our brother. See you later, then.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bye,’ said Harry and Ron. The twins slid the compartment door shut behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you really Harry Potter?’ Ron blurted out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry nodded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – well, I thought it might be one of Fred and George’s jokes,’ said Ron. ‘And have you really got – you know …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pointed at Harry’s forehead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pulled back his fringe to show the lightning scar. Ron stared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So that’s where You-Know-Who –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry, ‘but I can’t remember it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing?’ said Ron eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – I remember a lot of green light, but nothing else.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wow,’ said Ron. He sat and stared at Harry for a few moments, then, as though he had suddenly realised what he was doing, he looked quickly out of the window again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are all your family wizards?’ asked Harry, who found Ron just as interesting as Ron found him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Journey from Platform Nine and Three-Quarters 75 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – yes, I think so,’ said Ron. ‘I think Mum’s got a second cousin who’s an accountant, but we never talk about him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So you must know loads of magic already.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Weasleys were clearly one of those old wizarding families the pale boy in Diagon Alley had talked about. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I heard you went to live with Muggles,’ said Ron. ‘What are they like?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Horrible – well, not all of them. My aunt and uncle and cousin are, though. Wish I’d had three wizard brothers.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Five,’ said Ron. For some reason, he was looking gloomy. ‘I’m the sixth in our family to go to Hogwarts. You could say I’ve got a lot to live up to. Bill and Charlie have already left – Bill was Head Boy and Charlie was captain of Quidditch. Now Percy’s a Prefect. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred and George mess around a lot, but they still get really good marks and everyone thinks they’re really funny. Everyone expects me to do as well as the others, but if I do, it’s no big deal, because they did it first. You never get anything new, either, with five brothers. I’ve got Bill’s old robes, Charlie’s old wand and Percy’s old rat.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron reached inside his jacket and pulled out a fat grey rat, which was asleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘His name’s Scabbers and he’s useless, he hardly ever wakes up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy got an owl from my dad for being made a Prefect, but they couldn’t aff– I mean, I got Scabbers instead.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s ears went pink. He seemed to think he’d said too much, because he went back to staring out of the window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t think there was anything wrong with not being able to afford an owl. After all, he’d never had any money in his life until a month ago, and he told Ron so, all about having to wear Dudley’s old clothes and never getting proper birthday presents. This seemed to cheer Ron up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… and until Hagrid told me, I didn’t know anything about being a wizard or about my parents or Voldemort –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">You said You-Know-Who’s name! </i>’ said Ron, sounding both shocked and impressed. ‘I’d have thought you, of all people –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not trying to be  <i class=\"calibre3\">brave</i> or anything, saying the name,’ said Harry. ‘I just never knew you shouldn’t. See what I mean? I’ve got loads to learn … I bet,’ he added, voicing for the first time </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>76 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">something that had been worrying him a lot lately, ‘I bet I’m the worst in the class.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You won’t be. There’s loads of people who come from Muggle families and they learn quick enough.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">While they had been talking, the train had carried them out of London. Now they were speeding past fields full of cows and sheep. They were quiet for a time, watching the fields and lanes flick past. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Around half past twelve there was a great clattering outside in the corridor and a smiling, dimpled woman slid back their door and said, ‘Anything off the trolley, dears?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who hadn’t had any breakfast, leapt to his feet, but Ron’s ears went pink again and he muttered that he’d brought sandwiches. Harry went out into the corridor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had never had any money for sweets with the Dursleys and now that he had pockets rattling with gold and silver he was ready to buy as many Mars Bars as he could carry – but the woman didn’t have Mars Bars. What she did have were Bertie Bott’s Every-Flavour Beans, Drooble’s Best Blowing Gum, Chocolate Frogs, Pumpkin Pasties, Cauldron Cakes, Liquorice Wands and a number of other strange things Harry had never seen in his life. Not wanting to miss anything, he got some of everything and paid the woman eleven silver Sickles and seven bronze Knuts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron stared as Harry brought it all back into the compartment and tipped it on to an empty seat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hungry, are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Starving,’ said Harry, taking a large bite out of a pumpkin pasty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had taken out a lumpy package and unwrapped it. There were four sandwiches in there. He pulled one of them apart and said, ‘She always forgets I don’t like corned beef.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Swap you for one of these,’ said Harry, holding up a pasty. ‘Go on –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t want this, it’s all dry,’ said Ron. ‘She hasn’t got much time,’ he added quickly, ‘you know, with five of us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go on, have a pasty,’ said Harry, who had never had anything to share before or, indeed, anyone to share it with. It was a nice feeling, sitting there with Ron, eating their way through all Harry’s pasties and cakes (the sandwiches lay forgotten). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are these?’ Harry asked Ron, holding up a pack of </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Journey from Platform Nine and Three-Quarters 77 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Chocolate Frogs. ‘They’re not  <i class=\"calibre3\">really</i> frogs, are they?’ He was starting to feel that nothing would surprise him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Ron. ‘But see what the card is, I’m missing Agrippa.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, of course, you wouldn’t know – Chocolate Frogs have cards inside them, you know, to collect – Famous Witches and Wizards. I’ve got about five hundred, but I haven’t got Agrippa or Ptolemy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry unwrapped his Chocolate Frog and picked up the card. It showed a man’s face. He wore half-moon glasses, had a long crooked nose and flowing silver hair, beard and moustache. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Underneath the picture was the name  <i class=\"calibre3\">Albus Dumbledore. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So  <i class=\"calibre3\">this</i> is Dumbledore!’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t tell me you’d never heard of Dumbledore!’ said Ron. ‘Can I have a frog? I might get Agrippa – thanks –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned over his card and read: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Albus Dumbledore, currently Headmaster of Hogwarts. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Considered by many the greatest wizard of modern</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">times, Professor Dumbledore is particularly famous for</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">his defeat of the dark wizard Grindelwald in 1945,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">for the discovery of the twelve uses of dragon’s</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">blood and his work on alchemy with his partner,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Nicolas Flamel. Professor Dumbledore enjoys</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">chamber music and tenpin bowling. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned the card back over and saw, to his astonishment, that Dumbledore’s face had disappeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s gone!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, you can’t expect him to hang around all day,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’ll be back. No, I’ve got Morgana again and I’ve got about six of her … do you want it? You can start collecting.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s eyes strayed to the pile of Chocolate Frogs waiting to be unwrapped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Help yourself,’ said Harry. ‘But in, you know, the Muggle world, people just stay put in photos.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do they? What, they don’t move at all?’ Ron sounded amazed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Weird! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared as Dumbledore sidled back into the picture on his card and gave him a small smile. Ron was more interested in </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>78 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">eating the frogs than looking at the Famous Witches and Wizards cards, but Harry couldn’t keep his eyes off them. Soon he had not only Dumbledore and Morgana, but Hengist of Woodcroft, Alberic Grunnion, Circe, Paracelsus and Merlin. He finally tore his eyes away from the druidess Cliodna, who was scratching her nose, to open a bag of Bertie Bott’s Every-Flavour Beans. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You want to be careful with those,’ Ron warned Harry. ‘When they say every flavour, they  <i class=\"calibre3\">mean</i> every flavour – you know, you get all the ordinary ones like chocolate and peppermint and marmalade, but then you can get spinach and liver and tripe. George reckons he had a bogey-flavoured one once.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron picked up a green bean, looked at it carefully and bit into a corner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bleaaargh – see? Sprouts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had a good time eating the Every-Flavour Beans. Harry got toast, coconut, baked bean, strawberry, curry, grass, coffee, sardine and was even brave enough to nibble the end off a funny grey one Ron wouldn’t touch, which turned out to be pepper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The countryside now flying past the window was becoming wilder. The neat fields had gone. Now there were woods, twisting rivers and dark green hills. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a knock on the door of their compartment and the round-faced boy Harry had passed on platform nine and three-quarters came in. He looked tearful. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry,’ he said, ‘but have you seen a toad at all?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When they shook their heads, he wailed, ‘I’ve lost him! He keeps getting away from me!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’ll turn up,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said the boy miserably. ‘Well, if you see him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t know why he’s so bothered,’ said Ron. ‘If I’d brought a toad I’d lose it as quick as I could. Mind you, I brought Scabbers, so I can’t talk.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rat was still snoozing on Ron’s lap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He might have died and you wouldn’t know the difference,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Ron in disgust. ‘I tried to turn him yellow yesterday to make him more interesting, but the spell didn’t work. I’ll show you, look …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He rummaged around in his trunk and pulled out a very battered-looking wand. It was chipped in places and something </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Journey from Platform Nine and Three-Quarters 79 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">white was glinting at the end. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Unicorn hair’s nearly poking out. Anyway –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had just raised his wand when the compartment door slid open again. The toadless boy was back, but this time he had a girl with him. She was already wearing her new Hogwarts robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Has anyone seen a toad? Neville’s lost one,’ she said. She had a bossy sort of voice, lots of bushy brown hair and rather large front teeth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve already told him we haven’t seen it,’ said Ron, but the girl wasn’t listening, she was looking at the wand in his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, are you doing magic? Let’s see it, then.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She sat down. Ron looked taken aback. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – all right.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He cleared his throat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sunshine, daisies, butter mellow, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Turn this stupid, fat rat yellow.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He waved his wand, but nothing happened. Scabbers stayed grey and fast asleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you sure that’s a real spell?’ said the girl. ‘Well, it’s not very good, is it? I’ve tried a few simple spells just for practice and it’s all worked for me. Nobody in my family’s magic at all, it was ever such a surprise when I got my letter, but I was ever so pleased, of course, I mean, it’s the very best school of witchcraft there is, I’ve heard – I’ve learnt all our set books off by heart, of course, I just hope it will be enough – I’m Hermione Granger, by the way, who are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She said all this very fast. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked at Ron and was relieved to see by his stunned face that he hadn’t learnt all the set books off by heart either. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m Ron Weasley,’ Ron muttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you really?’ said Hermione. ‘I know all about you, of course – I got a few extra books for background reading, and you’re in  <i class=\"calibre3\">Modern Magical History</i> and  <i class=\"calibre3\">The Rise and Fall of the Dark</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Arts</i> and  <i class=\"calibre3\">Great Wizarding Events of the Twentieth Century. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Am I?’ said Harry, feeling dazed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Goodness, didn’t you know, I’d have found out everything I could if it was me,’ said Hermione. ‘Do either of you know what house you’ll be in? I’ve been asking around and I hope I’m in Gryffindor, it sounds by far the best, I hear Dumbledore himself </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>80 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">was one, but I suppose Ravenclaw wouldn’t be too bad … Anyway, we’d better go and look for Neville’s toad. You two had better change, you know, I expect we’ll be there soon.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And she left, taking the toadless boy with her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Whatever house I’m in, I hope she’s not in it,’ said Ron. He threw his wand back into his trunk. ‘Stupid spell – George gave it to me, bet he knew it was a dud.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What house are your brothers in?’ asked Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gryffindor,’ said Ron. Gloom seemed to be settling on him again. ‘Mum and Dad were in it, too. I don’t know what they’ll say if I’m not. I don’t suppose Ravenclaw  <i class=\"calibre3\">would</i> be too bad, but imagine if they put me in Slytherin.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s the house Vol– I mean, You-Know-Who was in?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Ron. He flopped back into his seat, looking depressed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know, I think the ends of Scabbers’s whiskers are a bit lighter,’ said Harry, trying to take Ron’s mind off houses. ‘So what do your oldest brothers do now they’ve left, anyway?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was wondering what a wizard did once he’d finished school. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Charlie’s in Romania studying dragons and Bill’s in Africa doing something for Gringotts,’ said Ron. ‘Did you hear about Gringotts? It’s been all over the  <i class=\"calibre3\">Daily Prophet</i>, but I don’t suppose you get that with the Muggles – someone tried to rob a high-security vault.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Really? What happened to them?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing, that’s why it’s such big news. They haven’t been caught. My dad says it must’ve been a powerful Dark wizard to get round Gringotts, but they don’t think they took anything, that’s what’s odd. ’Course, everyone gets scared when something like this happens in case You-Know-Who’s behind it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned this news over in his mind. He was starting to get a prickle of fear every time You-Know-Who was mentioned. He supposed this was all part of entering the magical world, but it had been a lot more comfortable saying ‘Voldemort’ without worrying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s your Quidditch team?’ Ron asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – I don’t know any,’ Harry confessed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What!’ Ron looked dumbfounded. ‘Oh, you wait, it’s the best </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Journey from Platform Nine and Three-Quarters 81 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">game in the world –’ And he was off, explaining all about the four balls and the positions of the seven players, describing famous games he’d been to with his brothers and the broomstick he’d like to get if he had the money. He was just taking Harry through the finer points of the game when the compartment door slid open yet again, but it wasn’t Neville the toadless boy or Hermione Granger this time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Three boys entered and Harry recognised the middle one at once: it was the pale boy from Madam Malkin’s robe shop. He was looking at Harry with a lot more interest than he’d shown back in Diagon Alley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is it true?’ he said. ‘They’re saying all down the train that Harry Potter’s in this compartment. So it’s you, is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry. He was looking at the other boys. Both of them were thickset and looked extremely mean. Standing either side of the pale boy they looked like bodyguards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, this is Crabbe and this is Goyle,’ said the pale boy carelessly, noticing where Harry was looking. ‘And my name’s Malfoy, Draco Malfoy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron gave a slight cough, which might have been hiding a snigger. Draco Malfoy looked at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Think my name’s funny, do you? No need to ask who you are. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">My father told me all the Weasleys have red hair, freckles and more children than they can afford.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned back to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ll soon find out some wizarding families are much better than others, Potter. You don’t want to go making friends with the wrong sort. I can help you there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He held out his hand to shake Harry’s, but Harry didn’t take it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think I can tell who the wrong sort are for myself, thanks,’ he said coolly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Draco Malfoy didn’t go red, but a pink tinge appeared in his pale cheeks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’d be careful if I were you, Potter,’ he said slowly. ‘Unless you’re a bit politer you’ll go the same way as your parents. They didn’t know what was good for them, either. You hang around with riff-raff like the Weasleys and that Hagrid and it’ll rub off on you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Both Harry and Ron stood up. Ron’s face was as red as his hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Say that again,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>82 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, you’re going to fight us, are you?’ Malfoy sneered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Unless you get out now,’ said Harry, more bravely than he felt, because Crabbe and Goyle were a lot bigger than him or Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But we don’t feel like leaving, do we, boys? We’ve eaten all our food and you still seem to have some.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Goyle reached towards the Chocolate Frogs next to Ron – Ron leapt forward, but before he’d so much as touched Goyle, Goyle let out a horrible yell. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Scabbers the rat was hanging off his finger, sharp little teeth sunk deep into Goyle’s knuckle – Crabbe and Malfoy backed away as Goyle swung Scabbers round and round, howling, and when Scabbers finally flew off and hit the window, all three of them disappeared at once. Perhaps they thought there were more rats lurking among the sweets, or perhaps they’d heard footsteps, because a second later, Hermione Granger had come in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What   <i class=\"calibre3\">has</i> been going on?’ she said, looking at the sweets all over the floor and Ron picking up Scabbers by his tail. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think he’s been knocked out,’ Ron said to Harry. He looked closer at Scabbers. ‘No – I don’t believe it – he’s gone back to sleep.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And so he had. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve met Malfoy before?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry explained about their meeting in Diagon Alley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve heard of his family,’ said Ron darkly. ‘They were some of the first to come back to our side after You-Know-Who disappeared. Said they’d been bewitched. My dad doesn’t believe it. He says Malfoy’s father didn’t need an excuse to go over to the Dark Side.’ He turned to Hermione. ‘Can we help you with something?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d better hurry up and put your robes on, I’ve just been up the front to ask the driver and he says we’re nearly there. You haven’t been fighting, have you? You’ll be in trouble before we even get there!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scabbers has been fighting, not us,’ said Ron, scowling at her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Would you mind leaving while we change?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right – I only came in here because people outside are behaving very childishly, racing up and down the corridors,’ said Hermione in a sniffy voice. ‘And you’ve got dirt on your nose, by the way, did you know?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron glared at her as she left. Harry peered out of the window. It was getting dark. He could see mountains and forests under a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Journey from Platform Nine and Three-Quarters 83 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">deep-purple sky. The train did seem to be slowing down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He and Ron took off their jackets and pulled on their long black robes. Ron’s were a bit short for him, you could see his trainers underneath them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A voice echoed through the train: ‘We will be reaching Hogwarts in five minutes’ time. Please leave your luggage on the train, it will be taken to the school separately.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s stomach lurched with nerves and Ron, he saw, looked pale under his freckles. They crammed their pockets with the last of the sweets and joined the crowd thronging the corridor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The train slowed right down and finally stopped. People pushed their way towards the door and out on to a tiny, dark platform. Harry shivered in the cold night air. Then a lamp came bobbing over the heads of the students and Harry heard a familiar voice: ‘Firs’-years! Firs’-years over here! All right there, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s big hairy face beamed over the sea of heads. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon, follow me – any more firs’-years? Mind yer step, now! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Firs’-years follow me!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slipping and stumbling, they followed Hagrid down what seemed to be a steep, narrow path. It was so dark either side of them that Harry thought there must be thick trees there. Nobody spoke much. Neville, the boy who kept losing his toad, sniffed once or twice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh’ll get yer firs’ sight o’ Hogwarts in a sec,’ Hagrid called over his shoulder, ‘jus’ round this bend here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud ‘Oooooh!’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The narrow path had opened suddenly on to the edge of a great black lake. Perched atop a high mountain on the other side, its windows sparkling in the starry sky, was a vast castle with many turrets and towers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No more’n four to a boat!’ Hagrid called, pointing to a fleet of little boats sitting in the water by the shore. Harry and Ron were followed into their boat by Neville and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone in?’ shouted Hagrid, who had a boat to himself, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right then – FORWARD!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And the fleet of little boats moved off all at once, gliding across the lake, which was as smooth as glass. Everyone was silent, staring up at the great castle overhead. It towered over them as they sailed nearer and nearer to the cliff on which it stood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Heads down!’ yelled Hagrid as the first boats reached the cliff; </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>84 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they all bent their heads and the little boats carried them through a curtain of ivy which hid a wide opening in the cliff face. They were carried along a dark tunnel, which seemed to be taking them right underneath the castle, until they reached a kind of underground harbour, where they clambered out on to rocks and pebbles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oy, you there! Is this your toad?’ said Hagrid, who was checking the boats as people climbed out of them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Trevor!’ cried Neville blissfully, holding out his hands. Then they clambered up a passageway in the rock after Hagrid’s lamp, coming out at last on to smooth, damp grass right in the shadow of the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They walked up a flight of stone steps and crowded around the huge, oak front door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone here? You there, still got yer toad?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid raised a gigantic fist and knocked three times on the castle door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER SEVEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Sorting Hat </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door swung open at once. A tall, black-haired witch in emerald-green robes stood there. She had a very stern face and Harry’s first thought was that this was not someone to cross. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The firs’-years, Professor McGonagall,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you, Hagrid. I will take them from here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She pulled the door wide. The Entrance Hall was so big you could have fitted the whole of the Dursleys’ house in it. The stone walls were lit with flaming torches like the ones at Gringotts, the ceiling was too high to make out, and a magnificent marble staircase facing them led to the upper floors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They followed Professor McGonagall across the flagged stone floor. Harry could hear the drone of hundreds of voices from a doorway to the right – the rest of the school must already be here </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– but Professor McGonagall showed the first-years into a small empty chamber off the hall. They crowded in, standing rather closer together than they would usually have done, peering about nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Welcome to Hogwarts,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘The start-of-term banquet will begin shortly, but before you take your seats in the Great Hall, you will be sorted into your houses. The Sorting is a very important ceremony because, while you are here, your house will be something like your family within Hogwarts. You will have classes with the rest of your house, sleep in your house dormitory and spend free time in your house common room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The four houses are called Gryffindor, Hufflepuff, Ravenclaw and Slytherin. Each house has its own noble history and each has produced outstanding witches and wizards. While you are at Hogwarts, your triumphs will earn your house points, while any rule-breaking will lose house points. At the end of the year, the house with the most points is awarded the House Cup, a great </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>86 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">honour. I hope each of you will be a credit to whichever house becomes yours. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Sorting Ceremony will take place in a few minutes in front of the rest of the school. I suggest you all smarten yourselves up as much as you can while you are waiting.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Her eyes lingered for a moment on Neville’s cloak, which was fastened under his left ear, and on Ron’s smudged nose. Harry nervously tried to flatten his hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I shall return when we are ready for you,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘Please wait quietly.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She left the chamber. Harry swallowed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How exactly do they sort us into houses?’ he asked Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Some sort of test, I think. Fred said it hurts a lot, but I think he was joking.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s heart gave a horrible jolt. A test? In front of the whole school? But he didn’t know any magic yet – what on earth would he have to do? He hadn’t expected something like this the moment they arrived. He looked around anxiously and saw that everyone else looked terrified too. No one was talking much except Hermione Granger, who was whispering very fast about all the spells she’d learnt and wondering which one she’d need. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried hard not to listen to her. He’d never been more nervous, never, not even when he’d had to take a school report home to the Dursleys saying that he’d somehow turned his teacher’s wig blue. He kept his eyes fixed on the door. Any second now, Professor McGonagall would come back and lead him to his doom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then something happened which made him jump about a foot in the air – several people behind him screamed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What the –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gasped. So did the people around him. About twenty ghosts had just streamed through the back wall. Pearly-white and slightly transparent, they glided across the room talking to each other and hardly glancing at the first-years. They seemed to be arguing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What looked like a fat little monk was saying, ‘Forgive and forget, I say, we ought to give him a second chance –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear Friar, haven’t we given Peeves all the chances he deserves? He gives us all a bad name and you know, he’s not really even a ghost – I say, what are you all doing here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A ghost wearing a ruff and tights had suddenly noticed the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Sorting Hat 87 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">first-years. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nobody answered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘New students!’ said the Fat Friar, smiling around at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘About to be sorted, I suppose?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A few people nodded mutely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hope to see you in Hufflepuff!’ said the Friar. ‘My old house, you know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Move along now,’ said a sharp voice. ‘The Sorting Ceremony’s about to start.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall had returned. One by one, the ghosts floated away through the opposite wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, form a line,’ Professor McGonagall told the first-years, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘and follow me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Feeling oddly as though his legs had turned to lead, Harry got into line behind a boy with sandy hair, with Ron behind him, and they walked out of the chamber, back across the hall and through a pair of double doors into the Great Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had never even imagined such a strange and splendid place. It was lit by thousands and thousands of candles which were floating in mid-air over four long tables, where the rest of the students were sitting. These tables were laid with glittering golden plates and goblets. At the top of the Hall was another long table where the teachers were sitting. Professor McGonagall led the first-years up here, so that they came to a halt in a line facing the other students, with the teachers behind them. The hundreds of faces staring at them looked like pale lanterns in the flickering candlelight. Dotted here and there among the students, the ghosts shone misty silver. Mainly to avoid all the staring eyes, Harry looked upwards and saw a velvety black ceiling dotted with stars. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He heard Hermione whisper, ‘It’s bewitched to look like the sky outside, I read about it in  <i class=\"calibre3\">Hogwarts: A History. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was hard to believe there was a ceiling there at all, and that the Great Hall didn’t simply open on to the heavens. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry quickly looked down again as Professor McGonagall silently placed a four-legged stool in front of the first-years. On top of the stool she put a pointed wizard’s hat. This hat was patched and frayed and extremely dirty. Aunt Petunia wouldn’t have let it in the house. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Maybe they had to try and get a rabbit out of it, Harry thought wildly, that seemed the sort of thing – noticing that everyone in </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>88 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the Hall was now staring at the hat, he stared at it too. For a few seconds, there was complete silence. Then the hat twitched. A rip near the brim opened wide like a mouth – and the hat began to sing: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">‘Oh, you may not think I’m pretty,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">But don’t judge on what you see, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">I’ll eat myself if you can find</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">A smarter hat than me. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">You can keep your bowlers black, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Your top hats sleek and tall, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">For I’m the Hogwarts Sorting Hat</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">And I can cap them all. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">There’s nothing hidden in your head</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Sorting Hat can’t see, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">So try me on and I will tell you</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Where you ought to be. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">You might belong in Gryffindor, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Where dwell the brave at heart, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Their daring, nerve and chivalry</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Set Gryffindors apart; </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">You might belong in Hufflepuff, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Where they are just and loyal, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Those patient Hufflepuffs are true</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">And unafraid of toil; </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Or yet in wise old Ravenclaw, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">If you’ve a ready mind, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Where those of wit and learning, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Will always find their kind; </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Or perhaps in Slytherin</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">You’ll make your real friends, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Those cunning folk use any means</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">To achieve their ends. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">So put me on! Don’t be afraid! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">And don’t get in a flap! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">You’re in safe hands (though I have none)</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">For I’m a Thinking Cap!’</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The whole Hall burst into applause as the hat finished its song. It bowed to each of the four tables and then became quite still again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Sorting Hat 89 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So we’ve just got to try on the hat!’ Ron whispered to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll kill Fred, he was going on about wrestling a troll.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry smiled weakly. Yes, trying on the hat was a lot better than having to do a spell, but he did wish they could have tried it on without everyone watching. The hat seemed to be asking rather a lot; Harry didn’t feel brave or quick-witted or any of it at the moment. If only the hat had mentioned a house for people who felt a bit queasy, that would have been the one for him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall now stepped forward holding a long roll of parchment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When I call your name, you will put on the hat and sit on the stool to be sorted,’ she said. ‘Abbott, Hannah!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A pink-faced girl with blonde pigtails stumbled out of line, put on the hat, which fell right down over her eyes, and sat down. A moment’s pause – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HUFFLEPUFF!’ shouted the hat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The table on the right cheered and clapped as Hannah went to sit down at the Hufflepuff table. Harry saw the ghost of the Fat Friar waving merrily at her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bones, Susan!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HUFFLEPUFF!’ shouted the hat again, and Susan scuttled off to sit next to Hannah. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Boot, Terry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘RAVENCLAW!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The table second from the left clapped this time; several Ravenclaws stood up to shake hands with Terry as he joined them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Brocklehurst, Mandy’ went to Ravenclaw too, but ‘Brown, Lavender’ became the first new Gryffindor and the table on the far left exploded with cheers; Harry could see Ron’s twin brothers catcalling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bulstrode, Millicent’ then became a Slytherin. Perhaps it was Harry’s imagination, after all he’d heard about Slytherin, but he thought they looked an unpleasant lot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was starting to feel definitely sick now. He remembered being picked for teams during sports lessons at his old school. He had always been last to be chosen, not because he was no good, but because no one wanted Dudley to think they liked him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Finch-Fletchley, Justin!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HUFFLEPUFF!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>90 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sometimes, Harry noticed, the hat shouted out the house at once, but at others it took a little while to decide. ‘Finnigan, Seamus’, the sandy-haired boy next to Harry in the line, sat on the stool for almost a whole minute before the hat declared him a Gryffindor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Granger, Hermione!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione almost ran to the stool and jammed the hat eagerly on her head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘GRYFFINDOR!’ shouted the hat. Ron groaned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A horrible thought struck Harry, as horrible thoughts always do when you’re very nervous. What if he wasn’t chosen at all? What if he just sat there with the hat over his eyes for ages, until Professor McGonagall jerked it off his head and said there had obviously been a mistake and he’d better get back on the train? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Neville Longbottom, the boy who kept losing his toad, was called, he fell over on his way to the stool. The hat took a long time to decide with Neville. When it finally shouted </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘GRYFFINDOR’, Neville ran off still wearing it, and had to jog back amid gales of laughter to give it to ‘MacDougal, Morag’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy swaggered forward when his name was called and got his wish at once: the hat had barely touched his head when it screamed, ‘SLYTHERIN!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy went to join his friends Crabbe and Goyle, looking pleased with himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There weren’t many people left now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Moon’ … ‘Nott’ … ‘Parkinson’ … then a pair of twin girls, ‘Patil’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and ‘Patil’ … then ‘Perks, Sally-Anne’ … and then, at last – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry stepped forward, whispers suddenly broke out like little hissing fires all over the hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Potter</i>, did she say?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">The</i> Harry Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The last thing Harry saw before the hat dropped over his eyes was the Hall full of people craning to get a good look at him. Next second he was looking at the black inside of the hat. He waited. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hmm,’ said a small voice in his ear. ‘Difficult. Very difficult. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Plenty of courage, I see. Not a bad mind, either. There’s talent, oh my goodness, yes – and a nice thirst to prove yourself, now that’s interesting … So where shall I put you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry gripped the edges of the stool and thought, ‘Not </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Sorting Hat 91 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slytherin, not Slytherin.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not Slytherin, eh?’ said the small voice. ‘Are you sure? You could be great, you know, it’s all here in your head, and Slytherin will help you on the way to greatness, no doubt about that – no? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Well, if you’re sure – better be GRYFFINDOR!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry heard the hat shout the last word to the whole Hall. He took off the hat and walked shakily towards the Gryffindor table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was so relieved to have been chosen and not put in Slytherin, he hardly noticed that he was getting the loudest cheer yet. Percy the Prefect got up and shook his hand vigorously, while the Weasley twins yelled, ‘We got Potter! We got Potter!’ Harry sat down opposite the ghost in the ruff he’d seen earlier. The ghost patted his arm, giving Harry the sudden, horrible feeling he’d just plunged it into a bucket of ice-cold water. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He could see the High Table properly now. At the end nearest him sat Hagrid, who caught his eye and gave him the thumbs-up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry grinned back. And there, in the centre of the High Table, in a large gold chair, sat Albus Dumbledore. Harry recognised him at once from the card he’d got out of the Chocolate Frog on the train. Dumbledore’s silver hair was the only thing in the whole Hall that shone as brightly as the ghosts. Harry spotted Professor Quirrell, too, the nervous young man from the Leaky Cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was looking very peculiar in a large purple turban. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And now there were only three people left to be sorted. ‘Turpin, Lisa’ became a Ravenclaw and then it was Ron’s turn. He was pale green by now. Harry crossed his fingers under the table and a second later the hat had shouted, ‘GRYFFINDOR!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry clapped loudly with the rest as Ron collapsed into the chair next to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well done, Ron, excellent,’ said Percy Weasley pompously across Harry as ‘Zabini, Blaise’ was made a Slytherin. Professor McGonagall rolled up her scroll and took the Sorting Hat away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked down at his empty gold plate. He had only just realised how hungry he was. The pumpkin pasties seemed ages ago. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Albus Dumbledore had got to his feet. He was beaming at the students, his arms opened wide, as if nothing could have pleased him more than to see them all there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Welcome!’ he said. ‘Welcome to a new year at Hogwarts! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before we begin our banquet, I would like to say a few words. And </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>92 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">here they are: Nitwit! Blubber! Oddment! Tweak! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He sat back down. Everybody clapped and cheered. Harry didn’t know whether to laugh or not. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is he – a bit mad?’ he asked Percy uncertainly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mad?’ said Percy airily. ‘He’s a genius! Best wizard in the world! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he is a bit mad, yes. Potatoes, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s mouth fell open. The dishes in front of him were now piled with food. He had never seen so many things he liked to eat on one table: roast beef, roast chicken, pork chops and lamb chops, sausages, bacon and steak, boiled potatoes, roast potatoes, chips, Yorkshire pudding, peas, carrots, gravy, ketchup and, for some strange reason, mint humbugs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dursleys had never exactly starved Harry, but he’d never been allowed to eat as much as he liked. Dudley had always taken anything that Harry really wanted, even if it made him sick. Harry piled his plate with a bit of everything except the humbugs and began to eat. It was all delicious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That does look good,’ said the ghost in the ruff sadly, watching Harry cut up his steak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t you –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I haven’t eaten for nearly five hundred years,’ said the ghost. ‘I don’t need to, of course, but one does miss it. I don’t think I’ve introduced myself? Sir Nicholas de Mimsy-Porpington at your service. Resident ghost of Gryffindor Tower.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know who you are!’ said Ron suddenly. ‘My brothers told me about you – you’re Nearly Headless Nick!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I would  <i class=\"calibre3\">prefer</i> you to call me Sir Nicholas de Mimsy –’ the ghost began stiffly, but sandy-haired Seamus Finnigan interrupted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Nearly</i> Headless? How can you be  <i class=\"calibre3\">nearly</i> headless?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sir Nicholas looked extremely miffed, as if their little chat wasn’t going at all the way he wanted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Like  <i class=\"calibre3\">this</i>,’ he said irritably. He seized his left ear and pulled. His whole head swung off his neck and fell on to his shoulder as if it was on a hinge. Someone had obviously tried to behead him, but not done it properly. Looking pleased at the stunned looks on their faces, Nearly Headless Nick flipped his head back on to his neck, coughed and said, ‘So – new Gryffindors! I hope you’re going to help us win the House Championship this year? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor have never gone so long without winning. Slytherin </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Sorting Hat 93 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">have got the cup six years in a row! The Bloody Baron’s becoming almost unbearable – he’s the Slytherin ghost.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked over at the Slytherin table and saw a horrible ghost sitting there, with blank staring eyes, a gaunt face and robes stained with silver blood. He was right next to Malfoy who, Harry was pleased to see, didn’t look too pleased with the seating arrangements. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did he get covered in blood?’ asked Seamus with great interest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve never asked,’ said Nearly Headless Nick delicately. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When everyone had eaten as much as they could, the remains of the food faded from the plates, leaving them sparkling clean as before. A moment later the puddings appeared. Blocks of ice-cream in every flavour you could think of, apple pies, treacle tarts, chocolate éclairs and jam doughnuts, trifle, strawberries, jelly, rice pudding … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry helped himself to a treacle tart, the talk turned to their families. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m half and half,’ said Seamus. ‘Me dad’s a Muggle. Mam didn’t tell him she was a witch ’til after they were married. Bit of a nasty shock for him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The others laughed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about you, Neville?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, my gran brought me up and she’s a witch,’ said Neville, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘but the family thought I was all Muggle for ages. My great-uncle Algie kept trying to catch me off my guard and force some magic out of me – he pushed me off the end of Blackpool pier once, I nearly drowned – but nothing happened until I was eight. Great-uncle Algie came round for tea and he was hanging me out of an upstairs window by the ankles when my great-auntie Enid offered him a meringue and he accidentally let go. But I bounced – all the way down the garden and into the road. They were all really pleased. Gran was crying, she was so happy. And you should have seen their faces when I got in here – they thought I might not be magic enough to come, you see. Great-uncle Algie was so pleased he bought me my toad.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On Harry’s other side, Percy Weasley and Hermione were talking about lessons (‘I  <i class=\"calibre3\">do</i> hope they start straight away, there’s so much to learn, I’m particularly interested in Transfiguration, you know, turning something into something else, of course, it’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>94 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">supposed to be very difficult –’; ‘You’ll be starting small, just matches into needles and that sort of thing –’). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who was starting to feel warm and sleepy, looked up at the High Table again. Hagrid was drinking deeply from his goblet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall was talking to Professor Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Quirrell, in his absurd turban, was talking to a teacher with greasy black hair, a hooked nose and sallow skin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It happened very suddenly. The hook-nosed teacher looked past Quirrell’s turban straight into Harry’s eyes – and a sharp, hot pain shot across the scar on Harry’s forehead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ouch!’ Harry clapped a hand to his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What is it?’ asked Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘N-nothing.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The pain had gone as quickly as it had come. Harder to shake off was the feeling Harry had got from the teacher’s look – a feeling that he didn’t like Harry at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s that teacher talking to Professor Quirrell?’ he asked Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, you know Quirrell already, do you? No wonder he’s looking so nervous, that’s Professor Snape. He teaches Potions, but he doesn’t want to – everyone knows he’s after Quirrell’s job. Knows an awful lot about the Dark Arts, Snape.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry watched Snape for a while but Snape didn’t look at him again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last, the puddings too disappeared and Professor Dumbledore got to his feet again. The Hall fell silent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ahem – just a few more words now we are all fed and watered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I have a few start-of-term notices to give you. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘First-years should note that the forest in the grounds is forbidden to all pupils. And a few of our older students would do well to remember that as well.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore’s twinkling eyes flashed in the direction of the Weasley twins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have also been asked by Mr Filch, the caretaker, to remind you all that no magic should be used between classes in the corridors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quidditch trials will be held in the second week of term. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Anyone interested in playing for their house teams should contact Madam Hooch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And finally, I must tell you that this year, the third-floor </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Sorting Hat 95 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">corridor on the right-hand side is out of bounds to everyone who does not wish to die a very painful death.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry laughed, but he was one of the few who did. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s not serious?’ he muttered to Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Must be,’ said Percy, frowning at Dumbledore. ‘It’s odd, because he usually gives us a reason why we’re not allowed to go somewhere – the forest’s full of dangerous beasts, everyone knows that. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I do think he might have told us Prefects, at least.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And now, before we go to bed, let us sing the school song!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">cried Dumbledore. Harry noticed that the other teachers’ smiles had become rather fixed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore gave his wand a little flick as if he was trying to get a fly off the end and a long golden ribbon flew out of it, which rose high above the tables and twisted itself snake-like into words. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone pick their favourite tune,’ said Dumbledore, ‘and off we go!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And the school bellowed: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">‘Hogwarts, Hogwarts, Hoggy Warty Hogwarts,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Teach us something please, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Whether we be old and bald</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Or young with scabby knees, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Our heads could do with filling</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">With some interesting stuff, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">For now they’re bare and full of air,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Dead flies and bits of fluff, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">So teach us things worth knowing,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Bring back what we’ve forgot, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Just do your best, we’ll do the rest,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">And learn until our brains all rot. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everybody finished the song at different times. At last, only the Weasley twins were left singing along to a very slow funeral march. Dumbledore conducted their last few lines with his wand, and when they had finished, he was one of those who clapped loudest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, music,’ he said, wiping his eyes. ‘A magic beyond all we do here! And now, bedtime. Off you trot!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindor first-years followed Percy through the chattering crowds, out of the Great Hall and up the marble staircase. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>96 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s legs were like lead again, but only because he was so tired and full of food. He was too sleepy even to be surprised that the people in the portraits along the corridors whispered and pointed as they passed, or that twice Percy led them through doorways hidden behind sliding panels and hanging tapestries. They climbed more staircases, yawning and dragging their feet, and Harry was just wondering how much further they had to go when they came to a sudden halt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A bundle of walking sticks was floating in mid-air ahead of them and as Percy took a step towards them they started throwing themselves at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Peeves,’ Percy whispered to the first-years. ‘A poltergeist.’ He raised his voice, ‘Peeves – show yourself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A loud, rude sound, like the air being let out of a balloon, answered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you want me to go to the Bloody Baron?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a  <i class=\"calibre3\">pop</i> and a little man with wicked dark eyes and a wide mouth appeared, floating cross-legged in the air, clutching the walking sticks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oooooooh!’ he said, with an evil cackle. ‘Ickle firsties! What fun!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He swooped suddenly at them. They all ducked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go away, Peeves, or the Baron’ll hear about this, I mean it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">barked Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peeves stuck out his tongue and vanished, dropping the walking sticks on Neville’s head. They heard him zooming away, rattling coats of armour as he passed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You want to watch out for Peeves,’  said  Percy,  as  they  set  off again. ‘The Bloody Baron’s the only one who can control him, he won’t even listen to us Prefects. Here we are.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At the very end of the corridor hung a portrait of a very fat woman in a pink silk dress. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Password?’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Caput Draconis</i>,’ said Percy, and the portrait swung forward to reveal a round hole in the wall. They all scrambled through it – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville needed a leg up – and found themselves in the Gryffindor common room, a cosy, round room full of squashy armchairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy directed the girls through one door to their dormitory and the boys through another. At the top of a spiral staircase – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they were obviously in one of the towers – they found their beds  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Sorting Hat 97 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">at last: five four-posters hung with deep-red velvet curtains. Their trunks had already been brought up. Too tired to talk much, they pulled on their pyjamas and fell into bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Great food, isn’t it?’ Ron muttered to Harry through the hangings. ‘Get  <i class=\"calibre3\">off, </i> Scabbers! He’s chewing my sheets.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was going to ask Ron if he’d had any of the treacle tart, but he fell asleep almost at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps Harry had eaten a bit too much, because he had a very strange dream. He was wearing Professor Quirrell’s turban, which kept talking to him, telling him he must transfer to Slytherin at once, because it was his destiny. Harry told the turban he didn’t want to be in Slytherin; it got heavier and heavier; he tried to pull it off but it tightened painfully – and there was Malfoy, laughing at him as he struggled with it – then Malfoy turned into the hook-nosed teacher, Snape, whose laugh became high and cold – there was a burst of green light and Harry woke, sweating and shaking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He rolled over and fell asleep again, and when he woke next day, he didn’t remember the dream at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER EIGHT — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Potions Master </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There, look.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Next to the tall kid with the red hair.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wearing the glasses?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you see his face?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you see his scar?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Whispers  followed  Harry  from  the  moment  he  left  his  dormitory next day. People queuing outside classrooms stood on tiptoe to get a look at him, or doubled back to pass him in the corridors again, staring. Harry wished they wouldn’t, because he was trying to concentrate on finding his way to classes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There were a hundred and forty-two staircases at Hogwarts: wide, sweeping ones; narrow, rickety ones; some that led somewhere different on a Friday; some with a vanishing step halfway up that you had to remember to jump. Then there were doors that wouldn’t open unless you asked politely, or tickled them in exactly the right place, and doors that weren’t really doors at all, but solid walls just pretending. It was also very hard to remember where anything was, because it all seemed to move around a lot. The people in the portraits kept going to visit each other and Harry was sure the coats of armour could walk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The ghosts didn’t help, either. It was always a nasty shock when one of them glided suddenly through a door you were trying to open. Nearly Headless Nick was always happy to point new Gryffindors in the right direction, but Peeves the poltergeist was worth two locked doors and a trick staircase if you met him when you were late for class. He would drop waste-paper baskets on your head, pull rugs from under your feet, pelt you with bits of chalk or sneak up behind you, invisible, grab your nose and screech, ‘GOT YOUR CONK!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Potions Master 99 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Even worse than Peeves, if that was possible, was the caretaker, Argus Filch. Harry and Ron managed to get on the wrong side of him on their very first morning. Filch found them trying to force their way through a door which unluckily turned out to be the entrance to the out-of-bounds corridor on the third floor. He wouldn’t believe they were lost, was sure they were trying to break into it on purpose and was threatening to lock them in the dungeons when they were rescued by Professor Quirrell, who was passing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filch owned a cat called Mrs Norris, a scrawny, dust-coloured creature with bulging, lamp-like eyes just like Filch’s. She patrolled the corridors alone. Break a rule in front of her, put just one toe out of line, and she’d whisk off for Filch, who’d appear, wheezing, two seconds later. Filch knew the secret passageways of the school better than anyone (except perhaps the Weasley twins) and could pop up as suddenly as any of the ghosts. The students all hated him and it was the dearest ambition of many to give Mrs Norris a good kick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then, once you had managed to find them, there were the lessons themselves. There was a lot more to magic, as Harry quickly found out, than waving your wand and saying a few funny words. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had to study the night skies through their telescopes every Wednesday at midnight and learn the names of different stars and the movements of the planets. Three times a week they went out to the greenhouses behind the castle to study Herbology, with a dumpy little witch called Professor Sprout, where they learnt how to take care of all the strange plants and fungi and found out what they were used for. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Easily the most boring lesson was History of Magic, which was the only class taught by a ghost. Professor Binns had been very old indeed when he had fallen asleep in front of the staff-room fire and got up next morning to teach, leaving his body behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Binns droned on and on while they scribbled down names and dates and got Emeric the Evil and Uric the Oddball mixed up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Flitwick, the Charms teacher, was a tiny little wizard who had to stand on a pile of books to see over his desk. At the start of their first lesson he took the register, and when he reached Harry’s name he gave an excited squeak and toppled out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall was again different. Harry had been quite right to think she wasn’t a teacher to cross. Strict and clever, she </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>100 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">gave them a talking-to the moment they had sat down in her first class. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Transfiguration is some of the most complex and dangerous magic you will learn at Hogwarts,’ she said. ‘Anyone messing around in my class will leave and not come back. You have been warned.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then she changed her desk into a pig and back again. They were all very impressed and couldn’t wait to get started, but soon realised they weren’t going to be changing the furniture into animals for a long time. After making a lot of complicated notes, they were each given a match and started trying to turn it into a needle. By the end of the lesson, only Hermione Granger had made any difference to her match; Professor McGonagall showed the class how it had gone all silver and pointy and gave Hermione a rare smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The class everyone had really been looking forward to was Defence Against the Dark Arts, but Quirrell’s lessons turned out to be a bit of a joke. His classroom smelled strongly of garlic, which everyone said was to ward off a vampire he’d met in Romania and was afraid would be coming back to get him one of these days. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His turban, he told them, had been given to him by an African prince as a thank-you for getting rid of a troublesome zombie, but they weren’t sure they believed this story. For one thing, when Seamus Finnigan asked eagerly to hear how Quirrell had fought off the zombie, Quirrell went pink and started talking about the weather; for another, they had noticed that a funny smell hung around the turban, and the Weasley twins insisted that it was stuffed full of garlic as well, so that Quirrell was protected wherever he went. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was very relieved to find out that he wasn’t miles behind everyone else. Lots of people had come from Muggle families and, like him, hadn’t had any idea that they were witches and wizards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was so much to learn that even people like Ron didn’t have much of a head start. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Friday was an important day for Harry and Ron. They finally managed to find their way down to the Great Hall for breakfast without getting lost once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What have we got today?’ Harry asked Ron as he poured sugar on his porridge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Double Potions with the Slytherins,’ said Ron. ‘Snape’s Head of </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Potions Master 101 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slytherin house. They say he always favours them – we’ll be able to see if it’s true.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wish McGonagall favoured us,’  said  Harry.  Professor McGonagall was Head of Gryffindor house, but it hadn’t stopped her giving them a huge pile of homework the day before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Just then, the post arrived. Harry had got used to this by now, but it had given him a bit of a shock on the first morning, when about a hundred owls had suddenly streamed into the Great Hall during breakfast, circling the tables until they saw their owners and dropping letters and packages on to their laps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hedwig hadn’t brought Harry anything so far. She sometimes flew in to nibble his ear and have a bit of toast before going off to sleep in the owlery with the other school owls. This morning, however, she fluttered down between the marmalade and the sugar bowl and dropped a note on to Harry’s plate. Harry tore it open at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Dear Harry, </i> (it said, in a very untidy scrawl) <i class=\"calibre3\">I know you get Friday afternoons off, so would you like to</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">come and have a cup of tea with me around three? I want to hear</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">all about your first week. Send us an answer back with Hedwig. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Hagrid</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry borrowed Ron’s quill, scribbled ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Yes, please, see you later</i>’ on the back of the note and sent Hedwig off again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was lucky that Harry had tea with Hagrid to look forward to, because the Potions lesson turned out to be the worst thing that had happened to him so far. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At the start-of-term banquet, Harry had got the idea that Professor Snape disliked him. By the end of the first Potions lesson, he knew he’d been wrong. Snape didn’t dislike Harry – he <i class=\"calibre3\">hated</i> him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Potions lessons took place down in one of the dungeons. It was colder here than up in the main castle and would have been quite creepy enough without the pickled animals floating in glass jars all around the walls. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape, like Flitwick, started the class by taking the register, and like Flitwick, he paused at Harry’s name. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, yes,’ he said softly, ‘Harry Potter. Our new –  <i class=\"calibre3\">celebrity</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Draco Malfoy and his friends Crabbe and Goyle sniggered </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>102 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">behind their hands. Snape finished calling the names and looked up at the class. His eyes were black like Hagrid’s, but they had none of Hagrid’s warmth. They were cold and empty and made you think of dark tunnels. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You are here to learn the subtle science and exact art of potion-making,’  he  began.  He  spoke  in  barely  more  than  a  whisper,  but they caught every word – like Professor McGonagall, Snape had the gift of keeping a class silent without effort. ‘As there is little foolish wand-waving here, many of you will hardly believe this is magic. I don’t expect you will really understand the beauty of the softly simmering cauldron with its shimmering fumes, the delicate power of liquids that creep through human veins, bewitching the mind, ensnaring the senses … I can teach you how to bottle fame, brew glory, even stopper death – if you aren’t as big a bunch of dunderheads as I usually have to teach.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">More silence followed this little speech. Harry and Ron exchanged looks with raised eyebrows. Hermione Granger was on the edge of her seat and looked desperate to start proving that she wasn’t a dunderhead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter!’ said Snape suddenly. ‘What would I get if I added powdered root of asphodel to an infusion of wormwood?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Powdered root of what to an infusion of what? </i> Harry glanced at Ron, who looked as stumped as he was; Hermione’s hand had shot into the air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know, sir,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s lips curled into a sneer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tut, tut – fame clearly isn’t everything.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He ignored Hermione’s hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s try again. Potter, where would you look if I told you to find me a bezoar?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione stretched her hand as high into the air as it would go without her leaving her seat, but Harry didn’t have the faintest idea what a bezoar was. He tried not to look at Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle, who were shaking with laughter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know, sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thought you wouldn’t open a book before coming, eh, Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry forced himself to keep looking straight into those cold eyes. He  <i class=\"calibre3\">had</i> looked through his books at the Dursleys’, but did Snape expect him to remember everything in  <i class=\"calibre3\">One Thousand</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Magical Herbs and Fungi? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Potions Master 103 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape was still ignoring Hermione’s quivering hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What is the difference, Potter, between monkshood and wolfsbane?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At this, Hermione stood up, her hand stretching towards the dungeon ceiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know,’ said Harry quietly. ‘I think Hermione does, though, why don’t you try her?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A few people laughed; Harry caught Seamus’s eye and Seamus winked. Snape, however, was not pleased. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sit down,’ he snapped at Hermione. ‘For your information, Potter, asphodel and wormwood make a sleeping potion so powerful it is known as the Draught of Living Death. A bezoar is a stone taken from the stomach of a goat and it will save you from most poisons. As for monkshood and wolfsbane, they are the same plant, which also goes by the name of aconite. Well? Why aren’t you all copying that down?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a sudden rummaging for quills and parchment. Over the noise, Snape said, ‘And a point will be taken from Gryffindor house for your cheek, Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Things didn’t improve for the Gryffindors as the Potions lesson continued. Snape put them all into pairs and set them to mixing up a simple potion to cure boils. He swept around in his long black cloak, watching them weigh dried nettles and crush snake fangs, criticising almost everyone except Malfoy, whom he seemed to like. He was just telling everyone to look at the perfect way Malfoy had stewed his horned slugs when clouds of acid green smoke and a loud hissing filled the dungeon. Neville had somehow managed to melt Seamus’s cauldron into a twisted blob and their potion was seeping across the stone floor, burning holes in people’s shoes. Within seconds, the whole class were standing on their stools while Neville, who had been drenched in the potion when the cauldron collapsed, moaned in pain as angry red boils sprang up all over his arms and legs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Idiot boy!’ snarled Snape, clearing the spilled potion away with one wave of his wand. ‘I suppose you added the porcupine quills before taking the cauldron off the fire?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville whimpered as boils started to pop up all over his nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Take him up to the hospital wing,’ Snape spat at Seamus. Then he rounded on Harry and Ron, who had been working next to Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>104 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You – Potter – why didn’t you tell him not to add the quills? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Thought he’d make you look good if he got it wrong, did you? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">That’s another point you’ve lost for Gryffindor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This was so unfair that Harry opened his mouth to argue, but Ron kicked him behind their cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t push it,’ he muttered. ‘I’ve heard Snape can turn very nasty.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As they climbed the steps out of the dungeon an hour later, Harry’s mind was racing and his spirits were low. He’d lost two points for Gryffindor in his very first week –  <i class=\"calibre3\">why</i> did Snape hate him so much? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Cheer up,’ said Ron. ‘Snape’s always taking points off Fred and George. Can I come and meet Hagrid with you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At five to three they left the castle and made their way across the grounds. Hagrid lived in a small wooden house on the edge of the Forbidden Forest. A crossbow and a pair of galoshes were outside the front door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Harry knocked they heard a frantic scrabbling from inside and several booming barks. Then Hagrid’s voice rang out, saying, ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Back</i>, Fang –  <i class=\"calibre3\">back. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s big hairy face appeared in the crack as he pulled the door open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hang on,’ he said. ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Back</i>, Fang.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He let them in, struggling to keep a hold on the collar of an enormous black boarhound. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was only one room inside. Hams and pheasants were hanging from the ceiling, a copper kettle was boiling on the open fire and in a corner stood a massive bed with a patchwork quilt over it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Make yerselves at home,’ said Hagrid, letting go of Fang, who bounded straight at Ron and started licking his ears. Like Hagrid, Fang was clearly not as fierce as he looked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is Ron,’ Harry told Hagrid, who was pouring boiling water into a large teapot and putting rock cakes on to a plate. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Another Weasley, eh?’ said Hagrid, glancing at Ron’s freckles. ‘I spent half me life chasin’ yer twin brothers away from the Forest.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rock cakes almost broke their teeth, but Harry and Ron pretended to be enjoying them as they told Hagrid all about their first lessons. Fang rested his head on Harry’s knee and drooled all over his robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Potions Master 105 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron were delighted to hear Hagrid call Filch ‘that old git’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An’ as fer that cat, Mrs Norris, I’d like ter introduce her to Fang some time. D’yeh know, every time I go up ter the school, she follows me everywhere? Can’t get rid of her – Filch puts her up to it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry told Hagrid about Snape’s lesson. Hagrid, like Ron, told Harry not to worry about it, that Snape liked hardly any of the students. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But he seemed to really  <i class=\"calibre3\">hate</i> me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rubbish!’ said Hagrid. ‘Why should he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Yet Harry couldn’t help thinking that Hagrid didn’t quite meet his eyes when he said that. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How’s yer brother Charlie?’ Hagrid asked Ron. ‘I liked him a lot </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– great with animals.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wondered if Hagrid had changed the subject on purpose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">While Ron told Hagrid all about Charlie’s work with dragons, Harry picked up a piece of paper that was lying on the table under the tea cosy. It was a cutting from the  <i class=\"calibre3\">Daily Prophet</i>: <i class=\"calibre3\">GRINGOTTS BREAK-IN LATEST </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Investigations continue into the break-in at Gringotts on 31 </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">July, widely believed to be the work of dark wizards or witches</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">unknown. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Gringotts’ goblins today insisted that nothing had been</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">taken. The vault that was searched had in fact been emptied</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">the same day. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">‘But we’re not telling you what was in there, so keep your</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">noses out if you know what’s good for you,’ said a Gringotts</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">spokesgoblin this afternoon. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry remembered Ron telling him on the train that someone had tried to rob Gringotts, but Ron hadn’t mentioned the date. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid!’ said Harry. ‘That Gringotts break-in happened on my birthday! It might’ve been happening while we were there!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was no doubt about it, Hagrid definitely didn’t meet Harry’s eyes this time. He grunted and offered him another rock cake. Harry read the story again.  <i class=\"calibre3\">The vault that was searched had in</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">fact been emptied earlier that same day. </i> Hagrid had emptied vault seven hundred and thirteen, if you could call it emptying, taking </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>106 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">out that grubby little package. Had that been what the thieves were looking for? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry and Ron walked back to the castle for dinner, their pockets weighed down with rock cakes they’d been too polite to refuse, Harry thought that none of the lessons he’d had so far had given him as much to think about as tea with Hagrid. Had Hagrid collected that package just in time? Where was it now? And did Hagrid know something about Snape that he didn’t want to tell Harry? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER NINE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Midnight Duel </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had never believed he would meet a boy he hated more than Dudley, but that was before he met Draco Malfoy. Still, first-year Gryffindors only had Potions with the Slytherins, so they didn’t have to put up with Malfoy much. Or at least, they didn’t until they spotted a notice pinned up in the Gryffindor common room which made them all groan. Flying lessons would be starting on Thursday – and Gryffindor and Slytherin would be learning together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Typical,’ said Harry darkly. ‘Just what I always wanted. To make a fool of myself on a broomstick in front of Malfoy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had been looking forward to learning to fly more than anything else. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t know you’ll make a fool of yourself,’ said Ron rea-sonably. ‘Anyway, I know Malfoy’s always going on about how good he is at Quidditch, but I bet that’s all talk.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy certainly did talk about flying a lot. He complained loudly about first-years never getting in the house Quidditch teams and told long, boastful stories which always seemed to end with him narrowly escaping Muggles in helicopters. He wasn’t the only one, though: the way Seamus Finnigan told it, he’d spent most of his childhood zooming around the countryside on his broomstick. Even Ron would tell anyone who’d listen about the time he’d almost hit a hang-glider on Charlie’s old broom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone from wizarding families talked about Quidditch con-stantly. Ron had already had a big argument with Dean Thomas, who shared their dormitory, about football. Ron couldn’t see what was exciting about a game with only one ball where no one was allowed to fly. Harry had caught Ron prodding Dean’s poster of West Ham football team, trying to make the players move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville had never been on a broomstick in his life, because his </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>108 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">grandmother had never let him near one. Privately, Harry felt she’d had good reason, because Neville managed to have an extraordinary number of accidents even with both feet on the ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione Granger was almost as nervous about flying as Neville was. This was something you couldn’t learn by heart out of a book – not that she hadn’t tried. At breakfast on Thursday she bored them all stupid with flying tips she’d got out of a library book called  <i class=\"calibre3\">Quidditch through the Ages. </i> Neville was hanging on to her every word, desperate for anything that might help him hang on to his broomstick later, but everybody else was very pleased when Hermione’s lecture was interrupted by the arrival of the post. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hadn’t had a single letter since Hagrid’s note, something that Malfoy had been quick to notice, of course. Malfoy’s eagle owl was always bringing him packages of sweets from home, which he opened gloatingly at the Slytherin table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A barn owl brought Neville a small package from his grandmother. He opened it excitedly and showed them a glass ball the size of a large marble, which seemed to be full of white smoke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s a Remembrall!’ he explained. ‘Gran knows I forget things – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">this tells you if there’s something you’ve forgotten to do. Look, you hold it tight like this and if it turns red – oh …’ His face fell, because the Remembrall had suddenly glowed scarlet, ‘… you’ve forgotten something …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville was trying to remember what he’d forgotten when Draco Malfoy, who was passing the Gryffindor table, snatched the Remembrall out of his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron jumped to their feet. They were half hoping for a reason to fight Malfoy, but Professor McGonagall, who could spot trouble quicker than any teacher in the school, was there in a flash. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s going on?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy’s got my Remembrall, Professor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Scowling, Malfoy quickly dropped the Remembrall back on the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just looking,’ he said, and he sloped away with Crabbe and Goyle behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At three-thirty that afternoon, Harry, Ron and the other Gryffindors hurried down the front steps into the grounds for  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Midnight Duel 109 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">their first flying lesson. It was a clear, breezy day and the grass rippled under their feet as they marched down the sloping lawns towards a smooth lawn on the opposite side of the grounds to the Forbidden Forest, whose trees were swaying darkly in the distance. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Slytherins were already there, and so were twenty broomsticks lying in neat lines on the ground. Harry had heard Fred and George Weasley complain about the school brooms, saying that some of them started to vibrate if you flew too high, or always flew slightly to the left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Their teacher, Madam Hooch, arrived. She had short, grey hair and yellow eyes like a hawk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, what are you all waiting for?’ she barked. ‘Everyone stand by a broomstick. Come on, hurry up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry glanced down at his broom. It was old and some of the twigs stuck out at odd angles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stick out your right hand over your broom,’ called Madam Hooch at the front, ‘and say, “Up!” ’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘UP!’ everyone shouted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s broom jumped into his hand at once, but it was one of the few that did. Hermione Granger’s had simply rolled over on the ground and Neville’s hadn’t moved at all. Perhaps brooms, like horses, could tell when you were afraid, thought Harry; there was a quaver in Neville’s voice that said only too clearly that he wanted to keep his feet on the ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch then showed them how to mount their brooms without sliding off the end, and walked up and down the rows, correcting their grips. Harry and Ron were delighted when she told Malfoy he’d been doing it wrong for years. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, when I blow my whistle, you kick off from the ground, hard,’ said Madam Hooch. ‘Keep your brooms steady, rise a few feet and then come straight back down by leaning forwards slightly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On my whistle – three – two –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Neville, nervous and jumpy and frightened of being left on the ground, pushed off hard before the whistle had touched Madam Hooch’s lips. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come back, boy!’ she shouted, but Neville was rising straight up like a cork shot out of a bottle – twelve feet – twenty feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry saw his scared white face look down at the ground falling away, saw him gasp, slip sideways off the broom and – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">WHAM – a thud and a nasty crack and Neville lay, face down, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>110 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">on the grass in a heap. His broomstick was still rising higher and higher and started to drift lazily towards the Forbidden Forest and out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch was bending over Neville, her face as white as his. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Broken wrist,’ Harry heard her mutter. ‘Come on, boy – it’s all right, up you get.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She turned to the rest of the class. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘None of you is to move while I take this boy to the hospital wing! You leave those brooms where they are or you’ll be out of Hogwarts before you can say “Quidditch”. Come on, dear.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville, his face tear-streaked, clutching his wrist, hobbled off with Madam Hooch, who had her arm around him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No sooner were they out of earshot than Malfoy burst into laughter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you see his face, the great lump?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The other Slytherins joined in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up, Malfoy,’ snapped Parvati Patil. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ooh, sticking up for Longbottom?’ said Pansy Parkinson, a hard-faced Slytherin girl. ‘Never thought  <i class=\"calibre3\">you’d</i> like fat little cry babies, Parvati.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look!’ said Malfoy, darting forward and snatching something out of the grass. ‘It’s that stupid thing Longbottom’s gran sent him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Remembrall glittered in the sun as he held it up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Give that here, Malfoy,’ said Harry quietly. Everyone stopped talking to watch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy smiled nastily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think I’ll leave it somewhere for Longbottom to collect – how about – up a tree?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Give it  <i class=\"calibre3\">here! </i>’ Harry yelled, but Malfoy had leapt on to his broomstick and taken off. He hadn’t been lying, he  <i class=\"calibre3\">could</i> fly well – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">hovering level with the topmost branches of an oak he called, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come and get it, Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry grabbed his broom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">No! </i>’ shouted Hermione Granger. ‘Madam Hooch told us not to move – you’ll get us all into trouble.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ignored her. Blood was pounding in his ears. He mounted the broom and kicked hard against the ground and up, up he soared, air rushed through his hair and his robes whipped out </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Midnight Duel 111 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">behind him – and in a rush of fierce joy he realised he’d found something he could do without being taught – this was easy, this was  <i class=\"calibre3\">wonderful. </i> He pulled his broomstick up a little to take it even higher and heard screams and gasps of girls back on the ground and an admiring whoop from Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned his broomstick sharply to face Malfoy in mid-air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy looked stunned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Give it here,’ Harry called, ‘or I’ll knock you off that broom!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yeah?’ said Malfoy, trying to sneer, but looking worried. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knew, somehow, what to do. He leant forward and grasped the broom tightly in both hands and it shot towards Malfoy like a javelin. Malfoy only just got out of the way in time; Harry made a sharp about turn and held the broom steady. A few people below were clapping. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No Crabbe and Goyle up here to save your neck, Malfoy,’ Harry called. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The same thought seemed to have struck Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Catch it if you can, then!’ he shouted, and he threw the glass ball high into the air and streaked back towards the ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry saw, as though in slow motion, the ball rise up in the air and then start to fall. He leant forward and pointed his broom handle down – next second he was gathering speed in a steep dive, racing the ball – wind whistled in his ears, mingled with the screams of people watching – he stretched out his hand – a foot from the ground he caught it, just in time to pull his broom straight, and he toppled gently on to the grass with the Remembrall clutched safely in his fist. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HARRY POTTER!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His heart sank faster than he’d just dived. Professor McGonagall was running towards them. He got to his feet, trembling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Never</i> – in all my time at Hogwarts –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall was almost speechless with shock, and her glasses flashed furiously, ‘– how  <i class=\"calibre3\">dare</i> you – might have broken your neck –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It wasn’t his fault, Professor –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Be quiet, Miss Patil –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Malfoy –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s  <i class=\"calibre3\">enough, </i> Mr Weasley. Potter, follow me, now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry caught sight of Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle’s triumphant </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>112 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">faces as he left, walking numbly in Professor McGonagall’s wake as she strode towards the castle. He was going to be expelled, he just knew it. He wanted to say something to defend himself, but there seemed to be something wrong with his voice. Professor McGonagall was sweeping along without even looking at him; he had to jog to keep up. Now he’d done it. He hadn’t even lasted two weeks. He’d be packing his bags in ten minutes. What would the Dursleys say when he turned up on the doorstep? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Up the front steps, up the marble staircase inside, and still Professor McGonagall didn’t say a word to him. She wrenched open doors and marched along corridors with Harry trotting miserably behind her. Maybe she was taking him to Dumbledore. He thought of Hagrid, expelled but allowed to stay on as gamekeeper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps he could be Hagrid’s assistant. His stomach twisted as he imagined it, watching Ron and the others becoming wizards while he stumped around the grounds, carrying Hagrid’s bag. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall stopped outside a classroom. She opened the door and poked her head inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excuse me, Professor Flitwick, could I borrow Wood for a moment?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood? thought Harry, bewildered; was Wood a cane she was going to use on him? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Wood turned out to be a person, a burly fifth-year boy who came out of Flitwick’s class looking confused. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Follow me, you two,’ said Professor McGonagall, and they marched on up the corridor, Wood looking curiously at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall pointed them into a classroom which was empty except for Peeves, who was busy writing rude words on the blackboard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Out, Peeves!’ she barked. Peeves threw the chalk into a bin, which clanged loudly, and he swooped out cursing. Professor McGonagall slammed the door behind him and turned to face the two boys. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter, this is Oliver Wood. Wood – I’ve found you a Seeker.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood’s expression changed from puzzlement to delight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you serious, Professor?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Absolutely,’ said Professor McGonagall crisply. ‘The boy’s a natural. I’ve never seen anything like it. Was that your first time on a broomstick, Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Midnight Duel 113 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry nodded silently. He didn’t have a clue what was going on, but he didn’t seem to be being expelled, and some of the feeling started coming back to his legs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He caught that thing in his hand after a fifty-foot dive,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall told Wood. ‘Didn’t even scratch himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Charlie Weasley couldn’t have done it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood was now looking as though all his dreams had come true at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ever seen a game of Quidditch, Potter?’ he asked excitedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wood’s captain of the Gryffindor team,’ Professor McGonagall explained. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s just the build for a Seeker, too,’ said Wood, now walking around Harry and staring at him. ‘Light – speedy – we’ll have to get him a decent broom, Professor – a Nimbus Two Thousand or a Cleansweep Seven, I’d say.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I shall speak to Professor Dumbledore and see if we can’t bend the first-year rule. Heaven knows, we need a better team than last year.  <i class=\"calibre3\">Flattened</i> in that last match by Slytherin, I couldn’t look Severus Snape in the face for weeks …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall peered sternly over her glasses at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I want to hear you’re training hard, Potter, or I may change my mind about punishing you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then she suddenly smiled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your father would have been proud,’ she said. ‘He was an excellent Quidditch player himself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re  <i class=\"calibre3\">joking. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was dinner time. Harry had just finished telling Ron what had happened when he’d left the grounds with Professor McGonagall. Ron had a piece of steak-and-kidney pie halfway to his mouth, but he’d forgotten all about it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Seeker? </i>’ he said. ‘But first-years  <i class=\"calibre3\">never</i> – you must be the youngest house player in about –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– a century,’ said Harry, shovelling pie into his mouth. He felt particularly hungry after the excitement of the afternoon. ‘Wood told me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was so amazed, so impressed, he just sat and gaped at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I start training next week,’ said Harry. ‘Only don’t tell anyone, Wood wants to keep it a secret.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>114 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred and George Weasley now came into the hall, spotted Harry and hurried over. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well done,’ said George in a low voice. ‘Wood told us. We’re on the team too – Beaters.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I tell you, we’re going to win that Quidditch Cup for sure this year,’ said Fred. ‘We haven’t won since Charlie left, but this year’s team is going to be brilliant. You must be good, Harry, Wood was almost skipping when he told us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyway, we’ve got to go, Lee Jordan reckons he’s found a new secret passageway out of the school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bet it’s that one behind the statue of Gregory the Smarmy that we found in our first week. See you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred and George had hardly disappeared when someone far less welcome turned up: Malfoy, flanked by Crabbe and Goyle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Having a last meal, Potter? When are you getting the train back to the Muggles?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re a lot braver now you’re back on the ground and you’ve got your little friends with you,’ said Harry coolly. There was of course nothing at all little about Crabbe and Goyle, but as the High Table was full of teachers, neither of them could do more than crack their knuckles and scowl. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’d take you on any time on my own,’ said Malfoy. ‘Tonight, if you want. Wizard’s duel. Wands only – no contact. What’s the matter? Never heard of a wizard’s duel before, I suppose?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course he has,’ said Ron, wheeling round. ‘I’m his second, who’s yours?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy looked at Crabbe and Goyle, sizing them up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Crabbe,’ he said. ‘Midnight all right? We’ll meet you in the trophy room, that’s always unlocked.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Malfoy had gone, Ron and Harry looked at each other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What  <i class=\"calibre3\">is</i> a wizard’s duel?’ said Harry. ‘And what do you mean, you’re my second?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, a second’s there to take over if you die,’ said Ron casually, getting started at last on his cold pie. Catching the look on Harry’s face, he added quickly, ‘but people only die in proper duels, you know, with real wizards. The most you and Malfoy’ll be able to do is send sparks at each other. Neither of you knows enough magic to do any real damage. I bet he expected you to refuse, anyway.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what if I wave my wand and nothing happens?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Throw it away and punch him on the nose,’ Ron suggested. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Midnight Duel 115 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excuse me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They both looked up. It was Hermione Granger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t a person eat in peace in this place?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione ignored him and spoke to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I couldn’t help overhearing what you and Malfoy were saying –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bet you could,’ Ron muttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– and you  <i class=\"calibre3\">mustn’t</i> go wandering around the school at night, think of the points you’ll lose Gryffindor if you’re caught, and you’re bound to be. It’s really very selfish of you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And it’s really none of your business,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Goodbye,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All the same, it wasn’t what you’d call the perfect end to the day, Harry thought, as he lay awake much later listening to Dean and Seamus falling asleep (Neville wasn’t back from the hospital wing). Ron had spent all evening giving him advice such as ‘If he tries to curse you, you’d better dodge it, because I can’t remember how to block them’. There was a very good chance they were going to get caught by Filch or Mrs Norris, and Harry felt he was pushing his luck, breaking another school rule today. On the other hand, Malfoy’s sneering face kept looming up out of the darkness – this was his big chance to beat Malfoy, face to face. He couldn’t miss it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Half past eleven,’ Ron muttered at last. ‘We’d better go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They pulled on their dressing-gowns, picked up their wands and crept across the tower room, down the spiral staircase and into the Gryffindor common room. A few embers were still glowing in the fireplace, turning all the armchairs into hunched black shadows. They had almost reached the portrait hole when a voice spoke from the chair nearest them: ‘I can’t believe you’re going to do this, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A lamp flickered on. It was Hermione Granger, wearing a pink dressing-gown and a frown. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">You! </i>’ said Ron furiously. ‘Go back to bed!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I almost told your brother,’ Hermione snapped. ‘Percy – he’s a Prefect, he’d put a stop to this.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t believe anyone could be so interfering. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on,’ he said to Ron. He pushed open the portrait of the Fat Lady and climbed through the hole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione wasn’t going to give up that easily. She followed Ron </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>116 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">through the portrait hole, hissing at them like an angry goose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t you  <i class=\"calibre3\">care</i> about Gryffindor, do you  <i class=\"calibre3\">only</i> care about yourselves,  <i class=\"calibre3\">I </i> don’t want Slytherin to win the House Cup and you’ll lose all the points I got from Professor McGonagall for knowing about Switching Spells.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go away.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, but I warned you, you just remember what I said when you’re on the train home tomorrow, you’re so –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But what they were, they didn’t find out. Hermione had turned to the portrait of the Fat Lady to get back inside and found herself facing an empty painting. The Fat Lady had gone on a night-time visit and Hermione was locked out of Gryffindor Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now what am I going to do?’ she asked shrilly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s your problem,’ said Ron. ‘We’ve got to go, we’re going to be late.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They hadn’t even reached the end of the corridor when Hermione caught up with them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m coming with you,’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You are  <i class=\"calibre3\">not</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you think I’m going to stand out here and wait for Filch to catch me? If he finds all three of us I’ll tell him the truth, that I was trying to stop you and you can back me up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve got some nerve –’ said Ron loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up, both of you!’ said Harry sharply. ‘I heard something.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a sort of snuffling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mrs Norris?’ breathed Ron, squinting through the dark. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It wasn’t Mrs Norris. It was Neville. He was curled up on the floor, fast asleep, but jerked suddenly awake as they crept nearer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank goodness you found me! I’ve been out here for hours. I couldn’t remember the new password to get in to bed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Keep your voice down, Neville. The password’s “Pig snout” but it won’t help you now, the Fat Lady’s gone off somewhere.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000001999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How’s your arm?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fine,’ said Neville, showing them. ‘Madam Pomfrey mended it in about a minute.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good – well, look, Neville, we’ve got to be somewhere, we’ll see you later –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t leave me!’ said Neville, scrambling to his feet. ‘I don’t want to stay here alone, the Bloody Baron’s been past twice already.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron looked at his watch and then glared furiously at Hermione </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Midnight Duel 117 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If either of you get us caught, I’ll never rest until I’ve learnt that Curse of the Bogies Quirrell told us about and used it on you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione opened her mouth, perhaps to tell Ron exactly how to use the Curse of the Bogies, but Harry hissed at her to be quiet and beckoned them all forward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They flitted along corridors striped with bars of moonlight from the high windows. At every turn Harry expected to run into Filch or Mrs Norris, but they were lucky. They sped up a staircase to the third floor and tiptoed towards the trophy room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy and Crabbe weren’t there yet. The crystal trophy cases glimmered where the moonlight caught them. Cups, shields, plates and statues winked silver and gold in the darkness. They edged along the walls, keeping their eyes on the doors at either end of the room. Harry took out his wand in case Malfoy leapt in and started at once. The minutes crept by. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s late, maybe he’s chickened out,’ Ron whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then a noise in the next room made them jump. Harry had only just raised his wand when they heard someone speak – and it wasn’t Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sniff around, my sweet, they might be lurking in a corner.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Filch speaking to Mrs Norris. Horror-struck, Harry waved madly at the other three to follow him as quickly as possible; they scurried silently towards the door away from Filch’s voice. Neville’s robes had barely whipped round the corner when they heard Filch enter the trophy room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re in here somewhere,’ they heard him mutter, ‘probably hiding.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This way!’ Harry mouthed to the others and, petrified, they began to creep down a long gallery full of suits of armour. They could hear Filch getting nearer. Neville suddenly let out a frightened squeak and broke into a run – he tripped, grabbed Ron around the waist and the pair of them toppled right into a suit of armour. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The clanging and crashing were enough to wake the whole castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘RUN!’ Harry yelled and the four of them sprinted down the gallery, not looking back to see whether Filch was following –  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they swung around the doorpost and galloped down one corridor then another, Harry in the lead without any idea where they were </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>118 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">or where they were going. They ripped through a tapestry and found themselves in a hidden passageway, hurtled along it and came out near their Charms classroom, which they knew was miles from the trophy room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think we’ve lost him,’ Harry panted, leaning against the cold wall and wiping his forehead. Neville was bent double, wheezing and spluttering. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I –  <i class=\"calibre3\">told</i> – you,’ Hermione gasped, clutching at the stitch in her chest. ‘I – told – you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got to get back to Gryffindor Tower,’ said Ron, ‘quickly as possible.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy tricked you,’ Hermione said to Harry. ‘You realise that, don’t you? He was never going to meet you – Filch knew someone was going to be in the trophy room, Malfoy must have tipped him off.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry thought she was probably right, but he wasn’t going to tell her that. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It wasn’t going to be that simple. They hadn’t gone more than a dozen paces when a doorknob rattled and something came shooting out of a classroom in front of them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Peeves. He caught sight of them and gave a squeal of delight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up, Peeves – please – you’ll get us thrown out.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peeves cackled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wandering around at midnight, ickle firsties? Tut, tut, tut. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Naughty, naughty, you’ll get caughty.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not if you don’t give us away, Peeves, please.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Should tell Filch, I should,’ said Peeves in a saintly voice, but his eyes glittered wickedly. ‘It’s for your own good, you know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out of the way,’ snapped Ron, taking a swipe at Peeves – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">this was a big mistake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘STUDENTS OUT OF BED!’ Peeves bellowed. ‘STUDENTS </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">OUT OF BED DOWN THE CHARMS CORRIDOR!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ducking under Peeves they ran for their lives, right to the end of the corridor, where they slammed into a door – and it was locked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is it!’ Ron moaned, as they pushed helplessly at the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re done for! This is the end!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They could hear footsteps, Filch running as fast as he could </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Midnight Duel 119 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">towards Peeves’s shouts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, move over,’ Hermione snarled. She grabbed Harry’s wand, tapped the lock and whispered, ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Alohomora! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The lock clicked and the door swung open – they piled through it, shut it quickly and pressed their ears against it, listening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Which way did they go, Peeves?’ Filch was saying. ‘Quick, tell me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Say “please”.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t mess me about, Peeves, now  <i class=\"calibre3\">where did they go? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shan’t say nothing if you don’t say please,’ said Peeves in his annoying sing-song voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right –  <i class=\"calibre3\">please. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘NOTHING! Ha haaa! Told you I wouldn’t say nothing if you didn’t say please! Ha ha! Haaaaaa!’ And they heard the sound of Peeves whooshing away and Filch cursing in rage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He thinks this door is locked,’ Harry whispered. ‘I think we’ll be OK – get  <i class=\"calibre3\">off, </i> Neville!’ For Neville had been tugging on the sleeve of Harry’s dressing-gown for the last minute. ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">What? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned around – and saw, quite clearly, what. For a moment, he was sure he’d walked into a nightmare – this was too much, on top of everything that had happened so far. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They  weren’t  in  a  room,  as  he  had  supposed.  They  were  in  a corridor. The forbidden corridor on the third floor. And now they knew why it was forbidden. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were looking straight into the eyes of a monstrous dog, a dog which filled the whole space between ceiling and floor. It had three heads. Three pairs of rolling, mad eyes; three noses, twitching and quivering in their direction; three drooling mouths, saliva hanging in slippery ropes from yellowish fangs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was standing quite still, all six eyes staring at them, and Harry knew that the only reason they weren’t already dead was that their sudden appearance had taken it by surprise, but it was quickly getting over that, there was no mistaking what those thunderous growls meant. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry groped for the doorknob – between Filch and death, he’d take Filch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They fell backwards – Harry slammed the door shut, and they ran, they almost flew, back down the corridor. Filch must have hurried off to look for them somewhere else because they didn’t see him anywhere, but they hardly cared – all they wanted to do </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>120 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">was put as much space as possible between them and that monster. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They didn’t stop running until they reached the portrait of the Fat Lady on the seventh floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where on earth have you all been?’ she asked, looking at their dressing-gowns hanging off their shoulders and their flushed, sweaty faces. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Never mind that – pig snout, pig snout,’ panted Harry, and the portrait swung forward. They scrambled into the common room and collapsed, trembling into armchairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a while before any of them said anything. Neville, indeed, looked as if he’d never speak again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What do they think they’re doing, keeping a thing like that locked up in a school?’ said Ron finally. ‘If any dog needs exercise, that one does.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione had got both her breath and her bad temper back again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t use your eyes, any of you, do you?’ she snapped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Didn’t you see what it was standing on?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The floor?’ Harry suggested. ‘I wasn’t looking at its feet, I was too busy with its heads.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,  <i class=\"calibre3\">not</i> the floor. It was standing on a trapdoor. It’s obviously guarding something.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She stood up, glaring at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I hope you’re pleased with yourselves. We could all have been killed – or worse, expelled. Now, if you don’t mind, I’m going to bed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron stared after her, his mouth open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, we don’t mind,’ he said. ‘You’d think we dragged her along, wouldn’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hermione had given Harry something else to think about as he climbed back into bed. The dog was guarding something … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What had Hagrid said? Gringotts was the safest place in the world for something you wanted to hide – except perhaps Hogwarts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It looked as though Harry had found out where the grubby little package from vault seven hundred and thirteen was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER TEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Hallowe’en </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy couldn’t believe his eyes when he saw that Harry and Ron were still at Hogwarts next day, looking tired but perfectly cheerful. Indeed, by next morning Harry and Ron thought that meeting the three-headed dog had been an excellent adventure and they were quite keen to have another one. In the meantime, Harry filled Ron in about the package that seemed to have been moved from Gringotts to Hogwarts, and they spent a lot of time wondering what could possibly need such heavy protection. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s either really valuable or really dangerous,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Or both,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But as all they knew for sure about the mysterious object was that it was about two inches long, they didn’t have much chance of guessing what it was without further clues. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neither Neville or Hermione showed the slightest interest in what lay underneath the dog and the trapdoor. All Neville cared about was never going near the dog again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione was now refusing to speak to Harry and Ron, but she was such a bossy know-it-all that they saw this as an added bonus. All they really wanted now was a way of getting back at Malfoy, and to their great delight, just such a thing arrived with the post about a week later. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the owls flooded into the Great Hall as usual, everyone’s attention was caught at once by a long thin package carried by six large screech owls. Harry was just as interested as everyone else to see what was in this large parcel and was amazed when the owls soared down and dropped it right in front of him, knocking his bacon to the floor. They had hardly fluttered out of the way when another owl dropped a letter on top of the parcel. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ripped open the letter first, which was lucky, because it said: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>122 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">DO NOT OPEN THE PARCEL AT THE TABLE. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">It contains your new Nimbus Two Thousand,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">but I don’t want everybody knowing you’ve</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">got a broomstick or they’ll all want one. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Oliver Wood will meet you tonight on the</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Quidditch pitch at seven o’clock for your</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">first training session. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Professor M. McGonagall</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had difficulty hiding his glee as he handed the note to Ron to read. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A Nimbus Two Thousand!’ Ron moaned enviously. ‘I’ve never even  <i class=\"calibre3\">touched</i> one.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They left the Hall quickly, wanting to unwrap the broomstick in private before their first lesson, but halfway across the Entrance Hall they found the way upstairs barred by Crabbe and Goyle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy seized the package from Harry and felt it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s a broomstick,’ he said, throwing it back to Harry with a mixture of jealousy and spite on his face. ‘You’ll be for it this time, Potter, first-years aren’t allowed them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron couldn’t resist it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not any old broomstick,’ he said, ‘it’s a Nimbus Two Thousand. What did you say you’ve got at home, Malfoy, a Comet Two Sixty?’ Ron grinned at Harry. ‘Comets look flashy, but they’re not in the same league as the Nimbus.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What would you know about it, Weasley, you couldn’t afford half the handle,’ Malfoy snapped back. ‘I suppose you and your brothers have to save up, twig by twig.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before Ron could answer, Professor Flitwick appeared at Malfoy’s elbow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not arguing, I hope, boys?’ he squeaked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter’s been sent a broomstick, Professor,’ said Malfoy quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, yes, that’s right,’ said Professor Flitwick, beaming at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor McGonagall told me all about the special circumstances, Potter. And what model is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A Nimbus Two Thousand, sir,’ said Harry, fighting not to laugh at the look of horror on Malfoy’s face. ‘And it’s really thanks to Malfoy here that I’ve got it,’ he added. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron headed upstairs, smothering their laughter at Malfoy’s obvious rage and confusion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hallowe’en 123 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, it’s true,’ Harry chortled as they reached the top of the marble staircase. ‘If he hadn’t stolen Neville’s Remembrall I wouldn’t be in the team …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So I suppose you think that’s a reward for breaking rules?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">came an angry voice from just behind them. Hermione was stomping up the stairs looking disapprovingly at the package in Harry’s hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I thought you weren’t speaking to us?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, don’t stop now,’ said Ron, ‘it’s doing us so much good.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione marched away with her nose in the air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had a lot of trouble keeping his mind on his lessons that day. It kept wandering up to the dormitory, where his new broomstick was lying under his bed, or straying off to the Quidditch pitch where he’d be learning to play that night. He bolted his dinner that evening without noticing what he was eating and then rushed upstairs with Ron to unwrap the Nimbus Two Thousand at last. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wow,’ Ron sighed, as the broomstick rolled on to Harry’s bed-spread. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Even Harry, who knew nothing about the different brooms, thought it looked wonderful. Sleek and shiny, with a mahogany handle, it had a long tail of neat, straight twigs and  <i class=\"calibre3\">Nimbus Two</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Thousand</i> written in gold near the top. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As seven o’clock drew nearer, Harry left the castle and set off towards the Quidditch pitch in the dusk. He’d never been inside the stadium before. Hundreds of seats were raised in stands around the pitch so that the spectators were high enough to see what was going on. At either end of the pitch were three golden poles with hoops on the end. They reminded Harry of the little plastic sticks Muggle children blew bubbles through, except that they were fifty feet high. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Too eager to fly again to wait for Wood, Harry mounted his broomstick and kicked off from the ground. What a feeling – he swooped in and out of the goalposts and then sped up and down the pitch. The Nimbus Two Thousand turned wherever he wanted at his lightest touch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hey, Potter, come down!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Oliver Wood had arrived. He was carrying a large wooden crate under his arm. Harry landed next to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very nice,’ said Wood, his eyes glinting. ‘I see what </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>124 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">McGonagall meant … you really are a natural. I’m just going to teach you the rules this evening, then you’ll be joining team practice three times a week.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He opened the crate. Inside were four different-sized balls. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Wood. ‘Now, Quidditch is easy enough to understand, even if it’s not too easy to play. There are seven players on each side. Three of them are called Chasers.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Three Chasers,’ Harry repeated, as Wood took out a bright red ball about the size of a football. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This ball’s called the Quaffle,’ said Wood. ‘The Chasers throw the Quaffle to each other and try and get it through one of the hoops to score a goal. Ten points every time the Quaffle goes through one of the hoops. Follow me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Chasers throw the Quaffle and put it through the hoops to score,’ Harry recited. ‘So – that’s sort of like basketball on broomsticks with six hoops, isn’t it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s basketball?’ said Wood curiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Never mind,’ said Harry quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, there’s another player on each side who’s called the Keeper – I’m Keeper for Gryffindor. I have to fly around our hoops and stop the other team from scoring.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Three Chasers, one Keeper,’ said Harry, who was determined to remember it all. ‘And they play with the Quaffle. OK, got that. So what are they for?’ He pointed at the three balls left inside the box. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll show you now,’ said Wood. ‘Take this.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He handed Harry a small club, a bit like a rounders bat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going to show you what the Bludgers do,’ Wood said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘These two are the Bludgers.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He showed Harry two identical balls, jet black and slightly smaller than the red Quaffle. Harry noticed that they seemed to be straining to escape the straps holding them inside the box. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stand back,’ Wood warned Harry. He bent down and freed one of the Bludgers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At once, the black ball rose high in the air and then pelted straight  at  Harry’s  face.  Harry  swung  at  it  with  the  bat  to  stop  it breaking his nose and sent it zig-zagging away into the air – it zoomed around their heads and then shot at Wood, who dived on top of it and managed to pin it to the ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See?’ Wood panted, forcing the struggling Bludger back into </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hallowe’en 125 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the crate and strapping it down safely. ‘The Bludgers rocket around trying to knock players off their brooms. That’s why you have two Beaters on each team. The Weasley twins are ours – it’s their job to protect their side from the Bludgers and try and knock them towards the other team. So – think you’ve got all that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Three Chasers try and score with the Quaffle; the Keeper guards the goalposts; the Beaters keep the Bludgers away from their team,’ Harry reeled off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very good,’ said Wood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – have the Bludgers ever killed anyone?’ Harry asked, hoping he sounded offhand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Never at Hogwarts. We’ve had a couple of broken jaws but nothing worse than that. Now, the last member of the team is the Seeker. That’s you. And you don’t have to worry about the Quaffle or the Bludgers –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– unless they crack my head open.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t worry, the Weasleys are more than a match for the Bludgers – I mean, they’re like a pair of human Bludgers themselves.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood reached into the crate and took out the fourth and last ball. Compared with the Quaffle and the Bludgers, it was tiny, about the size of a large walnut. It was bright gold and had little fluttering silver wings. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">This</i>,’ said Wood, ‘is the Golden Snitch, and it’s the most important ball of the lot. It’s very hard to catch because it’s so fast and difficult to see. It’s the Seeker’s job to catch it. You’ve got to weave in and out of the Chasers, Beaters, Bludgers and Quaffle to get it before the other team’s Seeker, because whichever Seeker catches the Snitch wins his team an extra hundred and fifty points, so they nearly always win. That’s why Seekers get fouled so much. A game of Quidditch only ends when the Snitch is caught, so it can go on for ages – I think the record is three months, they had to keep bringing on substitutes so the players could get some sleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, that’s it – any questions?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shook his head. He understood what he had to do all right, it was doing it that was going to be the problem. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We won’t practise with the Snitch yet,’ said Wood, carefully shutting it back inside the crate. ‘It’s too dark, we might lose it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Let’s try you out with a few of these.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>126 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled a bag of ordinary golf balls out of his pocket, and a few minutes later, he and Harry were up in the air, Wood throwing the golf balls as hard as he could in every direction for Harry to catch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t miss a single one, and Wood was delighted. After half an hour, night had really fallen and they couldn’t carry on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That Quidditch Cup’ll have our name on it this year,’ said Wood happily as they trudged back up to the castle. ‘I wouldn’t be surprised if you turn out better than Charlie Weasley, and he could have played for England if he hadn’t gone off chasing dragons.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps it was because he was now so busy, what with Quidditch practice three evenings a week on top of all his homework, but Harry could hardly believe it when he realised that he’d already been at Hogwarts two months. The castle felt more like home than Privet Drive had ever done. His lessons, too, were becoming more and more interesting now that they had mastered the basics. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On Hallowe’en morning they woke to the delicious smell of bak-ing pumpkin wafting through the corridors. Even better, Professor Flitwick announced in Charms that he thought they were ready to start making objects fly, something they had all been dying to try since they’d seen him make Neville’s toad zoom around the classroom. Professor Flitwick put the class into pairs to practise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s partner was Seamus Finnigan (which was a relief, because Neville had been trying to catch his eye). Ron, however, was to be working with Hermione Granger. It was hard to tell whether Ron or Hermione was angrier about this. She hadn’t spoken to either of them since the day Harry’s broomstick had arrived. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, don’t forget that nice wrist movement we’ve been practising!’ squeaked Professor Flitwick, perched on top of his pile of books as usual. ‘Swish and flick, remember, swish and flick. And saying the magic words properly is very important, too – never forget Wizard Baruffio, who said ‘s’ instead of ‘f’ and found himself on the floor with a buffalo on his chest.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was very difficult. Harry and Seamus swished and flicked, but the feather they were supposed to be sending skywards just lay on the desktop. Seamus got so impatient that he prodded it with his wand and set fire to it – Harry had to put it out with his hat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hallowe’en 127 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron, at the next table, wasn’t having much more luck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Wingardium Leviosa! </i>’ he shouted, waving his long arms like a windmill. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re saying it wrong,’ Harry heard Hermione snap. ‘It’s Wing-gar-dium Levi- <i class=\"calibre3\">o</i>-sa, make the “gar” nice and long.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You do it, then, if you’re so clever,’ Ron snarled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione rolled up the sleeves of her gown, flicked her wand and said, ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Wingardium Leviosa! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Their feather rose off the desk and hovered about four feet above their heads. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, well done!’ cried Professor Flitwick, clapping. ‘Everyone see here, Miss Granger’s done it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was in a very bad temper by the end of the class. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s no wonder no one can stand her,’ he said to Harry as they pushed their way into the crowded corridor. ‘She’s a nightmare, honestly.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Someone  knocked  into  Harry  as  they  hurried  past  him.  It  was Hermione. Harry caught a glimpse of her face – and was startled to see that she was in tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think she heard you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So?’ said Ron, but he looked a bit uncomfortable. ‘She must’ve noticed she’s got no friends.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione didn’t turn up for the next class and wasn’t seen all afternoon. On their way down to the Great Hall for the Hallowe’en feast, Harry and Ron overheard Parvati Patil telling her friend Lavender that Hermione was crying in the girls’ toilets and wanted to be left alone. Ron looked still more awkward at this, but a moment later they had entered the Great Hall, where the Hallowe’en decorations put Hermione out of their minds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A thousand live bats fluttered from the walls and ceiling while a thousand more swooped over the tables in low black clouds, making the candles in the pumpkins stutter. The feast appeared suddenly on the golden plates, as it had at the start-of-term banquet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was just helping himself to a jacket potato when Professor Quirrell came sprinting into the Hall, his turban askew and terror on his face. Everyone stared as he reached Professor Dumbledore’s chair, slumped against the table and gasped, ‘Troll – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">in the dungeons – thought you ought to know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He then sank to the floor in a dead faint. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>128 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was uproar. It took several purple firecrackers exploding from the end of Professor Dumbledore’s wand to bring silence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Prefects,’ he rumbled, ‘lead your houses back to the dormitories immediately!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy was in his element. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Follow me! Stick together, first-years! No need to fear the troll if you follow my orders! Stay close behind me, now. Make way, first-years coming through! Excuse me, I’m a Prefect!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How could a troll get in?’ Harry asked as they climbed the stairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t ask me, they’re supposed to be really stupid,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe Peeves let it in for a Hallowe’en joke.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They passed different groups of people hurrying in different directions. As they jostled their way through a crowd of confused Hufflepuffs, Harry suddenly grabbed Ron’s arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve just thought – Hermione.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about her?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She doesn’t know about the troll.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron bit his lip. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, all right,’ he snapped. ‘But Percy’d better not see us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ducking down, they joined the Hufflepuffs going the other way, slipped down a deserted side corridor and hurried off towards the girls’ toilets. They had just turned the corner when they heard quick footsteps behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Percy!’ hissed Ron, pulling Harry behind a large stone griffin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peering around it, however, they saw not Percy but Snape. He crossed the corridor and disappeared from view. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s he doing?’ Harry whispered. ‘Why isn’t he down in the dungeons with the rest of the teachers?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Search me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quietly as possible, they crept along the next corridor after Snape’s fading footsteps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s heading for the third floor,’ Harry said, but Ron held up his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you smell something?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sniffed and a foul stench reached his nostrils, a mixture of old socks and the kind of public toilet no one seems to clean. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then they heard it – a low grunting and the shuffling foot-falls of gigantic feet. Ron pointed: at the end of a passage to the left, something huge was moving towards them. They shrank into </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hallowe’en 129 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the shadows and watched as it emerged into a patch of moonlight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a horrible sight. Twelve feet tall, its skin was a dull, gran-ite grey, its great lumpy body like a boulder with its small bald head perched on top like a coconut. It had short legs thick as tree trunks with flat, horny feet. The smell coming from it was incredible. It was holding a huge wooden club, which dragged along the floor because its arms were so long. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The troll stopped next to a doorway and peered inside. It wag-gled its long ears, making up its tiny mind, then slouched slowly into the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The key’s in the lock,’ Harry muttered. ‘We could lock it in.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good idea,’ said Ron nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They edged towards the open door, mouths dry, praying the troll wasn’t about to come out of it. With one great leap, Harry managed to grab the key, slam the door and lock it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Yes! </i>’ <i class=\"calibre3\"> </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flushed with their victory they started to run back up the passage, but as they reached the corner they heard something that made their hearts stop – a high, petrified scream – and it was coming from the chamber they’d just locked up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, no,’ said Ron, pale as the Bloody Baron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s the girls’ toilets!’ Harry gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Hermione! </i>’ they said together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was the last thing they wanted to do, but what choice did they have? Wheeling around they sprinted back to the door and turned the key, fumbling in their panic – Harry pulled the door open – they ran inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione Granger was shrinking against the wall opposite, looking as if she was about to faint. The troll was advancing on her, knocking the sinks off the walls as it went. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Confuse it!’ Harry said desperately to Ron, and seizing a tap he threw it as hard as he could against the wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The troll stopped a few feet from Hermione. It lumbered around, blinking stupidly, to see what had made the noise. Its mean little eyes saw Harry. It hesitated, then made for him instead, lifting its club as it went. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oy, pea-brain!’ yelled Ron from the other side of the chamber, and he threw a metal pipe at it. The troll didn’t even seem to notice the pipe hitting its shoulder, but it heard the yell and paused again, turning its ugly snout towards Ron instead, giving </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>130 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry time to run around it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, run,  <i class=\"calibre3\">run! </i>’ Harry yelled at Hermione, trying to pull her towards the door, but she couldn’t move, she was still flat against the wall, her mouth open with terror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The shouting and the echoes seemed to be driving the troll berserk. It roared again and started towards Ron, who was nearest and had no way to escape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry then did something that was both very brave and very stupid: he took a great running jump and managed to fasten his arms around the troll’s neck from behind. The troll couldn’t feel Harry hanging there, but even a troll will notice if you stick a long bit of wood up its nose, and Harry’s wand had still been in his hand when he’d jumped – it had gone straight up one of the troll’s nostrils. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Howling with pain, the troll twisted and flailed its club, with Harry clinging on for dear life; any second, the troll was going to rip him off or catch him a terrible blow with the club. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione had sunk to the floor in fright; Ron pulled out his own wand – not knowing what he was going to do he heard himself cry the first spell that came into his head: ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Wingardium</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Leviosa! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The club flew suddenly out of the troll’s hand, rose high, high up into the air, turned slowly over – and dropped, with a sickening crack, on to its owner’s head. The troll swayed on the spot and then fell flat on its face, with a thud that made the whole room tremble. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry got to his feet. He was shaking and out of breath. Ron was standing there with his wand still raised, staring at what he had done. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Hermione who spoke first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is it – dead?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t think so,’ said Harry. ‘I think it’s just been knocked out.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He bent down and pulled his wand out of the troll’s nose. It was covered in what looked like lumpy grey glue. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Urgh – troll bogies.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He wiped it on the troll’s trousers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A sudden slamming and loud footsteps made the three of them look up. They hadn’t realised what a racket they had been making, but of course, someone downstairs must have heard the crashes and the troll’s roars. A moment later, Professor </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hallowe’en 131 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">McGonagall had come bursting into the room, closely followed by Snape, with Quirrell bringing up the rear. Quirrell took one look at the troll, let out a faint whimper and sat quickly down on a toilet, clutching his heart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape bent over the troll. Professor McGonagall was looking at Ron and Harry. Harry had never seen her look so angry. Her lips were white. Hopes of winning fifty points for Gryffindor faded quickly from Harry’s mind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What on earth were you thinking of?’ said Professor McGonagall,  with  cold  fury  in  her  voice.  Harry  looked  at  Ron, who was still standing with his wand in the air. ‘You’re lucky you weren’t killed. Why aren’t you in your dormitory?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape gave Harry a swift, piercing look. Harry looked at the floor. He wished Ron would put his wand down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then a small voice came out of the shadows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please, Professor McGonagall – they were looking for me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Miss Granger!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione had managed to get to her feet at last. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I went looking for the troll because I – I thought I could deal with it on my own – you know, because I’ve read all about them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron dropped his wand. Hermione Granger, telling a downright lie to a teacher? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If they hadn’t found me, I’d be dead now. Harry stuck his wand up its nose and Ron knocked it out with its own club. They didn’t have time to come and fetch anyone. It was about to finish me off when they arrived.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron tried to look as though this story wasn’t new to them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – in that case …’ said Professor McGonagall, staring at the three of them. ‘Miss Granger, you foolish girl, how could you think of tackling a mountain troll on your own?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione hung her head. Harry was speechless. Hermione was the last person to do anything against the rules, and here she was, pretending she had, to get them out of trouble. It was as if Snape had started handing out sweets. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Miss Granger, five points will be taken from Gryffindor for this,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘I’m very disappointed in you. If you’re not hurt at all, you’d better get off to Gryffindor Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Students are finishing the feast in their houses.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>132 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall turned to Harry and Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I still say you were lucky, but not many first-years could have taken on a full-grown mountain troll. You each win Gryffindor five points. Professor Dumbledore will be informed of this. You may go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They hurried out of the chamber and didn’t speak at all until they had climbed two floors up. It was a relief to be away from the smell of the troll, quite apart from anything else. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We should have got more than ten points,’ Ron grumbled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Five, you mean, once she’s taken off Hermione’s.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good of her to get us out of trouble like that,’ Ron admitted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mind you, we  <i class=\"calibre3\">did</i> save her.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She might not have needed saving if we hadn’t locked the thing in with her,’ Harry reminded him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had reached the portrait of the Fat Lady. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pig snout,’ they said and entered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The common room was packed and noisy. Everyone was eating the food that had been sent up. Hermione, however, stood alone by the door, waiting for them. There was a very embarrassed pause. Then, none of them looking at each other, they all said </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thanks’, and hurried off to get plates. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But from that moment on, Hermione Granger became their friend. There are some things you can’t share without ending up liking each other, and knocking out a twelve-foot mountain troll is one of them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER ELEVEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Quidditch </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As they entered November, the weather turned very cold. The mountains around the school became icy grey and the lake like chilled steel. Every morning the ground was covered in frost. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid could be seen from the upstairs windows, defrosting broomsticks on the Quidditch pitch, bundled up in a long moleskin overcoat, rabbit-fur gloves and enormous beaverskin boots. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Quidditch season had begun. On Saturday, Harry would be playing in his first match after weeks of training: Gryffindor ver-sus Slytherin. If Gryffindor won, they would move up into second place in the House Championship. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hardly anyone had seen Harry play because Wood had decided that, as their secret weapon, Harry should be kept, well, secret. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the news that he was playing Seeker had leaked out somehow, and Harry didn’t know which was worse – people telling him he’d be brilliant or people telling him they’d be running around underneath him, holding a mattress. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was really lucky that Harry now had Hermione as a friend. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He didn’t know how he’d have got through all his homework without her, what with all the last-minute Quidditch practice Wood was making them do. She had also lent him  <i class=\"calibre3\">Quidditch</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">through the Ages</i>, which turned out to be a very interesting read. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry learnt that there were seven hundred ways of committing a Quidditch foul and that all of them had happened during a World Cup match in 1473; that Seekers were usually the smallest and fastest players and that most serious Quidditch accidents seemed to happen to them; that although people rarely died playing Quidditch, referees had been known to vanish and turn up months later in the Sahara Desert. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione had become a bit more relaxed about breaking rules since Harry and Ron had saved her from the mountain troll and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>134 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">she was much nicer for it. The day before Harry’s first Quidditch match the three of them were out in the freezing courtyard during break, and she had conjured them up a bright blue fire which could be carried around in a jam jar. They were standing with their backs to it, getting warm, when Snape crossed the yard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry noticed at once that Snape was limping. Harry, Ron and Hermione moved closer together to block the fire from view; they were sure it wouldn’t be allowed. Unfortunately, something about their guilty faces caught Snape’s eye. He limped over. He hadn’t seen the fire, but he seemed to be looking for a reason to tell them off anyway. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that you’ve got there, Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was  <i class=\"calibre3\">Quidditch through the Ages. </i> Harry showed him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Library books are not to be taken outside the school,’ said Snape. ‘Give it to me. Five points from Gryffindor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s just made that rule up,’ Harry muttered angrily as Snape limped away. ‘Wonder what’s wrong with his leg?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno, but I hope it’s really hurting him,’ said Ron bitterly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindor common room was very noisy that evening. Harry, Ron and Hermione sat together next to a window. Hermione was checking Harry and Ron’s Charms homework for them. She would never let them copy (‘How will you learn?’), but by asking her to read it through, they got the right answers anyway. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt restless. He wanted  <i class=\"calibre3\">Quidditch through the Ages</i> back, to take his mind off his nerves about tomorrow. Why should he be afraid of Snape? Getting up, he told Ron and Hermione he was going to ask Snape if he could have it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rather you than me,’ they said together, but Harry had an idea that Snape wouldn’t refuse if there were other teachers listening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He made his way down to the staff room and knocked. There was no answer. He knocked again. Nothing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps Snape had left the book in there? It was worth a try. He pushed the door ajar and peered inside – and a horrible scene met his eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape and Filch were inside, alone. Snape was holding his robes above his knees. One of his legs was bloody and mangled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filch was handing Snape bandages. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Blasted thing,’ Snape was saying. ‘How are you supposed to keep your eyes on all three heads at once?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quidditch 135 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to shut the door quietly, but – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘POTTER!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s face was twisted with fury as he dropped his robes quickly to hide his leg. Harry gulped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I just wondered if I could have my book back.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘GET OUT!  <i class=\"calibre3\">OUT! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry left, before Snape could take any more points from Gryffindor. He sprinted back upstairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you get it?’ Ron asked as Harry joined them. ‘What’s the matter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In a low whisper, Harry told them what he’d seen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know what this means?’ he finished breathlessly. ‘He tried to get past that three-headed dog at Hallowe’en! That’s where he was going when we saw him – he’s after whatever it’s guarding! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And I’d bet my broomstick  <i class=\"calibre3\">he</i> let that troll in, to create a diversion!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s eyes were wide. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No – he wouldn’t,’ she said. ‘I know he’s not very nice, but he wouldn’t try and steal something Dumbledore was keeping safe.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Honestly, Hermione, you think all teachers are saints or something,’ snapped Ron. ‘I’m with Harry. I wouldn’t put anything past Snape. But what’s he after? What’s that dog guarding?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went to bed with his head buzzing with the same question. Neville was snoring loudly, but Harry couldn’t sleep. He tried to empty his mind – he needed to sleep, he had to, he had his first Quidditch match in a few hours – but the expression on Snape’s face when Harry had seen his leg wasn’t easy to forget. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The next morning dawned very bright and cold. The Great Hall was full of the delicious smell of fried sausages and the cheerful chatter of everyone looking forward to a good Quidditch match. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve got to eat some breakfast.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t want anything.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just a bit of toast,’ wheedled Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not hungry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt terrible. In an hour’s time he’d be walking on to the pitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, you need your strength,’ said Seamus Finnigan. ‘Seekers are always the ones who get nobbled by the other team.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thanks, Seamus,’ said Harry, watching Seamus pile ketchup on his sausages. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>136 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">By eleven o’clock the whole school seemed to be out in the stands around the Quidditch pitch. Many students had binoculars. The seats might be raised high in the air but it was still difficult to see what was going on sometimes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione joined Neville, Seamus and Dean the West Ham fan up in the top row. As a surprise for Harry, they had painted a large banner on one of the sheets Scabbers had ruined. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It said  <i class=\"calibre3\">Potter for President</i> and Dean, who was good at drawing, had done a large Gryffindor lion underneath. Then Hermione had performed a tricky little charm so that the paint flashed different colours. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Meanwhile, in the changing rooms, Harry and the rest of the team were changing into their scarlet Quidditch robes (Slytherin would be playing in green). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood cleared his throat for silence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK, men,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And women,’ said Chaser Angelina Johnson. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And women,’ Wood agreed. ‘This is it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The big one,’ said Fred Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The one we’ve all been waiting for,’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We know Oliver’s speech by heart,’ Fred told Harry. ‘We were in the team last year.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up, you two,’ said Wood. ‘This is the best team Gryffindor’s had in years. We’re going to win. I know it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He glared at them all as if to say, ‘Or else.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right. It’s time. Good luck, all of you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry followed Fred and George out of the changing room and, hoping his knees weren’t going to give way, walked on to the pitch to loud cheers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch was refereeing. She stood in the middle of the pitch, waiting for the two teams, her broom in her hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, I want a nice fair game, all of you,’ she said, once they were all gathered around her. Harry noticed that she seemed to be speaking particularly to the Slytherin captain, Marcus Flint, a fifth-year. Harry thought Flint looked as if he had some troll blood in him. Out of the corner of his eye he saw the fluttering banner high above, flashing  <i class=\"calibre3\">Potter for President</i> over the crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His heart skipped. He felt braver. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mount your brooms, please.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry clambered on to his Nimbus Two Thousand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quidditch 137 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch gave a loud blast on her silver whistle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fifteen brooms rose up, high, high into the air. They were off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And the Quaffle is taken immediately by Angelina Johnson of Gryffindor – what an excellent Chaser that girl is, and rather attractive, too –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘JORDAN!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry, Professor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Weasley twins’ friend, Lee Jordan, was doing the commen-tary for the match, closely watched by Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And she’s really belting along up there, a neat pass to Alicia Spinnet, a good find of Oliver Wood’s, last year only a reserve – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">back to Johnson and – no, Slytherin have taken the Quaffle, Slytherin captain Marcus Flint gains the Quaffle and off he goes – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flint flying like an eagle up there – he’s going to sc– no, stopped by an excellent move by Gryffindor Keeper Wood and Gryffindor take the Quaffle – that’s Chaser Katie Bell of Gryffindor there, nice dive around Flint, off up the field and – OUCH – that must have hurt, hit in the back of the head by a Bludger – Quaffle taken by Slytherin – that’s Adrian Pucey speeding off towards the goalposts, but he’s blocked by a second Bludger – sent his way by Fred or George Weasley, can’t tell which – nice play by the Gryffindor Beater, anyway, and Johnson back in possession of the Quaffle, a clear field ahead and off she goes – she’s really flying – dodges a speeding Bludger – the goalposts are ahead – come on, now, Angelina – Keeper Bletchley dives – misses – GRYFFINDOR </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">SCORE!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor cheers filled the cold air, with howls and moans from the Slytherins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Budge up there, move along.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione squeezed together to give Hagrid enough space to join them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bin watchin’ from me hut,’ said Hagrid, patting a large pair of binoculars round his neck, ‘But it isn’t the same as bein’ in the crowd. No sign of the Snitch yet, eh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nope,’ said Ron. ‘Harry hasn’t had much to do yet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Kept outta trouble, though, that’s somethin’,’ said Hagrid, raising his binoculars and peering skywards at the speck that was Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Way up above them, Harry was gliding over the game, squinting </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>138 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">about for some sign of the Snitch. This was part of his and Wood’s game plan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Keep out of the way until you catch sight of the Snitch,’ Wood had said. ‘We don’t want you attacked before you have to be.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Angelina had scored, Harry had done a couple of loop-the-loops to let out his feelings. Now he was back to staring around for the Snitch. Once he caught sight of a flash of gold but it was just a reflection from one of the Weasleys’ wristwatches, and once a Bludger decided to come pelting his way, more like a cannon ball than anything, but Harry dodged it and Fred Weasley came chasing after it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right there, Harry?’ he had time to yell, as he beat the Bludger furiously towards Marcus Flint. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Slytherin in possession,’ Lee Jordan was saying. ‘Chaser Pucey ducks two Bludgers, two Weasleys and Chaser Bell and speeds towards the – wait a moment – was that the Snitch?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A murmur ran through the crowd as Adrian Pucey dropped the Quaffle, too busy looking over his shoulder at the flash of gold that had passed his left ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry saw it. In a great rush of excitement he dived downwards after the streak of gold. Slytherin Seeker Terence Higgs had seen it, too. Neck and neck they hurtled towards the Snitch – all the Chasers seemed to have forgotten what they were supposed to be doing as they hung in mid-air to watch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was faster than Higgs – he could see the little round ball, wings fluttering, darting up ahead – he put on an extra spurt of speed – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">WHAM! A roar of rage echoed from the Gryffindors below – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Marcus Flint had blocked Harry on purpose and Harry’s broom span off course, Harry holding on for dear life. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Foul!’ screamed the Gryffindors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch spoke angrily to Flint and then ordered a free shot at the goalposts for Gryffindor. But in all the confusion, of course, the Golden Snitch had disappeared from sight again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Down in the stands, Dean Thomas was yelling, ‘Send him off, ref! Red card!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This isn’t football, Dean,’ Ron reminded him. ‘You can’t send people off in Quidditch – and what’s a red card?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hagrid was on Dean’s side. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They oughta change the rules, Flint coulda knocked Harry outta the air.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quidditch 139 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lee Jordan was finding it difficult not to take sides. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So – after that obvious and disgusting bit of cheating –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Jordan!’ growled Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I mean, after that open and revolting foul –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Jordan, I’m warning you</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, all right. Flint nearly kills the Gryffindor Seeker, which could happen to anyone, I’m sure, so a penalty to Gryffindor, taken by Spinnet, who puts it away, no trouble, and we continue play, Gryffindor still in possession.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was as Harry dodged another Bludger which went spinning dangerously past his head that it happened. His broom gave a sudden, frightening lurch. For a split second, he thought he was going to fall. He gripped the broom tightly with both his hands and knees. He’d never felt anything like that. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It happened again. It was as though the broom was trying to buck him off. But Nimbus Two Thousands did not suddenly decide to buck their riders off. Harry tried to turn back towards the Gryffindor goalposts; he had half a mind to ask Wood to call time out – and then he realised that his broom was completely out of his control. He couldn’t turn it. He couldn’t direct it at all. It was zig-zagging through the air and every now and then making violent swishing movements which almost unseated him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lee was still commentating. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Slytherin in possession – Flint with the Quaffle – passes Spinnet </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– passes Bell – hit hard in the face by a Bludger, hope it broke his nose – only joking, Professor – Slytherin score – oh no …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Slytherins were cheering. No one seemed to have noticed that Harry’s broom was behaving strangely. It was carrying him slowly higher, away from the game, jerking and twitching as it went. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno what Harry thinks he’s doing,’ Hagrid mumbled. He stared through his binoculars. ‘If I didn’ know better, I’d say he’d lost control of his broom … but he can’t have …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Suddenly, people were pointing up at Harry all over the stands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His broom had started to roll over and over, with him only just managing to hold on. Then the whole crowd gasped. Harry’s broom had given a wild jerk and Harry swung off it. He was now dangling from it, holding on with only one hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did something happen to it when Flint blocked him?’ Seamus whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>140 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t have,’ Hagrid said, his voice shaking. ‘Can’t nothing interfere with a broomstick except powerful Dark Magic – no kid could do that to a Nimbus Two Thousand.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At these words, Hermione seized Hagrid’s binoculars, but instead of looking up at Harry, she started looking frantically at the crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing?’ moaned Ron, grey-faced. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I knew it,’ Hermione gasped. ‘Snape – look.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron grabbed the binoculars. Snape was in the middle of the stands opposite them. He had his eyes fixed on Harry and was muttering non-stop under his breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s doing something – jinxing the broom,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What should we do?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Leave it to me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before Ron could say another word, Hermione had disappeared. Ron turned the binoculars back on Harry. His broom was vibrating so hard, it was almost impossible for him to hang on much longer. The whole crowd were on their feet, watching, terrified, as the Weasleys flew up to try and pull Harry safely on to one of their brooms, but it was no good – every time they got near him, the broom would jump higher still. They dropped lower and circled beneath him, obviously hoping to catch him if he fell. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Marcus Flint seized the Quaffle and scored five times without anyone noticing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, Hermione,’ Ron muttered desperately. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione had fought her way across to the stand where Snape stood and was now racing along the row behind him; she didn’t even stop to say sorry as she knocked Professor Quirrell headfirst into the row in front. Reaching Snape, she crouched down, pulled out her wand and whispered a few, well chosen words. Bright blue flames shot from her wand on to the hem of Snape’s robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took perhaps thirty seconds for Snape to realise that he was on fire. A sudden yelp told her she had done her job. Scooping the fire off him into a little jar in her pocket she scrambled back along the row – Snape would never know what had happened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was enough. Up in the air, Harry was suddenly able to clamber back on to his broom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Neville, you can look!’ Ron said. Neville had been sobbing into Hagrid’s jacket for the last five minutes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was speeding towards the ground when the crowd saw </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quidditch 141 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">him clap his hand to his mouth as though he was about to be sick </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– he hit the pitch on all fours – coughed – and something gold fell into his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve got the Snitch!’ he shouted, waving it above his head, and the game ended in complete confusion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He didn’t  <i class=\"calibre3\">catch</i> it, he nearly  <i class=\"calibre3\">swallowed</i> it,’ Flint was still howling twenty minutes later, but it made no difference – Harry hadn’t broken any rules and Lee Jordan was still happily shouting the result – Gryffindor had won by one hundred and seventy points to sixty. Harry heard none of this, though. He was being made a cup of strong tea back in Hagrid’s hut, with Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was Snape,’ Ron was explaining. ‘Hermione and I saw him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was cursing your broomstick, muttering, he wouldn’t take his eyes off you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rubbish,’ said Hagrid, who hadn’t heard a word of what had gone on next to him in the stands. ‘Why would Snape do somethin’ like that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione looked at each other, wondering what to tell him. Harry decided on the truth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I found out something about him,’ he told Hagrid. ‘He tried to get past that three-headed dog at Hallowe’en. It bit him. We think he was trying to steal whatever it’s guarding.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid dropped the teapot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How do you know about Fluffy?’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Fluffy? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah – he’s mine – bought him off a Greek chappie I met in the pub las’ year – I lent him to Dumbledore to guard the –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes?’ said Harry eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, don’t ask me any more,’ said Hagrid gruffly. ‘That’s top secret, that is.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Snape’s trying to  <i class=\"calibre3\">steal</i> it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rubbish,’ said Hagrid again. ‘Snape’s a Hogwarts teacher, he’d do nothin’ of the sort.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So why did he just try and kill Harry?’ cried Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The afternoon’s events certainly seemed to have changed her mind about Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know a jinx when I see one, Hagrid, I’ve read all about them! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You’ve got to keep eye contact, and Snape wasn’t blinking at all, I saw him!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m tellin’ yeh, yer wrong!’ said Hagrid hotly. ‘I don’ know why </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>142 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s broom acted like that, but Snape wouldn’ try an’ kill a student! Now, listen to me, all three of yeh – yer meddlin’ in things that don’ concern yeh. It’s dangerous. You forget that dog, an’ you forget what it’s guardin’, that’s between Professor Dumbledore an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nicolas Flamel –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aha!’ said Harry. ‘So there’s someone called Nicolas Flamel involved, is there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid looked furious with himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER TWELVE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Mirror of Erised </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Christmas was coming. One morning in mid-December, Hogwarts woke to find itself covered in several feet of snow. The lake froze solid and the Weasley twins were punished for bewitching several snowballs so that they followed Quirrell around, bouncing off the back of his turban. The few owls that managed to battle their way through the stormy sky to deliver post had to be nursed back to health by Hagrid before they could fly off again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No one could wait for the holidays to start. While the Gryffindor common room and the Great Hall had roaring fires, the draughty corridors had become icy and a bitter wind rattled the windows in the classrooms. Worst of all were Professor Snape’s classes down in the dungeons, where their breath rose in a mist before them and they kept as close as possible to their hot cauldrons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I do feel so sorry,’ said Draco Malfoy, one Potions class, ‘for all those people who have to stay at Hogwarts for Christmas because they’re not wanted at home.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was looking over at Harry as he spoke. Crabbe and Goyle chuckled. Harry, who was measuring out powdered spine of lion-fish, ignored them. Malfoy had been even more unpleasant than usual since the Quidditch match. Disgusted that Slytherin had lost, he had tried to get everyone laughing at how a wide-mouthed tree frog would be replacing Harry as Seeker next. Then he’d realised that nobody found this funny, because they were all so impressed at the way Harry had managed to stay on his buck-ing broomstick. So Malfoy, jealous and angry, had gone back to taunting Harry about having no proper family. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was true that Harry wasn’t going back to Privet Drive for Christmas. Professor McGonagall had come round the week before, making a list of students who would be staying for the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>144 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">holidays, and Harry had signed up at once. He didn’t feel sorry for himself at all; this would probably be the best Christmas he’d ever had. Ron and his brothers were staying too, because Mr and Mrs Weasley were going to Romania to visit Charlie. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When they left the dungeons at the end of Potions, they found a large fir tree blocking the corridor ahead. Two enormous feet sticking out at the bottom and a loud puffing sound told them that Hagrid was behind it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hi, Hagrid, want any help?’ Ron asked, sticking his head through the branches. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nah, I’m all right, thanks, Ron.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Would you mind moving out of the way?’ came Malfoy’s cold drawl from behind them. ‘Are you trying to earn some extra money, Weasley? Hoping to be gamekeeper yourself when you leave Hogwarts, I suppose – that hut of Hagrid’s must seem like a palace compared to what your family’s used to.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron dived at Malfoy just as Snape came up the stairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘WEASLEY!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron let go of the front of Malfoy’s robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He was provoked, Professor Snape,’ said Hagrid, sticking his huge hairy face out from behind the tree. ‘Malfoy was insultin’ his family.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Be that as it may, fighting is against Hogwarts rules, Hagrid,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Snape silkily. ‘Five points from Gryffindor, Weasley, and be grateful it isn’t more. Move along, all of you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle pushed roughly past the tree, scattering needles everywhere and smirking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll get him,’ said Ron, grinding his teeth at Malfoy’s back, ‘one of these days, I’ll get him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I hate them both,’ said Harry, ‘Malfoy and Snape.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, cheer up, it’s nearly Christmas,’ said Hagrid. ‘Tell yeh what, come with me an’ see the Great Hall, looks a treat.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So Harry, Ron and Hermione followed Hagrid and his tree off to the Great Hall, where Professor McGonagall and Professor Flitwick were busy with the Christmas decorations. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, Hagrid, the last tree – put it in the far corner, would you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hall looked spectacular. Festoons of holly and mistletoe hung all around the walls and no fewer than twelve towering Christmas trees stood around the room, some sparkling with tiny icicles, some glittering with hundreds of candles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Mirror of Erised 145 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How many days you got left until yer holidays?’ Hagrid asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just one,’ said Hermione. ‘And that reminds me – Harry, Ron, we’ve got half an hour before lunch, we should be in the library.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh yeah, you’re right,’ said Ron, tearing his eyes away from Professor Flitwick, who had golden bubbles blossoming out of his wand and was trailing them over the branches of the new tree. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The library?’ said Hagrid, following them out of the Hall. ‘Just before the holidays? Bit keen, aren’t yeh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, we’re not working,’ Harry told him brightly. ‘Ever since you mentioned Nicolas Flamel we’ve been trying to find out who he is.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You  <i class=\"calibre3\">what? </i>’ Hagrid looked shocked. ‘Listen here – I’ve told yeh </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– drop it. It’s nothin’ to you what that dog’s guardin’.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We just want to know who Nicolas Flamel is, that’s all,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Unless you’d like to tell us and save us the trouble?’ Harry added. ‘We must’ve been through hundreds of books already and we can’t find him anywhere – just give us a hint – I know I’ve read his name somewhere.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sayin’ nothin’,’ said Hagrid flatly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just have to find out for ourselves,  then,’  said  Ron,  and  they left Hagrid looking disgruntled and hurried off to the library. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had indeed been searching books for Flamel’s name ever since Hagrid had let it slip, because how else were they going to find out what Snape was trying to steal? The trouble was, it was very hard to know where to begin, not knowing what Flamel might have done to get himself into a book. He wasn’t in  <i class=\"calibre3\">Great</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Wizards of the Twentieth Century</i>, or  <i class=\"calibre3\">Notable Magical Names of Our</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Time</i>; he was missing, too, from  <i class=\"calibre3\">Important Modern Magical</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Discoveries, </i> and  <i class=\"calibre3\">A Study of Recent Developments in Wizardry. </i> And then, of course, there was the sheer size of the library; tens of thousands of books; thousands of shelves; hundreds of narrow rows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione took out a list of subjects and titles she had decided to search while Ron strode off down a row of books and started pulling them off the shelves at random. Harry wandered over to the Restricted Section. He had been wondering for a while if Flamel wasn’t somewhere in there. Unfortunately, you needed a specially signed note from one of the teachers to look in any of the restricted books and he knew he’d never get one. These were </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>146 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the books containing powerful Dark Magic never taught at Hogwarts and only read by older students studying advanced Defence Against the Dark Arts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you looking for, boy?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pince the librarian brandished a feather duster at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d better get out, then. Go on – out!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wishing he’d been a bit quicker at thinking up some story, Harry left the library. He, Ron and Hermione had already agreed they’d better not ask Madam Pince where they could find Flamel. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were sure she’d be able to tell them, but they couldn’t risk Snape hearing what they were up to. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry waited outside in the corridor to see if the other two had found anything, but he wasn’t very hopeful. They had been looking for a fortnight, after all, but as they only had odd moments between lessons it wasn’t surprising they’d found nothing. What they really needed was a nice long search without Madam Pince breathing down their necks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Five minutes later, Ron and Hermione joined him, shaking their heads. They went off to lunch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You will keep looking while I’m away, won’t you?’ said Hermione. ‘And send me an owl if you find anything.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you could ask your parents if they know who Flamel is,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Ron. ‘It’d be safe to ask them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very safe, as they’re both dentists,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Once the holidays had started, Ron and Harry were having too good a time to think much about Flamel. They had the dormitory to themselves and the common room was far emptier than usual, so they were able to get the good armchairs by the fire. They sat by the hour eating anything they could spear on a toasting fork – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">bread, crumpets, marshmallows – and plotting ways of getting Malfoy expelled, which were fun to talk about even if they wouldn’t work. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron also started teaching Harry wizard chess. This was exactly like Muggle chess except that the figures were alive, which made it a lot like directing troops in battle. Ron’s set was very old and battered. Like everything else he owned, it had once belonged to someone else in his family – in this case, his grandfather. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">However, old chessmen weren’t a drawback at all. Ron knew them </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Mirror of Erised 147 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">so well he never had trouble getting them to do what he wanted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry played with chessmen Seamus Finnigan had lent him and they didn’t trust him at all. He wasn’t a very good player yet and they kept shouting different bits of advice at him, which was confusing: ‘Don’t send me there, can’t you see his knight? Send <i class=\"calibre3\">him, </i> we can afford to lose  <i class=\"calibre3\">him. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On  Christmas  Eve,  Harry  went  to  bed  looking  forward  to  the next day for the food and the fun, but not expecting any presents at all. When he woke early next morning, however, the first thing he saw was a small pile of packages at the foot of his bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Happy Christmas,’ said Ron sleepily as Harry scrambled out of bed and pulled on his dressing-gown. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You too,’ said Harry. ‘Will you look at this? I’ve got some presents!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What did you expect, turnips?’ said Ron, turning to his own pile, which was a lot bigger than Harry’s. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry picked up the top parcel. It was wrapped in thick brown paper and scrawled across it was  <i class=\"calibre3\">To Harry, from Hagrid. </i> Inside was a roughly cut wooden flute. Hagrid had obviously whittled it himself. Harry blew it – it sounded a bit like an owl. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A second, very small parcel contained a note. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">We received your message and enclose your Christmas present. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">From Uncle Vernon and Aunt Petunia. </i> Sellotaped to the note was a fifty-pence piece. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s friendly,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was fascinated by the fifty pence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Weird! </i>’ he said. ‘What a shape! This is  <i class=\"calibre3\">money? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can keep it,’ said Harry, laughing at how pleased Ron was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid and my aunt and uncle – so who sent these?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think I know who that one’s from,’ said Ron, going a bit pink and pointing to a very lumpy parcel. ‘My mum. I told her you didn’t expect any presents and – oh, no,’ he groaned, ‘she’s made you a Weasley jumper.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had torn open the parcel to find a thick, hand-knitted sweater in emerald green and a large box of home-made fudge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Every year she makes us a jumper,’ said Ron, unwrapping his own, ‘and mine’s  <i class=\"calibre3\">always</i> maroon.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s really nice of her,’ said Harry, trying the fudge, which was very tasty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His next present also contained sweets – a large box of </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>148 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Chocolate Frogs from Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This left only one parcel. Harry picked it up and felt it. It was very light. He unwrapped it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something fluid and silvery grey went slithering to the floor, where it lay in gleaming folds. Ron gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve heard of those,’ he said in a hushed voice, dropping the box of Every-Flavour Beans he’d got from Hermione. ‘If that’s what I think it is – they’re really rare, and  <i class=\"calibre3\">really</i> valuable.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry picked the shining, silvery cloth off the floor. It was strange to the touch, like water woven into material. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s an Invisibility Cloak,’ said Ron, a look of awe on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sure it is – try it on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry threw the Cloak around his shoulders and Ron gave a yell. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It  <i class=\"calibre3\">is! </i> Look down!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked down at his feet, but they had gone. He dashed to the mirror. Sure enough, his reflection looked back at him, just his head suspended in mid-air, his body completely invisible. He pulled the Cloak over his head and his reflection vanished completely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s a note!’ said Ron suddenly. ‘A note fell out of it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pulled off the Cloak and seized the letter. Written in narrow, loopy writing he had never seen before were the following words: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Your father left this in my possession before he died. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">It is time it was returned to you. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Use it well. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">A Very Merry Christmas to you. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was no signature. Harry stared at the note. Ron was admiring the Cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’d give  <i class=\"calibre3\">anything</i> for one of these,’ he said. ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Anything. </i> What’s the matter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing,’ said Harry. He felt very strange. Who had sent the Cloak? Had it really once belonged to his father? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before he could say or think anything else, the dormitory door was flung open and Fred and George Weasley bounded in. Harry stuffed the Cloak quickly out of sight. He didn’t feel like sharing it </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Mirror of Erised 149 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">with anyone else yet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Merry Christmas!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hey, look – Harry’s got a Weasley jumper, too!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred and George were wearing blue jumpers, one with a large yellow F on it, the other with a large yellow G. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry’s is better than ours, though,’ said Fred, holding up Harry’s jumper. ‘She obviously makes more of an effort if you’re not family.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why aren’t you wearing yours, Ron?’ George demanded. ‘Come on, get it on, they’re lovely and warm.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I hate maroon,’ Ron moaned half-heartedly as he pulled it over his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You haven’t got a letter on yours,’ George observed. ‘I suppose she thinks you don’t forget your name. But we’re not stupid – we know we’re called Gred and Forge.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s all this noise?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy Weasley stuck his head through the door, looking disapproving. He had clearly come halfway through unwrapping his presents as he, too, carried a lumpy jumper over his arm, which Fred seized. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘P for prefect! Get it on, Percy, come on, we’re all wearing ours, even Harry got one.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – don’t – want –’ said Percy thickly, as the twins forced the jumper over his head, knocking his glasses askew. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you’re not sitting with the Prefects today, either,’ said George. ‘Christmas is a time for family.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They frog-marched Percy from the room, his arms pinned to his sides by his jumper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had never in all his life had such a Christmas dinner. A hundred fat, roast turkeys, mountains of roast and boiled potatoes, platters of fat chipolatas, tureens of buttered peas, silver boats of thick, rich gravy and cranberry sauce – and stacks of wizard crackers every few feet along the table. These fantastic crackers were nothing like the feeble Muggle ones the Dursleys usually bought, with their little plastic toys and their flimsy paper hats. Harry pulled a wizard cracker with Fred and it didn’t just bang, it went off with a blast like a cannon and engulfed them all in a cloud of blue smoke, while from the inside exploded a rear-admiral’s hat and several live, white mice. Up on the High </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>150 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Table, Dumbledore had swapped his pointed wizard’s hat for a flowered bonnet and was chuckling merrily at a joke Professor Flitwick had just read him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flaming Christmas puddings followed the turkey. Percy nearly broke his teeth on a silver Sickle embedded in his slice. Harry watched Hagrid getting redder and redder in the face as he called for more wine, finally kissing Professor McGonagall on the cheek, who, to Harry’s amazement, giggled and blushed, her top hat lop-sided. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Harry finally left the table, he was laden down with a stack of things out of the crackers, including a pack of non-explodable, luminous balloons, a grow-your-own-warts kit and his own new wizard chess set. The white mice had disappeared and Harry had a nasty feeling they were going to end up as Mrs Norris’ Christmas dinner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and the Weasleys spent a happy afternoon having a furious snowball fight in the grounds. Then, cold, wet and gasping for breath, they returned to the fire in the Gryffindor common room, where Harry broke in his new chess set by losing spectacularly to Ron. He suspected he wouldn’t have lost so badly if Percy hadn’t tried to help him so much. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After a tea of turkey sandwiches, crumpets, trifle, and Christmas cake, everyone felt too full and sleepy to do much before bed except sit and watch Percy chase Fred and George all over Gryffindor Tower because they’d stolen his prefect badge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It had been Harry’s best Christmas day ever. Yet something had been nagging at the back of his mind all day. Not until he climbed into bed was he free to think about it: the Invisibility Cloak and whoever had sent it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron, full of turkey and cake and with nothing mysterious to bother him, fell asleep almost as soon as he’d drawn the curtains of his four-poster. Harry leant over the side of his own bed and pulled the Cloak out from under it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His father’s … this had been his father’s. He let the material flow over his hands, smoother than silk, light as air.  <i class=\"calibre3\">Use it well, </i> the note had said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had to try it, now. He slipped out of bed and wrapped the Cloak around himself. Looking down at his legs, he saw only moonlight and shadows. It was a very funny feeling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Use it well. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Mirror of Erised 151 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Suddenly, Harry felt wide awake. The whole of Hogwarts was open to him in this Cloak. Excitement flooded through him as he stood there in the dark and silence. He could go anywhere in this, anywhere, and Filch would never know. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron grunted in his sleep. Should Harry wake him? Something held him back – his father’s Cloak – he felt that this time – the first time – he wanted to use it alone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He crept out of the dormitory, down the stairs, across the common room and climbed through the portrait hole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s there?’ squawked the Fat Lady. Harry said nothing. He walked quickly down the corridor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Where should he go? He stopped, his heart racing, and thought. And then it came to him. The Restricted Section in the library. He’d be able to read as long as he liked, as long as it took to find out who Flamel was. He set off, drawing the Invisibility Cloak tight around him as he walked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The library was pitch black and very eerie. Harry lit a lamp to see his way along the rows of books. The lamp looked as if it was floating along in mid-air, and even though Harry could feel his arm supporting it, the sight gave him the creeps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Restricted Section was right at the back of the library. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stepping carefully over the rope which separated these books from the rest of the library, he held up his lamp to read the titles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They didn’t tell him much. Their peeling, faded gold letters spelled words in languages Harry couldn’t understand. Some had no title at all. One book had a dark stain on it that looked horribly like blood. The hairs on the back of Harry’s neck prickled. Maybe he was imagining it, maybe not, but he thought a faint whispering was coming from the books, as though they knew someone was there who shouldn’t be. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had to start somewhere. Setting the lamp down carefully on the floor, he looked along the bottom shelf for an interesting-looking book. A large black and silver volume caught his eye. He pulled it out with difficulty, because it was very heavy, and, bal-ancing it on his knee, let it fall open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A piercing, blood-curdling shriek split the silence – the book was screaming! Harry snapped it shut, but the shriek went on and on, one high, unbroken, ear-splitting note. He stumbled backwards and knocked over his lamp, which went out at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Panicking, he heard footsteps coming down the corridor outside – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>152 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">stuffing the shrieking book back on the shelf, he ran for it. He passed Filch almost in the doorway; Filch’s pale, wild eyes looked straight through him and Harry slipped under Filch’s outstretched arm and streaked off up the corridor, the book’s shrieks still ringing in his ears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He came to a sudden halt in front of a tall suit of armour. He had been so busy getting away from the library, he hadn’t paid attention to where he was going. Perhaps because it was dark, he didn’t recognise where he was at all. There was a suit of armour near the kitchens, he knew, but he must be five floors above there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You asked me to come directly to you, Professor, if anyone was wandering around at night, and somebody’s been in the library – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Restricted Section.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt the blood drain out of his face. Wherever he was, Filch must know a short cut, because his soft, greasy voice was getting nearer, and to his horror, it was Snape who replied. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Restricted Section? Well, they can’t be far, we’ll catch them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood rooted to the spot as Filch and Snape came around the corner ahead. They couldn’t see him, of course, but it was a narrow corridor and if they came much nearer they’d knock right into him – the Cloak didn’t stop him being solid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He backed away as quietly as he could. A door stood ajar to his left. It was his only hope. He squeezed through it, holding his breath, trying not to move it, and to his relief he managed to get inside the room without their noticing anything. They walked straight past and Harry leant against the wall, breathing deeply, listening to their footsteps dying away. That had been close, very close. It was a few seconds before he noticed anything about the room he had hidden in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It looked like a disused classroom. The dark shapes of desks and chairs were piled against the walls and there was an upturned waste-paper basket – but propped against the wall facing him was something that didn’t look as if it belonged there, something that looked as if someone had just put it there to keep it out of the way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a magnificent mirror, as high as the ceiling, with an ornate gold frame, standing on two clawed feet. There was an inscription carved around the top:  <i class=\"calibre3\">Erised stra ehru oyt ube cafru</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">oyt on wohsi. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Mirror of Erised 153 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His panic fading now that there was no sound of Filch and Snape, Harry moved nearer to the mirror, wanting to look at himself but see no reflection again. He stepped in front of it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had to clap his hands to his mouth to stop himself screaming. He whirled around. His heart was pounding far more furiously than when the book had screamed – for he had seen not only himself in the mirror, but a whole crowd of people standing right behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the room was empty. Breathing very fast, he turned slowly back to the mirror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There he was, reflected in it, white and scared-looking, and there, reflected behind him, were at least ten others. Harry looked over his shoulder – but, still, no one was there. Or were they all invisible, too? Was he in fact in a room full of invisible people and this mirror’s trick was that it reflected them, invisible or not? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked in the mirror again. A woman standing right behind his reflection was smiling at him and waving. He reached out a hand and felt the air behind him. If she was really there, he’d touch her, their reflections were so close together, but he felt only air – she and the others existed only in the mirror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She was a very pretty woman. She had dark red hair and her eyes – her eyes are just like mine, Harry thought, edging a little closer to the glass. Bright green – exactly the same shape, but then he noticed that she was crying; smiling, but crying at the same time. The tall, thin, black-haired man standing next to her put his arm around her. He wore glasses, and his hair was very untidy. It stuck up at the back, just like Harry’s did. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was so close to the mirror now that his nose was nearly touching that of his reflection. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mum?’ he whispered. ‘Dad?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They just looked at him, smiling. And slowly, Harry looked into the faces of the other people in the mirror and saw other pairs of green eyes like his, other noses like his, even a little old man who looked as though he had Harry’s knobbly knees – Harry was looking at his family, for the first time in his life. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Potters smiled and waved at Harry and he stared hungrily back at them, his hands pressed flat against the glass as though he was hoping to fall right through it and reach them. He had a powerful kind of ache inside him, half joy, half terrible sadness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">How long he stood there, he didn’t know. The reflections did </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>154 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">not fade and he looked and looked until a distant noise brought him back to his senses. He couldn’t stay here, he had to find his way back to bed. He tore his eyes away from his mother’s face, whispered, ‘I’ll come back,’ and hurried from the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You could have woken me up,’ said Ron, crossly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can come tonight, I’m going back, I want to show you the mirror.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’d like to see your mum and dad,’ Ron said eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And I want to see all your family, all the Weasleys, you’ll be able to show me your other brothers and everyone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can see them any old time,’ said Ron. ‘Just come round my house this summer. Anyway, maybe it only shows dead people. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Shame about not finding Flamel, though. Have some bacon or something, why aren’t you eating anything?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t eat. He had seen his parents and would be seeing them again tonight. He had almost forgotten about Flamel. It didn’t seem very important any more. Who cared what the threeheaded dog was guarding? What did it matter if Snape stole it, really? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you all right?’ said Ron. ‘You look odd.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What Harry feared most was that he might not be able to find the mirror room again. With Ron covered in the Cloak too, they had to walk much more slowly next night. They tried retracing Harry’s route from the library, wandering around the dark passageways for nearly an hour. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m freezing,’ said Ron. ‘Let’s forget it and go back.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">No! </i>’ Harry hissed. ‘I know it’s here somewhere.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They passed the ghost of a tall witch gliding in the opposite direction, but saw no one else. Just as Ron started moaning that his feet were dead with cold, Harry spotted the suit of armour. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s here – just here – yes!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They pushed the door open. Harry dropped the Cloak from round his shoulders and ran to the mirror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There they were. His mother and father beamed at the sight of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See?’ Harry whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t see anything.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look! Look at them all … there are loads of them …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Mirror of Erised 155 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can only see you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look in it properly, go on, stand where I am.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stepped aside, but with Ron in front of the mirror, he couldn’t see his family any more, just Ron in his paisley pyjamas. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron, though, was staring transfixed at his image. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at me!’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you see all your family standing around you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No – I’m alone – but I’m different – I look older – and I’m Head Boy!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">What? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I am – I’m wearing the badge like Bill used to – and I’m holding the House Cup and the Quidditch Cup – I’m Quidditch captain, too!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron tore his eyes away from this splendid sight to look excitedly at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you think this mirror shows the future?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How can it? All my family are dead – let me have another look –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You had it to yourself all last night, give me a bit more time.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re only holding the Quidditch Cup, what’s interesting about that? I want to see my parents.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t push me –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A sudden noise outside in the corridor put an end to their discussion. They hadn’t realised how loudly they had been talking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quick!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron threw the Cloak back over them as the luminous eyes of Mrs Norris came round the door. Ron and Harry stood quite still, both thinking the same thing – did the Cloak work on cats? After what seemed an age, she turned and left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This isn’t safe – she might have gone for Filch, I bet she heard us. Come on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Ron pulled Harry out of the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The snow still hadn’t melted next morning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Want to play chess, Harry?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why don’t we go down and visit Hagrid?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No … you go …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know what you’re thinking about, Harry, that mirror. Don’t go back tonight.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>156 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why not?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I dunno, I’ve just got a bad feeling about it – and anyway, you’ve had too many close shaves already. Filch, Snape and Mrs Norris are wandering around. So what if they can’t see you? What if they walk into you? What if you knock something over?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You sound like Hermione.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m serious, Harry, don’t go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry only had one thought in his head, which was to get back in front of the mirror, and Ron wasn’t going to stop him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">That third night he found his way more quickly than before. He was walking so fast he knew he was making more noise than was wise, but he didn’t meet anyone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And there were his mother and father smiling at him again, and one of his grandfathers nodding happily. Harry sank down to sit on the floor in front of the mirror. There was nothing to stop him staying here all night with his family. Nothing at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Except – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So – back again, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt as though his insides had turned to ice. He looked behind him. Sitting on one of the desks by the wall was none other than Albus Dumbledore. Harry must have walked straight past him, so desperate to get to the mirror he hadn’t noticed him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – I didn’t see you, sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Strange how short-sighted being invisible can make you,’ said Dumbledore, and Harry was relieved to see that he was smiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So,’ said Dumbledore, slipping off the desk to sit on the floor with Harry, ‘you, like hundreds before you, have discovered the delights of the Mirror of Erised.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I didn’t know it was called that, sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I expect you’ve realised by now what it does?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It – well – it shows me my family –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And it showed your friend Ron himself as Head Boy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did you know –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t need a cloak to become invisible,’ said Dumbledore gently. ‘Now, can you think what the Mirror of Erised shows us all?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shook his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let me explain. The happiest man on earth would be able to use the Mirror of Erised like a normal mirror, that is, he would look into it and see himself exactly as he is. Does that help?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Mirror of Erised 157 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry thought. Then he said slowly, ‘It shows us what we want </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… whatever we want …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes  and  no,’  said  Dumbledore  quietly.  ‘It  shows  us  nothing more or less than the deepest, most desperate desire of our hearts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You, who have never known your family, see them standing around you. Ronald Weasley, who has always been overshadowed by his brothers, sees himself standing alone, the best of all of them. However, this mirror will give us neither knowledge or truth. Men have wasted away before it, entranced by what they have seen, or been driven mad, not knowing if what it shows is real or even possible. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Mirror will be moved to a new home tomorrow, Harry, and I ask you not to go looking for it again. If you ever  <i class=\"calibre3\">do</i> run across it, you will now be prepared. It does not do to dwell on dreams and forget to live, remember that. Now, why don’t you put that admirable Cloak back on and get off to bed?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sir – Professor Dumbledore? Can I ask you something?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Obviously, you’ve just done so,’ Dumbledore smiled. ‘You may ask me one more thing, however.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What do you see when you look in the Mirror?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I? I see myself holding a pair of thick, woollen socks.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘One can never have enough socks,’ said Dumbledore. ‘Another Christmas has come and gone and I didn’t get a single pair. People will insist on giving me books.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was only when he was back in bed that it struck Harry that Dumbledore might not have been quite truthful. But then, he thought, as he shoved Scabbers off his pillow, it had been quite a personal question. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER THIRTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Nicolas Flamel </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore had convinced Harry not to go looking for the Mirror of Erised again and for the rest of the Christmas holidays the Invisibility Cloak stayed folded at the bottom of his trunk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wished he could forget what he’d seen in the Mirror as easily, but he couldn’t. He started having nightmares. Over and over again he dreamed about his parents disappearing in a flash of green light while a high voice cackled with laughter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You see, Dumbledore was right, that mirror could drive you mad,’ said Ron, when Harry told him about these dreams. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione, who came back the day before term started, took a different view of things. She was torn between horror at the idea of Harry being out of bed, roaming the school three nights in a row (‘If Filch had caught you!’) and disappointment that he hadn’t at least found out who Nicolas Flamel was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had almost given up hope of ever finding Flamel in a library book, even though Harry was still sure he’d read the name somewhere. Once term had started, they were back to skimming through books for ten minutes during their breaks. Harry had even less time than the other two, because Quidditch practice had started again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood was working the team harder than ever. Even the endless rain that had replaced the snow couldn’t dampen his spirits. The Weasleys complained that Wood was becoming a fanatic, but Harry was on Wood’s side. If they won their next match, against Hufflepuff, they would overtake Slytherin in the House Championship for the first time in seven years. Quite apart from wanting to win, Harry found that he had fewer nightmares when he was tired out after training. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, during one particularly wet and muddy practice session, Wood gave the team a bit of bad news. He’d just got very angry </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nicholas Flamel 159 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">with the Weasleys, who kept dive-bombing each other and pretending to fall off their brooms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Will you stop messing around!’ he yelled. ‘That’s exactly the sort of thing that’ll lose us the match! Snape’s refereeing this time, and he’ll be looking for any excuse to knock points off Gryffindor!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">George Weasley really did fall off his broom at these words. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Snape’s</i> refereeing?’ he spluttered through a mouthful of mud. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When’s he ever refereed a Quidditch match? He’s not going to be fair if we might overtake Slytherin.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rest of the team landed next to George to complain, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not  <i class=\"calibre3\">my</i> fault,’ said Wood. ‘We’ve just got to make sure we play a clean game, so Snape hasn’t got an excuse to pick on us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Which was all very well, thought Harry, but he had another reason for not wanting Snape near him while he was playing Quidditch … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rest of the team hung back to talk to each other as usual at the end of practice, but Harry headed straight back to the Gryffindor common room, where he found Ron and Hermione playing chess. Chess was the only thing Hermione ever lost at, something Harry and Ron thought was very good for her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t talk to me for a moment,’ said Ron when Harry sat down next to him. ‘I need to concen–’ He caught sight of Harry’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the matter with you? You look terrible.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Speaking quietly so that no one else would hear, Harry told the other two about Snape’s sudden, sinister desire to be a Quidditch referee. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t play,’ said Hermione at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Say you’re ill,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pretend to break your leg,’ Hermione suggested. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Really</i> break your leg,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t,’ said Harry. ‘There isn’t a reserve Seeker. If I back out, Gryffindor can’t play at all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment Neville toppled into the common room. How he had managed to climb through the portrait hole was anyone’s guess, because his legs had been stuck together with what they recognised at once as the Leg-Locker Curse. He must have had to bunny hop all the way up to Gryffindor Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone fell about laughing except Hermione, who leapt up and performed the counter-curse. Neville’s legs sprang apart and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>160 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he got to his feet, trembling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What happened?’ Hermione asked him, leading him over to sit with Harry and Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy,’ said Neville shakily. ‘I met him outside the library. He said he’d been looking for someone to practise that on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go to Professor McGonagall!’ Hermione urged Neville. ‘Report him!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville shook his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t want more trouble,’ he mumbled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve got to stand up to him, Neville!’ said Ron. ‘He’s used to walking all over people, but that’s no reason to lie down in front of him and make it easier.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s  no  need  to  tell  me  I’m  not  brave  enough  to  be  in Gryffindor, Malfoy’s already done that,’ Neville choked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt in the pocket of his robes and pulled out a Chocolate Frog, the very last one from the box Hermione had given him for Christmas. He gave it to Neville, who looked as though he might cry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re worth twelve of Malfoy,’ Harry said. ‘The Sorting Hat chose you for Gryffindor, didn’t it? And where’s Malfoy? In stink-ing Slytherin.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville’s lips twitched in a weak smile as he unwrapped the Frog. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thanks, Harry … I think I’ll go to bed … D’you want the card, you collect them, don’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Neville walked away Harry looked at the Famous Wizard card. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore again,’ he said. ‘He was the first one I ever –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gasped. He stared at the back of the card. Then he looked up at Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">I’ve found him! </i>’ he whispered. ‘I’ve found Flamel! I  <i class=\"calibre3\">told</i> you I’d read the name somewhere before, I read it on the train coming here – listen to this: “Professor Dumbledore is particularly famous for his defeat of the dark wizard Grindelwald in 1945, for the discovery of the twelve uses of dragon’s blood  <i class=\"calibre3\">and his work on</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">alchemy with his partner, Nicolas Flamel</i>”  <i class=\"calibre3\">! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione jumped to her feet. She hadn’t looked so excited since they’d got back the marks for their very first piece of homework. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stay there!’ she said, and she sprinted up the stairs to the girls’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">dormitories. Harry and Ron barely had time to exchange mystified looks before she was dashing back, an enormous old book in her arms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nicholas Flamel 161 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I never thought to look in here!’ she whispered excitedly. ‘I got this out of the library weeks ago for a bit of light reading.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Light? </i>’ said Ron, but Hermione told him to be quiet until she’d looked something up, and started flicking frantically through the pages, muttering to herself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last she found what she was looking for. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I knew it! I  <i class=\"calibre3\">knew</i> it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are we allowed to speak yet?’ said Ron grumpily. Hermione ignored him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nicolas Flamel,’ she whispered dramatically, ‘is the  <i class=\"calibre3\">only known</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">maker of the Philosopher’s Stone! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This didn’t have quite the effect she’d expected. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The what?’ said Harry and Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,  <i class=\"calibre3\">honestly, </i> don’t you two read? Look – read that, there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She pushed the book towards them, and Harry and Ron read: <i class=\"calibre3\">The ancient study of alchemy is concerned with</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">making the Philosopher’s Stone, a legendary</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">substance with astonishing powers. The Stone</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">will transform any metal into pure gold. It also</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">produces the Elixir of Life, which will make</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">the drinker immortal. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">There have been many reports of the Philosopher’s</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Stone over the centuries, but the only Stone currently</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">in existence belongs to Mr Nicolas Flamel, the noted</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">alchemist and opera-lover. Mr Flamel, who</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">celebrated his six hundred and sixty-fifth birthday</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">last year, enjoys a quiet life in Devon with his wife,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Perenelle (six hundred and fifty-eight). </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See?’ said Hermione, when Harry and Ron had finished. ‘The dog must be guarding Flamel’s Philosopher’s Stone! I bet he asked Dumbledore to keep it safe for him, because they’re friends and he knew someone was after it. That’s why he wanted the Stone moved out of Gringotts!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A stone that makes gold and stops you ever dying!’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No wonder Snape’s after it!  <i class=\"calibre3\">Anyone</i> would want it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And no wonder we couldn’t find Flamel in that  <i class=\"calibre3\">Study of Recent</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Developments in Wizardry, </i>’ said Ron. ‘He’s not exactly recent if he’s six hundred and sixty-five, is he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>162 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Next morning in Defence Against the Dark Arts, while copying down different ways of treating werewolf bites, Harry and Ron were still discussing what they’d do with a Philosopher’s Stone if they had one. It wasn’t until Ron said he’d buy his own Quidditch team that Harry remembered about Snape and the coming match. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going to play,’ he told Ron and Hermione. ‘If I don’t, all the Slytherins will think I’m just too scared to face Snape. I’ll show them … it’ll really wipe the smiles off their faces if we win.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just as long as we’re not wiping you off the pitch,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the match drew nearer, however, Harry became more and more nervous, whatever he told Ron and Hermione. The rest of the team weren’t too calm, either. The idea of overtaking Slytherin in the House Championship was wonderful, no one had done it for nearly seven years, but would they be allowed to, with such a biased referee? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t know whether he was imagining it or not, but he seemed to keep running into Snape wherever he went. At times, he even wondered whether Snape was following him, trying to catch him on his own. Potions lessons were turning into a sort of weekly torture, Snape was so horrible to Harry. Could Snape possibly know they’d found out about the Philosopher’s Stone? Harry didn’t see how he could – yet he sometimes had the horrible feeling that Snape could read minds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knew, when they wished him good luck outside the changing rooms next afternoon, that Ron and Hermione were wondering whether they’d ever see him alive again. This wasn’t what you’d call comforting. Harry hardly heard a word of Wood’s pep talk as he pulled on his Quidditch robes and picked up his Nimbus Two Thousand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione, meanwhile, had found a place in the stands next to Neville, who couldn’t understand why they looked so grim and worried, or why they had both brought their wands to the match. Little did Harry know that Ron and Hermione had been secretly practising the Leg-Locker Curse. They’d got the idea from Malfoy using it on Neville, and were ready to use it on Snape if he showed any sign of wanting to hurt Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, don’t forget, it’s  <i class=\"calibre3\">Locomotor Mortis, </i>’ Hermione muttered as </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nicholas Flamel 163 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron slipped his wand up his sleeve. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I  <i class=\"calibre3\">know, </i>’ Ron snapped. ‘Don’t nag.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Back in the changing room, Wood had taken Harry aside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t want to pressure you, Potter, but if we ever need an early capture of the Snitch it’s now. Finish the game before Snape can favour Hufflepuff too much.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The whole school’s out there!’ said Fred Weasley, peering out of the door. ‘Even – blimey – Dumbledore’s come to watch!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s heart did a somersault. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Dumbledore? </i>’ he said, dashing to the door to make sure. Fred was right. There was no mistaking that silver beard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could have laughed out loud with relief. He was safe. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was simply no way that Snape would dare to try and hurt him if Dumbledore was watching. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps that was why Snape was looking so angry as the teams marched on to the pitch, something that Ron noticed, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve never seen Snape look so mean,’ he told Hermione. ‘Look – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they’re off. Ouch!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Someone had poked Ron in the back of the head. It was Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, sorry, Weasley, didn’t see you there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy grinned broadly at Crabbe and Goyle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wonder how long Potter’s going to stay on his broom this time? Anyone want a bet? What about you, Weasley?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron didn’t answer; Snape had just awarded Hufflepuff a penalty because George Weasley had hit a Bludger at him. Hermione, who had all her fingers crossed in her lap, was squinting fixedly at Harry, who was circling the game like a hawk, looking for the Snitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know how I think they choose people for the Gryffindor team?’ said Malfoy loudly a few minutes later, as Snape awarded Hufflepuff another penalty for no reason at all. ‘It’s people they feel sorry for. See, there’s Potter, who’s got no parents, then there’s the Weasleys, who’ve got no money – you should be on the team, Longbottom, you’ve got no brains.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville went bright red but turned in his seat to face Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m worth twelve of you, Malfoy,’ he stammered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle howled with laughter, but Ron, still not daring to take his eyes from the game, said, ‘You tell him, Neville.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Longbottom, if brains were gold you’d be poorer than Weasley, and that’s saying something.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>164 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s nerves were already stretched to breaking point with anxiety about Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m warning you, Malfoy – one more word –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron!’ said Hermione suddenly. ‘Harry –!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What? Where?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had suddenly gone into a spectacular dive, which drew gasps and cheers from the crowd. Hermione stood up, her crossed fingers in her mouth, as Harry streaked towards the ground like a bullet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re in luck, Weasley, Potter’s obviously spotted some money on the ground!’ said Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron snapped. Before Malfoy knew what was happening, Ron was on top of him, wrestling him to the ground. Neville hesitated, then clambered over the back of his seat to help. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, Harry!’ Hermione screamed, leaping on to her seat to watch as Harry sped straight at Snape – she didn’t even notice Malfoy and Ron rolling around under her seat, or the scuffles and yelps coming from the whirl of fists that was Neville, Crabbe and Goyle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Up in the air, Snape turned on his broomstick just in time to see something scarlet shoot past him, missing him by inches – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">next second, Harry had pulled out of the dive, his arm raised in triumph, the Snitch clasped in his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The stands erupted; it had to be a record, no one could ever remember the Snitch being caught so quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron! Ron! Where are you? The game’s over! Harry’s won! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">We’ve won! Gryffindor are in the lead!’ shrieked Hermione, dancing up and down on her seat and hugging Parvati Patil in the row in front. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jumped off his broom, a foot from the ground. He couldn’t believe it. He’d done it – the game was over; it had barely lasted five minutes. As Gryffindors came spilling on to the pitch, he saw Snape land nearby, white-faced and tight-lipped – then Harry felt a hand on his shoulder and looked up into Dumbledore’s smiling face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well done,’ said Dumbledore quietly, so that only Harry could hear. ‘Nice to see you haven’t been brooding about that mirror … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">been keeping busy … excellent …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape spat bitterly on the ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nicholas Flamel 165 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry left the changing room alone some time later, to take his Nimbus Two Thousand back to the broomshed. He couldn’t ever remember feeling happier. He’d really done something to be proud of now – no one could say he was just a famous name any more. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The evening air had never smelled so sweet. He walked over the damp grass, reliving the last hour in his head, which was a happy blur: Gryffindors running to lift him on to their shoulders; Ron and Hermione in the distance, jumping up and down, Ron cheering through a heavy nosebleed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had reached the shed. He leant against the wooden door and looked up at Hogwarts, with its windows glowing red in the setting sun. Gryffindor in the lead. He’d done it, he’d shown Snape … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And speaking of Snape … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A hooded figure came swiftly down the front steps of the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Clearly not wanting to be seen, it walked as fast as possible towards the Forbidden Forest. Harry’s victory faded from his mind as he watched. He recognised the figure’s prowling walk. Snape, sneaking into the Forest while everyone else was at dinner – what was going on? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jumped back on his Nimbus Two Thousand and took off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gliding silently over the castle he saw Snape enter the Forest at a run. He followed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The trees were so thick he couldn’t see where Snape had gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He flew in circles, lower and lower, brushing the top branches of trees until he heard voices. He glided towards them and landed noiselessly in a towering beech tree. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He climbed carefully along one of the branches, holding tight to his broomstick, trying to see through the leaves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Below, in a shadowy clearing, stood Snape, but he wasn’t alone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell was there, too. Harry couldn’t make out the look on his face, but he was stuttering worse than ever. Harry strained to catch what they were saying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… d-don’t know why you wanted t-t-to meet here of all p-places, Severus …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, I thought we’d keep this private,’ said Snape, his voice icy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Students aren’t supposed to know about the Philosopher’s Stone, after all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry leant forward. Quirrell was mumbling something. Snape interrupted him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>166 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you found out how to get past that beast of Hagrid’s yet?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘B-b-but Severus, I –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t want me as your enemy, Quirrell,’ said Snape, taking a step towards him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I-I don-t know what you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know perfectly well what I mean.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">An owl hooted loudly and Harry nearly fell out of the tree. He steadied himself in time to hear Snape say, ‘– your little bit of hocus pocus. I’m waiting.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘B-but I d-d-don’t –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very well,’ Snape cut in. ‘We’ll have another little chat soon, when you’ve had time to think things over and decided where your loyalties lie.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He threw his cloak over his head and strode out of the clearing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was almost dark now, but Harry could see Quirrell, standing quite still as though he was petrified. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, where have you  <i class=\"calibre3\">been? </i>’ Hermione squeaked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We won! You won! We won!’ shouted Ron, thumping Harry on the back. ‘And I gave Malfoy a black eye and Neville tried to take on Crabbe and Goyle single-handed! He’s still out cold but Madam Pomfrey says he’ll be all right – talk about showing Slytherin! Everyone’s waiting for you in the common room, we’re having a party, Fred and George stole some cakes and stuff from the kitchens.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Never mind that now,’ said Harry breathlessly. ‘Let’s find an empty room, you wait ’til you hear this …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He made sure Peeves wasn’t inside before shutting the door behind them, then he told them what he’d seen and heard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So we were right, it  <i class=\"calibre3\">is </i> the Philosopher’s Stone, and Snape’s trying to force Quirrell to help him get it. He asked if he knew how to get past Fluffy – and he said something about Quirrell’s “hocus-pocus” – I reckon there are other things guarding the stone apart from Fluffy, loads of enchantments, probably, and Quirrell would have done some anti-Dark Arts spell which Snape needs to break through –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So you mean the Stone’s only safe as long as Quirrell stands up to Snape?’ said Hermione in alarm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’ll be gone by next Tuesday,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER FOURTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Norbert the Norwegian </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Ridgeback </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell, however, must have been braver than they’d thought. In the weeks that followed he did seem to be getting paler and thinner, but it didn’t look as though he’d cracked yet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Every time they passed the third-floor corridor, Harry, Ron and Hermione would press their ears to the door to check that Fluffy was still growling inside. Snape was sweeping about in his usual bad temper, which surely meant that the Stone was still safe. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Whenever Harry passed Quirrell these days he gave him an encouraging sort of smile, and Ron had started telling people off for laughing at Quirrell’s stutter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione, however, had more on her mind than the Philosopher’s Stone. She had started drawing up revision timetables and colour-coding all her notes. Harry and Ron wouldn’t have minded, but she kept nagging them to do the same. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, the exams are ages away.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ten weeks,’ Hermione snapped. ‘That’s not ages, that’s like a second to Nicolas Flamel.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But we’re not six hundred years old,’ Ron reminded her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyway, what are you revising for, you already know it all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What am I revising for? Are you mad? You realise we need to pass these exams to get into the second year? They’re very important, I should have started studying a month ago, I don’t know what’s got into me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Unfortunately, the teachers seemed to be thinking along the same lines as Hermione. They piled so much homework on them that the Easter holidays weren’t nearly as much fun as the Christmas ones. It was hard to relax with Hermione next to you reciting the twelve uses of dragon’s blood or practising wand </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>168 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">movements. Moaning and yawning, Harry and Ron spent most of their free time in the library with her, trying to get through all their extra work. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll never remember this,’ Ron burst out one afternoon, throwing down his quill and looking longingly out of the library window. It was the first really fine day they’d had in months. The sky was a clear, forget-me-not blue and there was a feeling in the air of summer coming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who was looking up ‘Dittany’ in  <i class=\"calibre3\">One Thousand Magical</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Herbs and Fungi, </i> didn’t look up until he heard Ron say, ‘Hagrid! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What are you doing in the library?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid shuffled into view, hiding something behind his back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked very out of place in his moleskin overcoat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Jus’ lookin’,’ he said, in a shifty voice that got their interest at once. ‘An’ what’re you lot up ter?’ He looked suddenly suspicious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yer not still lookin’ fer Nicolas Flamel, are yeh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, we found out who he is ages ago,’ said Ron impressively. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">And </i> we know what that dog’s guarding, it’s a Philosopher’s St–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Shhhh! </i>’ Hagrid looked around quickly to see if anyone was listening. ‘Don’ go shoutin’ about it, what’s the matter with yeh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There are a few things we wanted to ask you, as a matter of fact,’ said Harry, ‘about what’s guarding the Stone apart from Fluffy –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘SHHHH!’ said Hagrid again. ‘Listen – come an’ see me later, I’m not promisin’ I’ll tell yeh anythin’, mind, but don’ go rabbitin’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">about it in here, students aren’ s’pposed ter know. They’ll think I’ve told yeh –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See you later, then,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid shuffled off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What was he hiding behind his back?’ said Hermione thoughtfully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you think it had anything to do with the Stone?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going to see what section he was in,’ said Ron, who’d had enough of working. He came back a minute later with a pile of books in his arms and slammed them down on the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Dragons! </i>’ he whispered. ‘Hagrid was looking up stuff about dragons! Look at these:  <i class=\"calibre3\">Dragon Species of Great Britain and</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Ireland; From Egg to Inferno, A Dragon Keeper’s Guide. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid’s always wanted a dragon, he told me so the first time I ever met him,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Norbert the Norwegian Ridgeback 169 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But it’s against our laws,’ said Ron. ‘Dragon-breeding was out-lawed by the Warlocks’ Convention of 1709, everyone knows that. It’s hard to stop Muggles noticing us if we’re keeping dragons in the back garden – anyway, you can’t tame dragons, it’s dangerous. You should see the burns Charlie’s got off wild ones in Romania.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But there aren’t wild dragons in  <i class=\"calibre3\">Britain? </i>’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course there are,’ said Ron. ‘Common Welsh Green and Hebridean Blacks. The Ministry of Magic has a job hushing them up, I can tell you. Our lot have to keep putting spells on Muggles who’ve spotted them, to make them forget.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So what on earth’s Hagrid up to?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When they knocked on the door of the gamekeeper’s hut an hour later, they were surprised to see that all the curtains were closed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid called, ‘Who is it?’ before he let them in and then shut the door quickly behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was stiflingly hot inside. Even though it was such a warm day, there was a blazing fire in the grate. Hagrid made them tea and offered them stoat sandwiches, which they refused. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So – yeh wanted to ask me somethin’?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry. There was no point beating about the bush. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We were wondering if you could tell us what’s guarding the Philosopher’s Stone apart from Fluffy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid frowned at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘O’ course I can’t,’ he said. ‘Number one, I don’ know meself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Number two, yeh know too much already, so I wouldn’ tell yeh if I could. That Stone’s here fer a good reason. It was almost stolen outta Gringotts – I s’ppose yeh’ve worked that out an’ all? Beats me how yeh even know abou’ Fluffy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, come on, Hagrid, you might not want to tell us, but you  <i class=\"calibre3\">do</i> know, you know everything that goes on round here,’ said Hermione in a warm, flattering voice. Hagrid’s beard twitched and they could tell he was smiling. ‘We only wondered who had  <i class=\"calibre3\">done</i> the guarding, really.’ Hermione went on. ‘We wondered who Dumbledore had trusted enough to help him, apart from you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s chest swelled at these last words. Harry and Ron beamed at Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I don’ s’pose it could hurt ter tell yeh that … let’s see … he borrowed Fluffy from me … then some o’ the teachers did </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>170 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">enchantments … Professor Sprout – Professor Flitwick – Professor McGonagall –’ he ticked them off on his fingers, ‘Professor Quirrell – an’ Dumbledore himself did somethin’, o’ course. Hang on, I’ve forgotten someone. Oh yeah, Professor Snape.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Snape? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah – yer not still on abou’ that, are yeh? Look, Snape helped <i class=\"calibre3\">protect</i> the Stone, he’s not about ter steal it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knew Ron and Hermione were thinking the same as he was. If Snape had been in on protecting the Stone, it must have been easy to find out how the other teachers had guarded it. He probably knew everything – except, it seemed, Quirrell’s spell and how to get past Fluffy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re the only one who knows how to get past Fluffy, aren’t you, Hagrid?’ said Harry anxiously. ‘And you wouldn’t tell anyone, would you? Not even one of the teachers?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not a soul knows except me an’ Dumbledore,’ said Hagrid proudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, that’s something,’ Harry muttered to the others. ‘Hagrid, can we have a window open? I’m boiling.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t, Harry, sorry,’ said Hagrid. Harry noticed him glance at the fire. Harry looked at it, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid – what’s  <i class=\"calibre3\">that? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he already knew what it was. In the very heart of the fire, underneath the kettle, was a huge, black egg. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah,’ said Hagrid, fiddling nervously with his beard. ‘That’s – er …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where did you get it, Hagrid?’ said Ron, crouching over the fire to get a closer look at the egg. ‘It must’ve cost you a fortune.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Won it,’ said Hagrid. ‘Las’ night. I was down in the village havin’ a few drinks an’ got into a game o’ cards with a stranger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Think he was quite glad ter get rid of it, ter be honest.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But what are you going to do with it when it’s hatched?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I’ve bin doin’ some readin’,’ said Hagrid, pulling a large book from under his pillow. ‘Got this outta the library –  <i class=\"calibre3\">Dragon-Breeding for Pleasure and Profit</i> – it’s a bit outta date, o’ course, but it’s all in here. Keep the egg in the fire, ’cause their mothers breathe on ’em, see, an’ when it hatches, feed it on a bucket o’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">brandy mixed with chicken blood every half hour. An’ see here – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">how ter recognise diff’rent eggs – what I got there’s a Norwegian Ridgeback. They’re rare, them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Norbert the Norwegian Ridgeback 171 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked very pleased with himself, but Hermione didn’t. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid, you live in a  <i class=\"calibre3\">wooden house, </i>’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hagrid wasn’t listening. He was humming merrily as he stoked the fire. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So now they had something else to worry about: what might happen to Hagrid if anyone found out he was hiding an illegal dragon in his hut. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wonder what it’s like to have a peaceful life,’ Ron sighed, as evening after evening they struggled through all the extra homework they were getting. Hermione had now started making revision timetables for Harry and Ron, too. It was driving them mad. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, one breakfast time, Hedwig brought Harry another note from Hagrid. He had written only two words:  <i class=\"calibre3\">It’s hatching. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron wanted to skip Herbology and go straight down to the hut. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione wouldn’t hear of it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, how many times in our lives are we going to see a dragon hatching?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got lessons, we’ll get into trouble, and that’s nothing to what Hagrid’s going to be in when someone finds out what he’s doing –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up!’ Harry whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy was only a few feet away and he had stopped dead to listen. How much had he heard? Harry didn’t like the look on Malfoy’s face at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione argued all the way to Herbology, and in the end, Hermione agreed to run down to Hagrid’s with the other two during morning break. When the bell sounded from the castle at the end of their lesson, the three of them dropped their trowels at once and hurried through the grounds to the edge of the Forest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid greeted them looking flushed and excited. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s nearly out.’ He ushered them inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The egg was lying on the table. There were deep cracks in it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something was moving inside; a funny clicking noise was coming from it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000002999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They all drew their chairs up to the table and watched with bated breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All at once there was a scraping noise and the egg split open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The baby dragon flopped on to the table. It wasn’t exactly pretty; Harry thought it looked like a crumpled, black umbrella. Its spiny </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>172 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">wings were huge compared to its skinny jet body and it had a long snout with wide nostrils, stubs of horns and bulging, orange eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It sneezed. A couple of sparks flew out of its snout. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Isn’t he  <i class=\"calibre3\">beautiful? </i>’ Hagrid murmured. He reached out a hand to stroke the dragon’s head. It snapped at his fingers, showing pointed fangs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bless him, look, he knows his mummy!’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid,’ said Hermione, ‘how fast do Norwegian Ridgebacks grow, exactly?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was about to answer when the colour suddenly drained from his face – he leapt to his feet and ran to the window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the matter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Someone was lookin’ through the gap in the curtains – it’s a kid – he’s runnin’ back up ter the school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry bolted to the door and looked out. Even at a distance there was no mistaking him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy had seen the dragon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something about the smile lurking on Malfoy’s face during the next week made Harry, Ron and Hermione very nervous. They spent most of their free time in Hagrid’s darkened hut, trying to reason with him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just let him go,’ Harry urged. ‘Set him free.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t,’ said Hagrid. ‘He’s too little. He’d die.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They looked at the dragon. It had grown three times in length in just a week. Smoke kept furling out of its nostrils. Hagrid hadn’t been doing his gamekeeping duties because the dragon was keeping him so busy. There were empty brandy bottles and chicken feathers all over the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve decided to call him Norbert,’ said Hagrid, looking at the dragon with misty eyes. ‘He really knows me now, watch. Norbert! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Norbert! Where’s Mummy?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s lost his marbles,’ Ron muttered in Harry’s ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid,’ said Harry loudly, ‘give it a fortnight and Norbert’s going to be as long as your house. Malfoy could go to Dumbledore at any moment.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid bit his lip. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – I know I can’t keep him for ever, but I can’t jus’ dump him, I can’t.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry suddenly turned to Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Norbert the Norwegian Ridgeback 173 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Charlie,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re losing it, too,’ said Ron. ‘I’m Ron, remember?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No – Charlie – your brother Charlie. In Romania. Studying dragons. We could send Norbert to him. Charlie can take care of him and then put him back in the wild!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Brilliant!’ said Ron. ‘How about it, Hagrid?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And in the end, Hagrid agreed that they could send an owl to Charlie to ask him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The following week dragged by. Wednesday night found Hermione and Harry sitting alone in the common room, long after everyone else had gone to bed. The clock on the wall had just chimed midnight when the portrait hole burst open. Ron appeared out of nowhere as he pulled off Harry’s Invisibility Cloak. He had been down at Hagrid’s hut, helping him feed Norbert, who was now eating dead rats by the crate. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It bit me!’ he said, showing them his hand, which was wrapped in a bloody handkerchief. ‘I’m not going to be able to hold a quill for a week. I tell you, that dragon’s the most horrible animal I’ve ever met, but the way Hagrid goes on about it, you’d think it was a fluffy little bunny rabbit. When it bit me he told me off for frightening it. And when I left, he was singing it a lullaby.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a tap on the dark window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s Hedwig!’ said Harry, hurrying to let her in. ‘She’ll have Charlie’s answer!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The three of them put their heads together to read the note. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Dear Ron, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">How are you? Thanks for the letter – I’d be glad to take</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">the Norwegian Ridgeback, but it won’t be easy getting</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">him here. I think the best thing will be to send him over</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">with some friends of mine who are coming to visit me</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">next week. Trouble is, they mustn’t be seen carrying</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">an illegal dragon. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Could you get the Ridgeback up the tallest tower at</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">midnight on Saturday? They can meet you there and</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">take him away while it’s still dark. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Send me an answer as soon as possible. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Love, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Charlie</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>174 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They looked at each other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got the Invisibility Cloak,’ said Harry. ‘It shouldn’t be too difficult – I think the Cloak’s big enough to cover two of us and Norbert.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a mark of how bad the last week had been that the other two agreed with him. Anything to get rid of Norbert – and Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a hitch. By next morning, Ron’s bitten hand had swollen to twice its usual size. He didn’t know whether it was safe to go to Madam Pomfrey – would she recognise a dragon bite? By the afternoon, though, he had no choice. The cut had turned a nasty shade of green. It looked as if Norbert’s fangs were poisonous. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione rushed up to the hospital wing at the end of the day to find Ron in a terrible state in bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not just my hand,’ he whispered, ‘although that feels like it’s about to fall off. Malfoy told Madam Pomfrey he wanted to borrow one of my books so he could come and have a good laugh at me. He kept threatening to tell her what really bit me – I’ve told her it was a dog but I don’t think she believes me – I shouldn’t have hit him at the Quidditch match, that’s why he’s doing this.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione tried to calm Ron down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’ll all be over at midnight on Saturday,’ said Hermione, but this didn’t soothe Ron at all. On the contrary, he sat bolt upright and broke into a sweat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Midnight on Saturday!’ he said in a hoarse voice. ‘Oh no – oh no – I’ve just remembered – Charlie’s letter was in that book Malfoy took, he’s going to know we’re getting rid of Norbert.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione didn’t get a chance to answer. Madam Pomfrey came over at that moment and made them leave, saying Ron needed sleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s too late to change the plan now,’ Harry told Hermione. ‘We haven’t got time to send Charlie another owl and this could be our only chance to get rid of Norbert. We’ll have to risk it. And we   <i class=\"calibre3\">have</i> got the Invisibility Cloak, Malfoy doesn’t know about that.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They found Fang the boarhound sitting outside with a bandaged tail when they went to tell Hagrid, who opened a window to talk to them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Norbert the Norwegian Ridgeback 175 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I won’t let you in,’ he puffed. ‘Norbert’s at a tricky stage – nothin’ I can’t handle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When they told him about Charlie’s letter, his eyes filled with tears, although that might have been because Norbert had just bitten him on the leg. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aargh! It’s all right, he only got my boot – jus’ playin’ – he’s only a baby, after all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The baby banged its tail on the wall, making the windows rattle. Harry and Hermione walked back to the castle, feeling Saturday couldn’t come quickly enough. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They would have felt sorry for Hagrid when the time came for him to say goodbye to Norbert if they hadn’t been so worried about what they had to do. It was a very dark, cloudy night and they were a bit late arriving at Hagrid’s hut because they’d had to wait for Peeves to get out of their way in the Entrance Hall, where he’d been playing tennis against the wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid had Norbert packed and ready in a large crate. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s got lots o’ rats an’ some brandy fer the journey,’ said Hagrid in a muffled voice. ‘An’ I’ve packed his teddy bear in case he gets lonely.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">From inside the crate came ripping noises that sounded to Harry as though teddy was having his head torn off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bye-bye, Norbert!’ Hagrid sobbed, as Harry and Hermione covered the crate with the Invisibility Cloak and stepped underneath it themselves. ‘Mummy will never forget you!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">How they managed to get the crate back up to the castle, they never knew. Midnight ticked nearer as they heaved Norbert up the marble staircase in the Entrance Hall and along the dark corridors. Up another staircase, then another – even one of Harry’s short cuts didn’t make the work much easier. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nearly there!’ Harry panted as they reached the corridor beneath the tallest tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then a sudden movement ahead of them made them almost drop the crate. Forgetting that they were already invisible, they shrank into the shadows, staring at the dark outlines of two people grappling with each other ten feet away. A lamp flared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall, in a tartan dressing-gown and a hairnet, had Malfoy by the ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Detention!’ she shouted. ‘And twenty points from Slytherin! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>176 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wandering around in the middle of the night, how  <i class=\"calibre3\">dare</i> you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t understand, Professor, Harry Potter’s coming – he’s got a dragon!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What utter rubbish! How dare you tell such lies! Come on – I shall see Professor Snape about you, Malfoy!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The steep spiral staircase up to the top of the tower seemed the easiest thing in the world after that. Not until they’d stepped out into the cold night air did they throw off the Cloak, glad to be able to breathe properly again. Hermione did a sort of jig. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy’s got detention! I could sing!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t,’ Harry advised her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Chuckling about Malfoy, they waited, Norbert thrashing about in his crate. About ten minutes later, four broomsticks came swooping down out of the darkness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Charlie’s friends were a cheery lot. They showed Harry and Hermione the harness they’d rigged up, so they could suspend Norbert between them. They all helped buckle Norbert safely into it and then Harry and Hermione shook hands with the others and thanked them very much. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last, Norbert was going … going …  <i class=\"calibre3\">gone. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They slipped back down the spiral staircase, their hearts as light as their hands, now that Norbert was off them. No more dragon – Malfoy in detention – what could spoil their happiness? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The answer to that was waiting at the foot of the stairs. As they stepped into the corridor, Filch’s face loomed suddenly out of the darkness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, well, well,’ he whispered, ‘we  <i class=\"calibre3\">are</i> in trouble.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They’d left the Invisibility Cloak on top of the tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER FIFTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Forbidden Forest </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Things couldn’t have been worse. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filch took them down to Professor McGonagall’s study on the first floor, where they sat and waited without saying a word to each other. Hermione was trembling. Excuses, alibis and wild cover-up stories chased each other around Harry’s brain, each more feeble than the last. He couldn’t see how they were going to get out of trouble this time. They were cornered. How could they have been so stupid as to forget the Cloak? There was no reason on earth that Professor McGonagall would accept for their being out of bed and creeping around the school in the dead of night, let alone being up the tallest astronomy tower, which was out-of-bounds except for classes. Add Norbert and the Invisibility Cloak and they might as well be packing their bags already. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Had Harry thought that things couldn’t have been worse? He was wrong. When Professor McGonagall appeared, she was leading Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ Neville burst out, the moment he saw the other two. ‘I was trying to find you to warn you, I heard Malfoy saying he was going to catch you, he said you had a drag–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shook his head violently to shut Neville up, but Professor McGonagall had seen. She looked more likely to breathe fire than Norbert as she towered over the three of them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I would never have believed it of any of you. Mr Filch says you were up the astronomy tower. It’s one o’clock in the morning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Explain yourselves. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was the first time Hermione had ever failed to answer a teacher’s question. She was staring at her slippers, as still as a statue. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think I’ve got a good idea of what’s been going on,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘It doesn’t take a genius to work it out. You fed Draco Malfoy some cock-and-bull story about a dragon, trying </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>178 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">to get him out of bed and into trouble. I’ve already caught him. I suppose you think it’s funny that Longbottom here heard the story and believed it, too?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry caught Neville’s eye and tried to tell him without words that this wasn’t true, because Neville was looking stunned and hurt. Poor, blundering Neville – Harry knew what it must have cost him to try and find them in the dark, to warn them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m disgusted,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘Four students out of bed in one night! I’ve never heard of such a thing before! You, Miss Granger, I thought you had more sense. As for you, Mr Potter, I thought Gryffindor meant more to you than this. All three of you will receive detentions – yes, you too, Mr Longbottom,  <i class=\"calibre3\">nothing</i> gives you the right to walk around school at night, especially these days, it’s very dangerous – and fifty points will be taken from Gryffindor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Fifty? </i>’ Harry gasped – they would lose the lead, the lead he’d won in the last Quidditch match. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fifty points  <i class=\"calibre3\">each</i>,’ said Professor McGonagall, breathing heavily through her long pointed nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor – please –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You  <i class=\"calibre3\">can’t</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t tell me what I can and can’t do, Potter. Now get back to bed, all of you. I’ve never been more ashamed of Gryffindor students.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A hundred and fifty points lost. That put Gryffindor in last place. In one night, they’d ruined any chance Gryffindor had had for the House Cup. Harry felt as though the bottom had dropped out of his stomach. How could they ever make up for this? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t sleep all night. He could hear Neville sobbing into his pillow for what seemed like hours. Harry couldn’t think of anything to say to comfort him. He knew Neville, like himself, was dreading the dawn. What would happen when the rest of Gryffindor found out what they’d done? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At first, Gryffindors passing the giant hour-glasses that record-ed the house points next day thought there’d been a mistake. How could they suddenly have a hundred and fifty points fewer than yesterday? And then the story started to spread: Harry Potter, the famous Harry Potter, their hero of two Quidditch matches, had lost them all those points, him and a couple of other stupid first-years. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Forbidden Forest 179 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">From being one of the most popular and admired people at the school, Harry was suddenly the most hated. Even Ravenclaws and Hufflepuffs turned on him, because everyone had been longing to see Slytherin lose the House Cup. Everywhere Harry went, people pointed and didn’t trouble to lower their voices as they insulted him. Slytherins, on the other hand, clapped as he walked past them, whistling and cheering, ‘Thanks Potter, we owe you one!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Only Ron stood by him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’ll all forget this in a few weeks. Fred and George have lost loads of points in all the time they’ve been here, and people still like them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’ve never lost a hundred and fifty points in one go, though, have they?’ said Harry miserably. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – no,’ Ron admitted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a bit late to repair the damage, but Harry swore to himself not to meddle in things that weren’t his business from now on. He’d had it with sneaking around and spying. He felt so ashamed of himself that he went to Wood and offered to resign from the Quidditch team. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Resign? </i>’ Wood thundered. ‘What good’ll that do? How are we going to get any points back if we can’t win at Quidditch?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But even Quidditch had lost its fun. The rest of the team wouldn’t speak to Harry during practice, and if they had to speak about him, they called him ‘the Seeker’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione and Neville were suffering, too. They didn’t have as bad a time as Harry, because they weren’t as well known, but nobody would speak to them either. Hermione had stopped drawing attention to herself in class, keeping her head down and working in silence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was almost glad that the exams weren’t far away. All the revision he had to do kept his mind off his misery. He, Ron and Hermione kept to themselves, working late into the night, trying to remember the ingredients in complicated potions, learn charms and spells off by heart, memorise the dates of magical discoveries and goblin rebellions … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, about a week before the exams were due to start, Harry’s new resolution not to interfere in anything that didn’t concern him was put to an unexpected test. Walking back from the library on his own one afternoon, he heard somebody whimpering from a classroom up ahead. As he drew closer, he heard Quirrell’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>180 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No – no – not again, please –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It sounded as though someone was threatening him. Harry moved closer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right – all right –’ he heard Quirrell sob. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Next second, Quirrell came hurrying out of the classroom, straightening his turban. He was pale and looked as though he was  about  to  cry.  He  strode  out  of  sight;  Harry  didn’t  think Quirrell had even noticed him. He waited until Quirrell’s footsteps had disappeared, then peered into the classroom. It was empty, but a door stood ajar at the other end. Harry was halfway towards it before he remembered what he’d promised himself about not meddling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All the same, he’d have gambled twelve Philosopher’s Stones that Snape had just left the room, and from what Harry had just heard, Snape would be walking with a new spring in his step – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell seemed to have given in at last. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went back to the library, where Hermione was testing Ron on Astronomy. Harry told them what he’d heard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Snape’s done it, then!’ said Ron. ‘If Quirrell’s told him how to break his Anti-Dark Force spell –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s still Fluffy, though,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe Snape’s found out how to get past him without asking Hagrid,’ said Ron, looking up at the thousands of books surrounding them. ‘I bet there’s a book somewhere in here, telling you how to get past a giant three-headed dog. So what do we do, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The light of adventure was kindling again in Ron’s eyes, but Hermione answered before Harry could. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go to Dumbledore. That’s what we should have done ages ago. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">If we try anything ourselves we’ll be thrown out for sure.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But we’ve got no  <i class=\"calibre3\">proof! </i>’ said Harry. ‘Quirrell’s too scared to back us up. Snape’s only got to say he doesn’t know how the troll got in at Hallowe’en and that he was nowhere near the third floor </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– who do you think they’ll believe, him or us? It’s not exactly a secret we hate him, Dumbledore’ll think we made it up to get him sacked. Filch wouldn’t help us if his life depended on it, he’s too friendly with Snape, and the more students get thrown out, the better, he’ll think. And don’t forget, we’re not supposed to know about the Stone or Fluffy. That’ll take a lot of explaining.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione looked convinced, but Ron didn’t. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If we just do a bit of poking around –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Forbidden Forest 181 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry flatly, ‘we’ve done enough poking around.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled a map of Jupiter towards him and started to learn the names of its moons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The following morning, notes were delivered to Harry, Hermione and Neville at the breakfast table. They were all the same: <i class=\"calibre3\">Your detention will take place at eleven o’clock tonight. Meet</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Mr Filch in the Entrance Hall. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Prof. M. McGonagall</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had forgotten they still had detentions to do in the furore over the points they’d lost. He half expected Hermione to complain that this was a whole night of revision lost, but she didn’t say a word. Like Harry, she felt they deserved what they’d got. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At eleven o’clock that night they said goodbye to Ron in the common room and went down to the entrance hall with Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filch was already there – and so was Malfoy. Harry had also forgotten that Malfoy had got a detention, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Follow me,’ said Filch, lighting a lamp and leading them outside. ‘I bet you’ll think twice about breaking a school rule again, won’t you, eh?’ he continued, leering at them. ‘Oh yes … hard work and pain are the best teachers if you ask me … It’s just a pity they let the old punishments die out … hang you by your wrists from the ceiling for a few days, I’ve got the chains still in my office, keep ’em well oiled in case they’re ever needed … Right, off we go, and don’t think of running off, now, it’ll be worse for you if you do.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They marched off across the dark grounds. Neville kept sniff-ing. Harry wondered what their punishment was going to be. It must be something really horrible, or Filch wouldn’t be sounding so delighted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The moon was bright, but clouds scudding across it kept throwing them into darkness. Ahead, Harry could see the lighted windows of Hagrid’s hut. Then they heard a distant shout. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is that you, Filch? Hurry up, I want ter get started.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s heart rose; if they were going to be working with Hagrid it wouldn’t be so bad. His relief must have showed in his face, because Filch said, ‘I suppose you think you’ll be enjoying yourself with that oaf? Well, think again,  boy  –  it’s  into  the  Forest </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>182 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you’re going and I’m much mistaken if you’ll all come out in one piece.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At this, Neville let out a little moan and Malfoy stopped dead in his tracks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Forest?’ he repeated, and he didn’t sound quite as cool as usual. ‘We can’t go in there at night – there’s all sorts of things in there – werewolves, I heard.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville clutched the sleeve of Harry’s robe and made a choking noise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s your lookout, isn’t it?’ said Filch, his voice cracking with glee. ‘Should’ve thought of them werewolves before you got in trouble, shouldn’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid came striding towards them out of the dark, Fang at his heel. He was carrying his large crossbow, and a quiver of arrows hung over his shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Abou’ time,’ he said. ‘I bin waitin’ fer half an hour already. All right, Harry, Hermione?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I shouldn’t be too friendly to them, Hagrid,’ said Filch coldly, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘they’re here to be punished, after all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s why yer late, is it?’ said Hagrid, frowning at Filch. ‘Bin lecturin’ them, eh? ’Snot your place ter do that. Yeh’ve done yer bit, I’ll take over from here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll  be  back  at  dawn,’  said  Filch,  ‘for  what’s  left  of  them,’  he added nastily, and he turned and started back towards the castle, his lamp bobbing away in the darkness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy now turned to Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not going in that Forest,’ he said, and Harry was pleased to hear the note of panic in his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh are if yeh want ter stay at Hogwarts,’ said Hagrid fiercely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh’ve done wrong an’ now yeh’ve got ter pay fer it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But this is servant stuff, it’s not for students to do. I thought we’d be writing lines or something. If my father knew I was doing this, he’d –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– tell yer that’s how it is at Hogwarts,’ Hagrid growled. ‘Writin’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">lines! What good’s that ter anyone? Yeh’ll do summat useful or yeh’ll get out. If yeh think yer father’d rather you were expelled, then get back off ter the castle an’ pack. Go on!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy didn’t move. He looked at Hagrid furiously but then dropped his gaze. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right then,’ said Hagrid, ‘now, listen carefully, ’cause it’s dan-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Forbidden Forest 183 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">gerous what we’re gonna do tonight an’ I don’ want no one takin’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">risks. Follow me over here a moment.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He led them to the very edge of the Forest. Holding his lamp up high he pointed down a narrow, winding earth track that disappeared into the thick black trees. A light breeze lifted their hair as they looked into the Forest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look there,’ said Hagrid, ‘see that stuff shinin’ on the ground? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Silvery stuff? That’s unicorn blood. There’s a unicorn in there bin hurt badly by summat. This is the second time in a week. I found one dead last Wednesday. We’re gonna try an’ find the poor thing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">We might have ter put it out of its misery.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what if whatever hurt the unicorn finds us first?’ said Malfoy, unable to keep the fear out of his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s nothin’ that lives in the Forest that’ll hurt yeh if yer with me or Fang,’ said Hagrid. ‘An’ keep ter the path. Right, now, we’re gonna split inter two parties an’ follow the trail in diff’rent directions. There’s blood all over the place, it must’ve bin stag-gerin’ around since last night at least.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I want Fang,’ said Malfoy quickly, looking at Fang’s long teeth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, but I warn yeh, he’s a coward,’ said Hagrid. ‘So me, Harry an’ Hermione’ll go one way an’ Draco, Neville an’ Fang’ll go the other. Now, if any of us finds the unicorn, we’ll send up green sparks, right? Get yer wands out an’ practise now – that’s it – an’ if anyone gets in trouble, send up red sparks, an’ we’ll all come an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">find yeh – so, be careful – let’s go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Forest was black and silent. A little way into it they reached a fork in the earth path and Harry, Hermione and Hagrid took the left path while Malfoy, Neville and Fang took the right. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They walked in silence, their eyes on the ground. Every now and then a ray of moonlight through the branches above lit a spot of silver blue blood on the fallen leaves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry saw that Hagrid looked very worried. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Could</i> a werewolf be killing the unicorns?’ Harry asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not fast enough,’ said Hagrid. ‘It’s not easy ter catch a unicorn, they’re powerful magic creatures. I never knew one ter be hurt before.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They walked past a mossy tree-stump. Harry could hear running water; there must be a stream somewhere close by. There were still spots of unicorn blood here and there along the winding path. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>184 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You all right, Hermione?’ Hagrid whispered. ‘Don’ worry, it can’t’ve gone far if it’s this badly hurt an’ then we’ll be able ter – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">GET BEHIND THAT TREE!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid seized Harry and Hermione and hoisted them off the path behind a towering oak. He pulled out an arrow and fitted it into his crossbow, raising it, ready to fire. The three of them listened. Something was slithering over dead leaves nearby: it sounded like a cloak trailing along the ground. Hagrid was squinting up the dark path, but after a few seconds, the sound faded away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I knew it,’ he murmured. ‘There’s summat in here that shouldn’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">be.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A werewolf?’ Harry suggested. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That wasn’ no werewolf an’ it wasn’ no unicorn, neither,’ said Hagrid grimly. ‘Right, follow me, but careful, now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They walked more slowly, ears straining for the faintest sound. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Suddenly, in a clearing ahead, something definitely moved. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s there?’ Hagrid called. ‘Show yerself – I’m armed!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And into the clearing came – was it a man, or a horse? To the waist, a man, with red hair and beard, but below that was a horse’s gleaming chestnut body with a long, reddish tail. Harry and Hermione’s jaws dropped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, it’s you, Ronan,’ said Hagrid in relief. ‘How are yeh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He walked forward and shook the centaur’s hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good evening to you, Hagrid,’ said Ronan. He had a deep, sorrowful voice. ‘Were you going to shoot me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t be too careful, Ronan,’ said Hagrid, patting his crossbow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s summat bad loose in this Forest. This is Harry Potter an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione Granger, by the way. Students up at the school. An’ this is Ronan, you two. He’s a centaur.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d noticed,’ said Hermione faintly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good evening,’ said Ronan. ‘Students, are you? And do you learn much, up at the school?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Erm –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A bit,’ said Hermione timidly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A bit. Well, that’s something.’ Ronan sighed. He flung back his head and stared at the sky. ‘Mars is bright tonight.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Hagrid, glancing up too. ‘Listen, I’m glad we’ve run inter yeh, Ronan, ’cause there’s a unicorn bin hurt – you seen anythin’?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Forbidden Forest 185 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ronan didn’t answer immediately. He stared unblinkingly upwards, then sighed again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Always the innocent are the first victims,’ he said. ‘So it has been for ages past, so it is now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Hagrid, ‘but have yeh seen anythin’, Ronan? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Anythin’ unusual?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mars is bright tonight,’ Ronan repeated while Hagrid watched him impatiently. ‘Unusually bright.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, but I was meanin’ anythin’ unusual a bit nearer home,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Hagrid. ‘So yeh haven’t noticed anythin’ strange?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Yet again, Ronan took a while to answer. At last, he said, ‘The Forest hides many secrets.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A movement in the trees behind Ronan made Hagrid raise his bow again, but it was only a second centaur, black-haired and  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">-bodied and wilder-looking than Ronan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hullo, Bane,’ said Hagrid. ‘All right?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good evening, Hagrid, I hope you are well?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well enough. Look, I’ve jus’ bin askin’ Ronan, you seen anythin’ odd in here lately? Only there’s a unicorn bin injured – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">would yeh know anythin’ about it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Bane walked over to stand next to Ronan. He looked skywards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mars is bright tonight,’ he said simply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve heard,’ said Hagrid grumpily. ‘Well, if either of you do see anythin’, let me know, won’t yeh? We’ll be off, then.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione followed him out of the clearing, staring over their shoulders at Ronan and Bane until the trees blocked their view. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Never,’ said Hagrid irritably, ‘try an’ get a straight answer out of a centaur. Ruddy star-gazers. Not interested in anythin’ closer’n the moon.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are there many of  <i class=\"calibre3\">them</i> in here?’ asked Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, a fair few … Keep themselves to themselves mostly, but they’re good enough about turnin’ up if ever I want a word. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They’re deep, mind, centaurs … they know things … jus’ don’ let on much.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you think that was a centaur we heard earlier?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did that sound like hooves to you? Nah, if yeh ask me, that was what’s bin killin’ the unicorns – never heard anythin’ like it before.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They walked on through the dense, dark trees. Harry kept </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>186 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">looking nervously over his shoulder. He had the nasty feeling they were being watched. He was very glad they had Hagrid and his crossbow with them. They had just passed a bend in the path when Hermione grabbed Hagrid’s arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid! Look! Red sparks, the others are in trouble!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You two wait here!’ Hagrid shouted. ‘Stay on the path, I’ll come back for yeh!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They heard him crashing away through the undergrowth and stood looking at each other, very scared, until they couldn’t hear anything but the rustling of leaves around them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t think they’ve been hurt, do you?’ whispered Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t care if Malfoy has, but if something’s got Neville … It’s our fault he’s here in the first place.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The minutes dragged by. Their ears seemed sharper than usual. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s seemed to be picking up every sigh of the wind, every cracking twig. What was going on? Where were the others? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last, a great crunching noise announced Hagrid’s return. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy, Neville and Fang were with him. Hagrid was fuming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy, it seemed, had sneaked up behind Neville and grabbed him for a joke. Neville had panicked and sent up the sparks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll be lucky ter catch anythin’ now, with the racket you two were makin’. Right, we’re changin’ groups – Neville, you stay with me an’ Hermione, Harry, you go with Fang an’ this idiot. I’m sorry,’ Hagrid added in a whisper to Harry, ‘but he’ll have a harder time frightenin’ you, an’ we’ve gotta get this done.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So Harry set off into the heart of the Forest with Malfoy and Fang. They walked for nearly half an hour, deeper and deeper into the Forest, until the path became almost impossible to follow because the trees were so thick. Harry thought the blood seemed to be getting thicker. There were splashes on the roots of a tree, as though the poor creature had been thrashing around in pain close by. Harry could see a clearing ahead, through the tangled branches of an ancient oak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look –’ he murmured, holding out his arm to stop Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something bright white was gleaming on the ground. They inched closer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was the unicorn all right, and it was dead. Harry had never seen anything so beautiful and sad. Its long slender legs were stuck out at odd angles where it had fallen and its mane was </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Forbidden Forest 187 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">spread pearly white on the dark leaves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had taken one step towards it when a slithering sound made him freeze where he stood. A bush on the edge of the clearing quivered … Then, out of the shadows, a hooded figure came crawling across the ground like some stalking beast. Harry, Malfoy and Fang stood transfixed. The cloaked figure reached the unicorn, it lowered its head over the wound in the animal’s side, and began to drink its blood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘AAAAAAAAAAARGH!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy let out a terrible scream and bolted – so did Fang. The hooded figure raised its head and looked right at Harry – unicorn blood was dribbling down its front. It got to its feet and came swiftly towards him – he couldn’t move for fear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then a pain pierced his head like he’d never felt before, it was as  though  his  scar  was  on  fire  –  half-blinded,  he  staggered  backwards. He heard hooves behind him, galloping, and something jumped clean over him, charging at the figure. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The pain in Harry’s head was so bad he fell to his knees. It took a minute or two to pass. When he looked up, the figure had gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A centaur was standing over him, not Ronan or Bane; this one looked younger; he had white-blond hair and a palomino body. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you all right?’ said the centaur, pulling Harry to his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes – thank you – what  <i class=\"calibre3\">was</i> that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The centaur didn’t answer. He had astonishingly blue eyes, like pale sapphires. He looked carefully at Harry, his eyes lingering on the scar which stood out, livid, on Harry’s forehead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You are the Potter boy,’ he said. ‘You had better get back to Hagrid. The Forest is not safe at this time – especially for you. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Can you ride? It will be quicker this way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My name is Firenze,’ he added, as he lowered himself on to his front legs so that Harry could clamber on to his back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was suddenly a sound of more galloping from the other side of the clearing. Ronan and Bane came bursting through the trees, their flanks heaving and sweaty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Firenze!’ Bane thundered. ‘What are you doing? You have a human on your back! Have you no shame? Are you a common mule?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you realise who this is?’ said Firenze. ‘This is the Potter boy. The quicker he leaves this Forest, the better.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What have you been telling him?’ growled Bane. ‘Remember, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>188 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Firenze, we are sworn not to set ourselves against the heavens. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Have we not read what is to come in the movements of the planets?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ronan pawed the ground nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sure Firenze thought he was acting for the best,’ he said, in his gloomy voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Bane kicked his back legs in anger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘For the best! What is that to do with us? Centaurs are concerned with what has been foretold! It is not our business to run around like donkeys after stray humans in our Forest!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Firenze suddenly reared on to his hind legs in anger, so that Harry had to grab his shoulders to stay on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you not see that unicorn?’ Firenze bellowed at Bane. ‘Do you not understand why it was killed? Or have the planets not let you in on that secret? I set myself against what is lurking in this Forest, Bane, yes, with humans alongside me if I must.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Firenze whisked around; with Harry clutching on as best he could, they plunged off into the trees, leaving Ronan and Bane behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t have a clue what was going on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why’s Bane so angry?’ he asked. ‘What was that thing you saved me from, anyway?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Firenze slowed to a walk, warned Harry to keep his head bowed in case of low-hanging branches but did not answer Harry’s question. They made their way through the trees in silence for so long that Harry thought Firenze didn’t want to talk to him any more. They were passing through a particularly dense patch of trees, however, when Firenze suddenly stopped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter, do you know what unicorn blood is used for?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry, startled by the odd question. ‘We’ve only used the horn and tail-hair in Potions.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That is because it is a monstrous thing, to slay a unicorn,’ said Firenze. ‘Only one who has nothing to lose, and everything to gain, would commit such a crime. The blood of a unicorn will keep you alive, even if you are an inch from death, but at a terrible price. You have slain something pure and defenceless to save yourself and you will have but a half life, a cursed life, from the moment the blood touches your lips.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared at the back of Firenze’s head, which was dappled silver in the moonlight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Forbidden Forest 189 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But who’d be that desperate?’ he wondered aloud. ‘If you’re going to be cursed for ever, death’s better, isn’t it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It is,’ Firenze agreed, ‘unless all you need is to stay alive long enough to drink something else – something that will bring you back to full strength and power – something that will mean you can never die. Mr Potter, do you know what is hidden in the school at this very moment?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Philosopher’s Stone! Of course – the Elixir of Life! But I don’t understand who –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you think of nobody who has waited many years to return to power, who has clung to life, awaiting their chance?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was as though an iron fist had clenched suddenly around Harry’s heart. Over the rustling of the trees, he seemed to hear once more what Hagrid had told him on the night they had met: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Some say he died. Codswallop, in my opinion. Dunno if he had enough human left in him to die.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you mean,’ Harry croaked, ‘that was  <i class=\"calibre3\">Vol</i>–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry! Harry, are you all right?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione was running towards them down the path, Hagrid puffing along behind her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m fine,’ said Harry, hardly knowing what he was saying. ‘The unicorn’s dead, Hagrid, it’s in that clearing back there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is where I leave you,’ Firenze murmured as Hagrid hurried off to examine the unicorn. ‘You are safe now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry slid off his back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good luck, Harry Potter,’ said Firenze. ‘The planets have been read wrongly before now, even by centaurs. I hope this is one of those times.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned and cantered back into the depths of the Forest, leaving Harry shivering behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had fallen asleep in the dark common room, waiting for them to return. He shouted something about Quidditch fouls when Harry roughly shook him awake. In a matter of seconds, though, he was wide-eyed as Harry began to tell him and Hermione what had happened in the Forest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t sit down. He paced up and down in front of the fire. He was still shaking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Snape wants the stone for Voldemort … and Voldemort’s waiting in the Forest … and all this time we thought Snape just wanted </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>190 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">to get rich …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop saying the name!’ said Ron in a terrified whisper, as if he thought Voldemort could hear them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wasn’t listening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Firenze saved me, but he shouldn’t have done … Bane was furious … he was talking about interfering with what the planets say is going to happen … They must show that Voldemort’s coming back … Bane thinks Firenze should have let Voldemort kill me … I suppose that’s written in the stars as well.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Will you stop saying the name! </i>’ Ron hissed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So all I’ve got to wait for now is Snape to steal the Stone,’ Harry went on feverishly, ‘then Voldemort will be able to come and finish me off … Well, I suppose Bane’ll be happy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione looked very frightened, but she had a word of comfort. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, everyone says Dumbledore’s the only one You-Know-Who was ever afraid of. With Dumbledore around, You-Know-Who won’t touch you. Anyway, who says the centaurs are right? It sounds like fortune-telling to me, and Professor McGonagall says that’s a very imprecise branch of magic.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The sky had turned light before they stopped talking. They went to bed exhausted, their throats sore. But the night’s surprises weren’t over. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Harry pulled back his sheets, he found his Invisibility Cloak folded neatly underneath them. There was a note pinned to it: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Just in case. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER SIXTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Through the Trapdoor </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In years to come, Harry would never quite remember how he had managed to get through his exams when he half expected Voldemort to come bursting through the door at any moment. Yet the days crept by and there could be no doubt that Fluffy was still alive and well behind the locked door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was swelteringly hot, especially in the large classroom where they did their written papers. They had been given special, new quills for the exams, which had been bewitched with an Anti-Cheating spell. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had practical exams as well. Professor Flitwick called them one by one into his class to see if they could make a pineapple tap-dance across a desk. Professor McGonagall watched them turn a mouse into a snuff-box – points were given for how pretty the snuff-box was, but taken away if it had whiskers. Snape made them all nervous, breathing down their necks while they tried to remember how to make a Forgetfulness Potion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry did the best he could, trying to ignore the stabbing pains in his forehead which had been bothering him ever since his trip into the Forest. Neville thought Harry had a bad case of exam nerves because Harry couldn’t sleep, but the truth was that Harry kept being woken by his old nightmare, except that it was now worse than ever because there was a hooded figure dripping blood in it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Maybe it was because they hadn’t seen what Harry had seen in the Forest, or because they didn’t have scars burning on their foreheads, but Ron and Hermione didn’t seem as worried about the Stone as Harry. The idea of Voldemort certainly scared them, but he didn’t keep visiting them in dreams, and they were so busy with their revision they didn’t have much time to fret about what Snape or anyone else might be up to. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>192 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Their very last exam was History of Magic. One hour of answer-ing questions about batty old wizards who’d invented self-stirring cauldrons and they’d be free, free for a whole wonderful week until their exam results came out. When the ghost of Professor Binns told them to put down their quills and roll up their parchment, Harry couldn’t help cheering with the rest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was far easier than I thought it would be,’ said Hermione, as they joined the crowds flocking out into the sunny grounds. ‘I needn’t have learnt about the 1637 Werewolf Code of Conduct or the uprising of Elfric the Eager.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione always liked to go through their exam papers afterwards, but Ron said this made him feel ill, so they wandered down to the lake and flopped under a tree. The Weasley twins and Lee Jordan were tickling the tentacles of a giant squid, which was bask-ing in the warm shallows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No more revision,’ Ron sighed happily, stretching out on the grass. ‘You could look more cheerful, Harry, we’ve got a week before we find out how badly we’ve done, there’s no need to worry yet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was rubbing his forehead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wish I knew what this  <i class=\"calibre3\">means! </i>’ he burst out angrily. ‘My scar keeps hurting – it’s happened before, but never as often as this.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go to Madam Pomfrey,’ Hermione suggested. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not ill,’ said Harry. ‘I think it’s a warning … it means danger’s coming …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron couldn’t get worked up, it was too hot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, relax, Hermione’s right, the Stone’s safe as long as Dumbledore’s around. Anyway, we’ve never had any proof Snape found out how to get past Fluffy. He nearly had his leg ripped off once, he’s not going to try it again in a hurry. And Neville will play Quidditch for England before Hagrid lets Dumbledore down.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry nodded, but he couldn’t shake off a lurking feeling that there was something he’d forgotten to do, something important. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When he tried to explain this, Hermione said, ‘That’s just the exams. I woke up last night and was halfway through my Transfiguration notes before I remembered we’d done that one.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was quite sure the unsettled feeling didn’t have anything to do with work, though. He watched an owl flutter towards the school across the bright blue sky, a note clamped in its mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was the only one who ever sent him letters. Hagrid would never betray Dumbledore. Hagrid would never tell anyone how to </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the Trapdoor 193 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">get past Fluffy … never … but – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry suddenly jumped to his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’re you going?’ said Ron sleepily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve just thought of something,’ said Harry. He had gone white. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got to go and see Hagrid, now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why?’ panted Hermione, hurrying to keep up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t you think it’s a bit odd,’ said Harry, scrambling up the grassy slope, ‘that what Hagrid wants more than anything else is a dragon, and a stranger turns up who just happens to have an egg in his pocket? How many people wander around with dragon eggs if it’s against wizard law? Lucky they found Hagrid, don’t you think? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Why didn’t I see it before?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you on about?’ said Ron, but Harry, sprinting across the grounds towards the Forest, didn’t answer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was sitting in an armchair outside his house; his trousers and sleeves were rolled up and he was shelling peas into a large bowl. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hullo,’ he said, smiling. ‘Finished yer exams? Got time fer a drink?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, please,’ said Ron, but Harry cut across him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, we’re in a hurry. Hagrid, I’ve got to ask you something. You know that night you won Norbert? What did the stranger you were playing cards with look like?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno,’ said Hagrid casually, ‘he wouldn’ take his cloak off.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He saw the three of them look stunned and raised his eyebrows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not that unusual, yeh get a lot o’ funny folk in the Hog’s Head </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– that’s one of the pubs down in the village. Mighta bin a dragon dealer, mightn’ he? I never saw his face, he kept his hood up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sank down next to the bowl of peas. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What did you talk to him about, Hagrid? Did you mention Hogwarts at all?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mighta come up,’ said Hagrid, frowning as he tried to remember. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah … he asked what I did, an’ I told him I was gamekeeper here </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… He asked a bit about the sorta creatures I look after … so I told him … an’ I said what I’d always really wanted was a dragon … an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">then … I can’ remember too well, ’cause he kept buyin’ me drinks … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Let’s see … yeah, then he said he had the dragon egg an’ we could play cards fer it if I wanted … but he had ter be sure I could handle it, he didn’ want it ter go ter any old home … So I told him, after Fluffy, a dragon would be easy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>194 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And did he – did he seem interested in Fluffy?’ Harry asked, trying to keep his voice calm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – yeah – how many three-headed dogs d’yeh meet, even around Hogwarts? So I told him, Fluffy’s a piece o’ cake if yeh know how to calm him down, jus’ play him a bit o’ music an’ he’ll go straight off ter sleep –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid suddenly looked horrified. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I shouldn’ta told yeh that!’ he blurted out. ‘Forget I said it! Hey </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– where’re yeh goin’?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione didn’t speak to each other at all until they came to a halt in the Entrance Hall, which seemed very cold and gloomy after the grounds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got to go to Dumbledore,’ said Harry. ‘Hagrid told that stranger how to get past Fluffy and it was either Snape or Voldemort under that cloak – it must’ve been easy, once he’d got Hagrid drunk. I just hope Dumbledore believes us. Firenze might back us up if Bane doesn’t stop him. Where’s Dumbledore’s office?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They looked around, as if hoping to see a sign pointing them in the right direction. They had never been told where Dumbledore lived, nor did they know anyone who had been sent to see him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll just have to –’ Harry began, but a voice suddenly rang across the hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you three doing inside?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Professor McGonagall, carrying a large pile of books. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We want to see Professor Dumbledore,’ said Hermione, rather bravely, Harry and Ron thought. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See Professor Dumbledore?’ Professor McGonagall repeated, as though this was a very fishy thing to want to do. ‘Why?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry swallowed – now what? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s sort of secret,’ he said, but he wished at once he hadn’t, because Professor McGonagall’s nostrils flared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore left ten minutes ago,’ she said coldly. ‘He received an urgent owl from the Ministry of Magic and flew off for London at once.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s  <i class=\"calibre3\">gone? </i>’ said Harry frantically. ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Now? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore is a very great wizard, Potter, he has many demands on his time –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But this is important.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Something you have to say is more important than the Ministry of Magic, Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the Trapdoor 195 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look,’ said Harry, throwing caution to the winds, ‘Professor – it’s about the Philosopher’s Stone –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Whatever Professor McGonagall had expected, it wasn’t that. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The books she was carrying tumbled out of her arms but she didn’t pick them up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How do you know –?’ she spluttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor, I think – I  <i class=\"calibre3\">know</i> – that Sn– that someone’s going to try and steal the Stone. I’ve got to talk to Professor Dumbledore.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She eyed him with a mixture of shock and suspicion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore will be back tomorrow,’ she said finally. ‘I don’t know how you found out about the Stone, but rest assured, no one can possibly steal it, it’s too well protected.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Professor –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter, I know what I’m talking about,’ she said shortly. She bent down and gathered up the fallen books. ‘I suggest you all go back outside and enjoy the sunshine.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But they didn’t. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s tonight,’ said Harry, once he was sure Professor McGonagall was out of earshot. ‘Snape’s going through the trapdoor tonight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He’s found out everything he needs and now he’s got Dumbledore out of the way. He sent that note, I bet the Ministry of Magic will get a real shock when Dumbledore turns up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But what can we –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione gasped. Harry and Ron wheeled round. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape was standing there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good afternoon,’ he said smoothly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They stared at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You shouldn’t be inside on a day like this,’ he said, with an odd, twisted smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We were –’ Harry began, without any idea what he was going to say. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You want to be more careful,’ said Snape. ‘Hanging around like this, people will think you’re up to something. And Gryffindor really can’t afford to lose any more points, can they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry flushed. They turned to go back outside, but Snape called them back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Be warned, Potter – any more night-time wanderings and I will personally make sure you are expelled. Good day to you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He strode off in the direction of the staff room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Out on the stone steps, Harry turned to the others. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>196 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right, here’s what we’ve got to do,’ he whispered urgently. ‘One of us has got to keep an eye on Snape – wait outside the staff room and follow him if he leaves it. Hermione, you’d better do that.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s obvious,’ said Ron. ‘You can pretend to be waiting for Professor Flitwick, you know.’ He put on a high voice, ‘Oh Professor Flitwick, I’m so worried, I think I got question fourteen b wrong …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, shut up,’ said Hermione, but she agreed to go and watch out for Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And we’d better stay outside the third-floor corridor,’ Harry told Ron. ‘Come on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But that part of the plan didn’t work. No sooner had they reached the door separating Fluffy from the rest of the school than Professor McGonagall turned up again, and this time, she lost her temper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I suppose you think you’re harder to get past than a pack of enchantments!’ she stormed. ‘Enough of this nonsense! If I hear you’ve come anywhere near here again, I’ll take another fifty points from Gryffindor! Yes, Weasley, from my own house!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron went back to the common room. Harry had just said, ‘At least Hermione’s on Snape’s tail,’ when the portrait of the Fat Lady swung open and Hermione came in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sorry, Harry!’ she wailed. ‘Snape came out and asked me what I was doing, so I said I was waiting for Flitwick, and Snape went to get him, and I’ve only just got away. I don’t know where Snape went.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, that’s it then, isn’t it?’ Harry said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The other two stared at him. He was pale and his eyes were glittering. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going out of here tonight and I’m going to try and get to the Stone first.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re mad!’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can’t!’ said Hermione. ‘After what McGonagall and Snape have said? You’ll be expelled!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘SO WHAT?’ Harry shouted. ‘Don’t you understand? If Snape gets hold of the Stone, Voldemort’s coming back! Haven’t you heard what it was like when he was trying to take over? There won’t be any Hogwarts to get expelled from! He’ll flatten it, or turn it into a school for the Dark Arts! Losing points doesn’t matter any more, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the Trapdoor 197 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">can’t you see? D’you think he’ll leave you and your families alone if Gryffindor win the House Cup? If I get caught before I can get to the Stone, well, I’ll have to go back to the Dursleys and wait for Voldemort to find me there. It’s only dying a bit later than I would have done, because I’m never going over to the Dark Side! I’m going through that trapdoor tonight and nothing you two say is going to stop me! Voldemort killed my parents, remember?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He glared at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re right, Harry,’ said Hermione in a small voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll use the Invisibility Cloak,’ said Harry. ‘It’s just lucky I got it back.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But will it cover all three of us?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All – all three of us?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, come off it, you don’t think we’d let you go alone?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course not,’ said Hermione briskly. ‘How do you think you’d get to the Stone without us? I’d better go and look through my books, there might be something useful …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if we get caught, you two will be expelled, too.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not if I can help it,’ said Hermione grimly. ‘Flitwick told me in secret that I got a hundred and twelve per cent on his exam. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They’re not throwing me out after that.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After dinner the three of them sat nervously apart in the common room. Nobody bothered them; none of the Gryffindors had anything to say to Harry any more, after all. This was the first night he hadn’t been upset by it. Hermione was skimming through all her notes, hoping to come across one of the enchantments they were about to try and break. Harry and Ron didn’t talk much. Both of them were thinking about what they were about to do. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slowly, the room emptied as people drifted off to bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Better get the Cloak,’ Ron muttered, as Lee Jordan finally left, stretching and yawning. Harry ran upstairs to their dark dormitory. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled out the Cloak and then his eyes fell on the flute Hagrid had given him for Christmas. He pocketed it to use on Fluffy – he didn’t feel much like singing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He ran back down to the common room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d better put the Cloak on here, and make sure it covers all three of us – if Filch spots one of our feet wandering along on its own –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing?’ said a voice from the corner of the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>198 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville appeared from behind an armchair, clutching Trevor the toad, who looked as though he’d been making another bid for freedom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing, Neville, nothing,’ said Harry, hurriedly putting the Cloak behind his back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville stared at their guilty faces. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re going out again,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, no, no,’ said Hermione. ‘No, we’re not. Why don’t you go to bed, Neville?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked at the grandfather clock by the door. They couldn’t afford to waste any more time, Snape might even now be playing Fluffy to sleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can’t go out,’ said Neville, ‘you’ll be caught again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor will be in even more trouble.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t understand,’ said Harry, ‘this is important.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Neville was clearly steeling himself to do something desperate. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I won’t let you do it,’ he said, hurrying to stand in front of the portrait hole. ‘I’ll – I’ll fight you!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Neville, </i>’ Ron exploded, ‘get away from that hole and don’t be an idiot –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t you call me an idiot!’ said Neville. ‘I don’t think you should be breaking any more rules! And you were the one who told me to stand up to people!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, but not to  <i class=\"calibre3\">us, </i>’ said Ron in exasperation. ‘Neville, you don’t know what you’re doing.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He took a step forward and Neville dropped Trevor the toad, who leapt out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go on then, try and hit me!’ said Neville, raising his fists. ‘I’m ready!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned to Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Do something, </i>’ he said desperately. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione stepped forward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Neville,’ she said, ‘I’m really, really sorry about this.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She raised her wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Petrificus Totalus! </i>’ she cried, pointing it at Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville’s arms snapped to his sides. His legs sprang together. His whole body rigid, he swayed where he stood and then fell flat on his face, stiff as a board. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione ran to turn him over. Neville’s jaws were jammed </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the Trapdoor 199 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">together so he couldn’t speak. Only his eyes were moving, looking at them in horror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’ve you done to him?’ Harry whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s the full Body-Bind,’ said Hermione miserably. ‘Oh, Neville, I’m so sorry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We had to, Neville, no time to explain,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ll understand later, Neville,’ said Ron, as they stepped over him and pulled on the Invisibility Cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But leaving Neville lying motionless on the floor didn’t feel like a very good omen. In their nervous state, every statue’s shadow looked like Filch, every distant breath of wind sounded like Peeves swooping down on them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At the foot of the first set of stairs, they spotted Mrs Norris skulking near the top. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, let’s kick her, just this once,’ Ron whispered in Harry’s ear, but Harry shook his head. As they climbed carefully around her, Mrs Norris turned her lamp-like eyes on them, but didn’t do anything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They didn’t meet anyone else until they reached the staircase up to the third floor. Peeves was bobbing halfway up, loosening the carpet so that people would trip. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s there?’ he said suddenly as they climbed towards him. He narrowed his wicked black eyes. ‘Know you’re there, even if I can’t see you. Are you ghoulie or ghostie or wee student beastie?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He rose up in the air and floated there, squinting at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Should call Filch, I should, if something’s a-creeping around unseen.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had a sudden idea. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Peeves,’ he said, in a hoarse whisper, ‘the Bloody Baron has his own reasons for being invisible.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peeves almost fell out of the air in shock. He caught himself in time and hovered about a foot off the stairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So sorry, your bloodiness, Mr Baron, sir,’ he said greasily. ‘My mistake, my mistake – I didn’t see you – of course I didn’t, you’re invisible – forgive old Peevsie his little joke, sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have business here, Peeves,’ croaked Harry. ‘Stay away from this place tonight.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I will, sir, I most certainly will,’ said Peeves, rising up in the air again. ‘Hope your business goes well, Baron, I’ll not bother you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he scooted off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>200 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Brilliant, </i> Harry!’ whispered Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A few seconds later, they were there, outside the third-floor corridor – and the door was already ajar. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, there you are,’ Harry said quietly. ‘Snape’s already got past Fluffy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Seeing the open door somehow seemed to impress upon all three of them what was facing them. Underneath the Cloak, Harry turned to the other two. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you want to go back, I won’t blame you,’ he said. ‘You can take the Cloak, I won’t need it now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be stupid,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re coming,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pushed the door open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the door creaked, low, rumbling growls met their ears. All three of the dog’s noses sniffed madly in their direction, even though it couldn’t see them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that at its feet?’ Hermione whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Looks like a harp,’ said Ron. ‘Snape must have left it there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It must wake up the moment you stop playing,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, here goes …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He put Hagrid’s flute to his lips and blew. It wasn’t really a tune, but from the first note the beast’s eyes began to droop. Harry hardly drew breath. Slowly, the dog’s growls ceased – it tottered on its paws and fell to its knees, then it slumped to the ground, fast asleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Keep playing,’ Ron warned Harry as they slipped out of the Cloak and crept towards the trapdoor. They could feel the dog’s hot, smelly breath as they approached the giant heads. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think we’ll be able to pull the door open,’ said Ron, peering over the dog’s back. ‘Want to go first, Hermione?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, I don’t!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right.’ Ron gritted his teeth and stepped carefully over the dog’s legs. He bent and pulled the ring of the trapdoor, which swung up and open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What can you see?’ Hermione said anxiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing – just black – there’s no way of climbing down, we’ll just have to drop.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who was still playing the flute, waved at Ron to get his attention and pointed at himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You want to go first? Are you sure?’ said Ron. ‘I don’t know how </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the Trapdoor 201 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">deep this thing goes. Give the flute to Hermione so she can keep him asleep.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry handed the flute over. In the few seconds’ silence, the dog growled and twitched, but the moment Hermione began to play, it fell back into its deep sleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry climbed over it and looked down through the trapdoor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was no sign of the bottom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He lowered himself through the hole until he was hanging on by his fingertips. Then he looked up at Ron and said, ‘If anything happens to me, don’t follow. Go straight to the owlery and send Hedwig to Dumbledore, right?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See you in a minute, I hope …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Harry let go. Cold, damp air rushed past him as he fell down, down, down and – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">FLUMP. With a funny, muffled sort of thump he landed on something soft. He sat up and felt around, his eyes not used to the gloom. It felt as though he was sitting on some sort of plant. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s OK!’ he called up to the light the size of a postage stamp which was the open trapdoor. ‘It’s a soft landing, you can jump!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron followed straight away. He landed sprawled next to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s this stuff?’ were his first words. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno, sort of plant thing. I suppose it’s here to break the fall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Come on, Hermione!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The distant music stopped. There was a loud bark from the dog, but Hermione had already jumped. She landed on Harry’s other side. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We must be miles under the school,’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lucky this plant thing’s here, really,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Lucky! </i>’ shrieked Hermione. ‘Look at you both!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She leapt up and struggled towards a damp wall. She had to struggle because the moment she had landed, the plant had started to twist snake-like tendrils around her ankles. As for Harry and Ron, their legs had already been bound tightly in long creepers without their noticing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione had managed to free herself before the plant got a firm grip on her. Now she watched in horror as the two boys fought to pull the plant off them, but the more they strained against it, the tighter and faster the plant wound around them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop moving!’ Hermione ordered them. ‘I know what this is – it’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>202 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Devil’s Snare!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, I’m so glad we know what it’s called, that’s a great help,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">snarled Ron, leaning back, trying to stop the plant curling around his neck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up, I’m trying to remember how to kill it!’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, hurry up, I can’t breathe!’ Harry gasped, wrestling with it as it curled around his chest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Devil’s Snare, Devil’s Snare … What did Professor Sprout say? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It likes the dark and the damp –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So light a fire!’ Harry choked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes – of course – but there’s no wood!’ Hermione cried, wringing her hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HAVE YOU GONE MAD?’ Ron bellowed. ‘ARE YOU A WITCH </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">OR NOT?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, right!’ said Hermione, and she whipped out her wand, waved it, muttered something and sent a jet of the same bluebell flames she had used on Snape at the plant. In a matter of seconds, the two boys felt it loosening its grip as it cringed away from the light and warmth. Wriggling and flailing, it unravelled itself from their bodies and they were able to pull free. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lucky you pay attention in Herbology, Hermione,’ said Harry as he joined her by the wall, wiping sweat off his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Ron, ‘and lucky Harry doesn’t lose his head in a crisis </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– “there’s no wood”,  <i class=\"calibre3\">honestly. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This way,’ said Harry, pointing down a stone passageway which was the only way on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All they could hear apart from their footsteps was the gentle drip of water trickling down the walls. The passageway sloped downwards and Harry was reminded of Gringotts. With an unpleasant jolt of the heart, he remembered the dragons said to be guarding vaults in the wizards’ bank. If they met a dragon, a fully grown dragon – Norbert had been bad enough … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you hear something?’ Ron whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry listened. A soft rustling and clinking seemed to be coming from up ahead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you think it’s a ghost?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know … sounds like wings to me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s light ahead – I can see something moving.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They reached the end of the passageway and saw before them a brilliantly lit chamber, its ceiling arching high above them. It was </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the Trapdoor 203 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">full of small, jewel-bright birds, fluttering and tumbling all around the room. On the opposite side of the chamber was a heavy, wooden door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you think they’ll attack us if we cross the room?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Probably,’ said Harry. ‘They don’t look very vicious, but I suppose if they all swooped down at once … Well, there’s nothing for it </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… I’ll run.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He took a deep breath, covered his face with his arms and sprinted across the room. He expected to feel sharp beaks and claws tearing at him any second, but nothing happened. He reached the door untouched. He pulled the handle, but it was locked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The other two followed him. They tugged and heaved at the door, but it wouldn’t budge, not even when Hermione tried her Alohomora Charm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now what?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘These birds … they can’t be here just for decoration,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They watched the birds soaring overhead, glittering –  <i class=\"calibre3\">glittering? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re not birds!’ Harry said suddenly, ‘they’re  <i class=\"calibre3\">keys! </i> Winged keys – look carefully. So that must mean …’ he looked around the chamber while the other two squinted up at the flock of keys. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… Yes – look! Broomsticks! We’ve got to catch the key to the door!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But there are  <i class=\"calibre3\">hundreds</i> of them!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron examined the lock on the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re looking for a big, old-fashioned one – probably silver, like the handle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They seized a broomstick each and kicked off into the air, soaring into the midst of the cloud of keys. They grabbed and snatched but the bewitched keys darted and dived so quickly it was almost impossible to catch one. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Not for nothing, though, was Harry the youngest Seeker in a century. He had a knack for spotting things other people didn’t. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After a minute’s weaving about through the whirl of rainbow feathers, he noticed a large silver key that had a bent wing, as if it had already been caught and stuffed roughly into the keyhole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That one!’ he called to the others. ‘That big one – there – no, there – with bright blue wings – the feathers are all crumpled on one side.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron went speeding in the direction that Harry was pointing, crashed into the ceiling and nearly fell off his broom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>204 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got to close in on it!’ Harry called, not taking his eyes off the key with the damaged wing. ‘Ron, you come at it from above – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione, stay below and stop it going down – and I’ll try and catch it. Right, NOW!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron dived, Hermione rocketed upwards, the key dodged them both and Harry streaked after it; it sped towards the wall, Harry leant forward and with a nasty crunching noise, pinned it against the stone with one hand. Ron and Hermione’s cheers echoed around the high chamber. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They landed quickly and Harry ran to the door, the key struggling in his hand. He rammed it into the lock and turned – it worked. The moment the lock had clicked open, the key took flight again, looking very battered now that it had been caught twice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready?’ Harry asked the other two, his hand on the door handle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They nodded. He pulled the door open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The next chamber was so dark they couldn’t see anything at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But as they stepped into it, light suddenly flooded the room to reveal an astonishing sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were standing on the edge of a huge chessboard, behind the black chessmen, which were all taller than they were and carved from what looked like black stone. Facing them, way across the chamber, were the white pieces. Harry, Ron and Hermione shivered slightly – the towering white chessmen had no faces. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now what do we do?’ Harry whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s obvious, isn’t it?’ said Ron. ‘We’ve got to play our way across the room.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Behind the white pieces they could see another door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How?’ said Hermione nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think,’ said Ron, ‘we’re going to have to be chessmen.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He walked up to a black knight and put his hand out to touch the knight’s horse. At once, the stone sprang to life. The horse pawed the ground and the knight turned his helmeted head to look down at Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do we – er – have to join you to get across?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The black knight nodded. Ron turned to the other two. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This wants thinking about …’ he said. ‘I suppose we’ve got to take the place of three of the black pieces …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione stayed quiet, watching Ron think. Finally he said, ‘Now, don’t be offended or anything, but neither of you are that good at chess –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the Trapdoor 205 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re not offended,’ said Harry quickly. ‘Just tell us what to do.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, Harry, you take the place of that bishop, and Hermione, you go there instead of that castle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going to be a knight,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The chessmen seemed to have been listening, because at these words a knight, a bishop and a castle turned their backs on the white pieces and walked off the board leaving three empty squares which Harry, Ron and Hermione took. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘White always plays first in chess,’ said Ron, peering across the board. ‘Yes … look …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A white pawn had moved forward two squares. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron started to direct the black pieces. They moved silently wherever he sent them. Harry’s knees were trembling. What if they lost? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry – move diagonally four squares to the right.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Their first real shock came when their other knight was taken. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The white queen smashed him to the floor and dragged him off the board, where he lay quite still, face down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Had to let that happen,’ said Ron, looking shaken. ‘Leaves you free to take that bishop, Hermione, go on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Every time one of their men was lost, the white pieces showed no mercy. Soon there was a huddle of limp black players slumped along the wall. Twice, Ron only just noticed in time that Harry and Hermione were in danger. He himself darted around the board taking almost as many white pieces as they had lost black ones. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re nearly there,’ he muttered suddenly. ‘Let me think – let me think …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The white queen turned her blank face towards him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes …’ said Ron softly, ‘it’s the only way … I’ve got to be taken.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘NO!’ Harry and Hermione shouted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s chess!’ snapped Ron. ‘You’ve got to make some sacrifices! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I’ll make my move and she’ll take me – that leaves you free to checkmate the king, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you want to stop Snape or not?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look, if you don’t hurry up, he’ll already have the Stone!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was nothing else for it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready?’ Ron called, his face pale but determined. ‘Here I go – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">now, don’t hang around once you’ve won.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>206 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stepped forward and the white queen pounced. She struck Ron hard around the head with her stone arm and he crashed to the floor – Hermione screamed but stayed on her square – the white queen dragged Ron to one side. He looked as if he’d been knocked out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Shaking, Harry moved three spaces to the left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The white king took off his crown and threw it at Harry’s feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had won. The chessmen parted and bowed, leaving the door ahead clear. With one last desperate look back at Ron, Harry and Hermione charged through the door and up the next passageway. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What if he’s –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’ll be all right,’ said Harry, trying to convince himself. ‘What do you reckon’s next?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve had Sprout’s, that was the Devil’s Snare – Flitwick must’ve put charms on the keys – McGonagall transfigured the chessmen to make them alive – that leaves Quirrell’s spell, and Snape’s …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had reached another door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right?’ Harry whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pushed it open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A disgusting smell filled their nostrils, making both of them pull their robes up over their noses. Eyes watering, they saw, flat on the floor in front of them, a troll even larger than the one they had tackled, out cold with a bloody lump on its head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m glad we didn’t have to fight that one,’ Harry whispered, as they stepped carefully over one of its massive legs. ‘Come on, I can’t breathe.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled open the next door, both of them hardly daring to look at what came next – but there was nothing very frightening in here, just a table with seven differently shaped bottles standing on it in a line. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Snape’s,’ said Harry. ‘What do we have to do?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They stepped over the threshold and immediately a fire sprang up behind them in the doorway. It wasn’t ordinary fire either; it was purple. At the same instant, black flames shot up in the doorway leading onwards. They were trapped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look!’ Hermione seized a roll of paper lying next to the bottles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked over her shoulder to read it: <i class=\"calibre3\">Danger lies before you, while safety lies behind, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the Trapdoor 207 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Two of us will help you, whichever you would find,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">One among us seven will let you move ahead,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Another will transport the drinker back instead,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Two among our number hold only nettle wine,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Three of us are killers, waiting hidden in line. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">Choose, unless you wish to stay here for evermore,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">To help you in your choice, we give you these clues four:</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">First, however slyly the poison tries to hide</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">You will always find some on nettle wine’s left side;</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Second, different are those who stand at either end,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">But if you would move onwards, neither is your friend;</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Third, as you see clearly, all are different size,</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Neither dwarf nor giant holds death in their insides;</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Fourth, the second left and the second on the right</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Are twins once you taste them, though different at first sight. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione let out a great sigh and Harry, amazed, saw that she was smiling, the very last thing he felt like doing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Brilliant, </i>’ said Hermione. ‘This isn’t magic – it’s logic – a puzzle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A lot of the greatest wizards haven’t got an ounce of logic, they’d be stuck in here for ever.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But so will we, won’t we?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course not,’ said Hermione. ‘Everything we need is here on this paper. Seven bottles: three are poison; two are wine; one will get us safely through the black fire and one will get us back through the purple.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But how do we know which to drink?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Give me a minute.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione read the paper several times. Then she walked up and down the line of bottles, muttering to herself and pointing at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last, she clapped her hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Got it,’ she said. ‘The smallest bottle will get us through the black fire – towards the Stone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked at the tiny bottle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s only enough there for one of us,’ he said. ‘That’s hardly one swallow.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They looked at each other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Which one will get you back through the purple flames?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione pointed at a rounded bottle at the right end of the line. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You drink that,’ said Harry. ‘No, listen – get back and get Ron – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>208 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">grab brooms from the flying-key room, they’ll get you out of the trapdoor and past Fluffy – go straight to the owlery and send Hedwig  to  Dumbledore,  we  need  him.  I  might  be  able  to  hold Snape off for a while, but I’m no match for him really.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Harry – what if You-Know-Who’s with him?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – I was lucky once, wasn’t I?’ said Harry, pointing at his scar. ‘I might get lucky again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s lip trembled and she suddenly dashed at Harry and threw her arms around him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Hermione! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry – you’re a great wizard, you know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not as good as you,’ said Harry, very embarrassed, as she let go of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Me!’ said Hermione. ‘Books! And cleverness! There are more important things – friendship and bravery and – oh Harry – be <i class=\"calibre3\">careful! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You drink first,’ said Harry. ‘You are sure which is which, aren’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Positive,’ said Hermione. She took a long drink from the round bottle at the end and shuddered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not poison?’ said Harry anxiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No – but it’s like ice.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quick, go, before it wears off.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good luck – take care –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘GO!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione turned and walked straight through the purple fire. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took a deep breath and picked up the smallest bottle. He turned to face the black flames. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here I come,’ he said and he drained the little bottle in one gulp. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was indeed as though ice was flooding his body. He put the bottle down and walked forward; he braced himself, saw the black flames licking his body but couldn’t feel them – for a moment he could see nothing but dark fire – then he was on the other side, in the last chamber. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was already someone there – but it wasn’t Snape. It wasn’t even Voldemort. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre4\">— CHAPTER SEVENTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre3\">The Man with Two Faces </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Quirrell. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">You! </i>’ gasped Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell smiled. His face wasn’t twitching at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Me,’ he said calmly. ‘I wondered whether I’d be meeting you here, Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I thought – Snape –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Severus?’ Quirrell laughed and it wasn’t his usual quivering treble, either, but cold and sharp. ‘Yes, Severus does seem the type, doesn’t he? So useful to have him swooping around like an overgrown bat. Next to him, who would suspect p-p-poor st-stuttering P-Professor Quirrell?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t take it in. This couldn’t be true, it couldn’t. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Snape tried to kill me!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, no, no.  <i class=\"calibre3\">I </i> tried to kill you. Your friend Miss Granger accidentally knocked me over as she rushed to set fire to Snape at that Quidditch match. She broke my eye contact with you. Another few seconds and I’d have got you off that broom. I’d have managed it before then if Snape hadn’t been muttering a counter-curse, trying to save you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Snape was trying to  <i class=\"calibre3\">save</i> me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course,’ said Quirrell coolly. ‘Why do you think he wanted to referee your next match? He was trying to make sure I didn’t do it again. Funny, really … he needn’t have bothered. I couldn’t do anything with Dumbledore watching. All the other teachers thought Snape was trying to stop Gryffindor winning, he  <i class=\"calibre3\">did</i> make himself unpopular … and what a waste of time, when after all that, I’m going to kill you tonight.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell snapped his fingers. Ropes sprang out of thin air and wrapped themselves tightly around Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re too nosy to live, Potter. Scurrying around the school at </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>210 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hallowe’en like that, for all I knew you’d seen me coming to look at what was guarding the Stone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">You</i> let the troll in?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Certainly. I have a special gift with trolls – you must have seen what I did to the one in the chamber back there? Unfortunately, while everyone else was running around looking for it, Snape, who already suspected me, went straight to the third floor to head me off – and not only did my troll fail to beat you to death, that three-headed dog didn’t even manage to bite Snape’s leg off properly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, wait quietly, Potter. I need to examine this interesting mirror.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was only then that Harry realised what was standing behind Quirrell. It was the Mirror of Erised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This mirror is the key to finding the Stone,’ Quirrell murmured, tapping his way around the frame. ‘Trust Dumbledore to come up with something like this … but he’s in London … I’ll be far away by the time he gets back …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All Harry could think of doing was to keep Quirrell talking and stop him concentrating on the Mirror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I saw you and Snape in the Forest –’ he blurted out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Quirrell idly, walking around the Mirror to look at the back. ‘He was on to me by that time, trying to find out how far I’d got. He suspected me all along. Tried to frighten me – as though he could, when I had Lord Voldemort on my side …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell came back out from behind the Mirror and stared hungrily into it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see the Stone … I’m presenting it to my master … but where is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry struggled against the ropes binding him, but they didn’t give. He  <i class=\"calibre3\">had</i> to keep Quirrell from giving his whole attention to the Mirror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Snape always seemed to hate me so much.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, he does,’ said Quirrell casually, ‘heavens, yes. He was at Hogwarts with your father, didn’t you know? They loathed each other. But he never wanted you  <i class=\"calibre3\">dead. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I heard you a few days ago, sobbing – I thought Snape was threatening you …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For the first time, a spasm of fear flitted across Quirrell’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sometimes,’  he  said,  ‘I  find  it  hard  to  follow  my  master’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Man with Two Faces 211 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">instructions – he is a great wizard and I am weak –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You mean he was there in the classroom with you?’ Harry gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He is with me wherever I go,’ said Quirrell quietly. ‘I met him when I travelled around the world. A foolish young man I was then, full of ridiculous ideas about good and evil. Lord Voldemort showed me how wrong I was. There is no good and evil, there is only power, and those too weak to seek it … Since then, I have served him faithfully, although I have let him down many times. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He has had to be very hard on me.’ Quirrell shivered suddenly. ‘He does not forgive mistakes easily. When I failed to steal the Stone from Gringotts, he was most displeased. He punished me … decided he would have to keep a closer watch on me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell’s voice tailed away. Harry was remembering his trip to Diagon Alley – how could he have been so stupid? He’d  <i class=\"calibre3\">seen</i> Quirrell there that very day, shaken hands with him in the Leaky Cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell cursed under his breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t understand … is the Stone  <i class=\"calibre3\">inside</i> the Mirror? Should I break it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s mind was racing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What I want more than anything else in the world at the moment, he thought, is to find the Stone before Quirrell does. So if I look in the Mirror, I should see myself finding it – which means I’ll see where it’s hidden! But how can I look without Quirrell realising what I’m up to? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He tried to edge to the left, to get in front of the glass without Quirrell noticing, but the ropes around his ankles were too tight: he tripped and fell over. Quirrell ignored him. He was still talking to himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What does this mirror do? How does it work? Help me, Master!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And to Harry’s horror, a voice answered, and the voice seemed to come from Quirrell himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Use the boy … Use the boy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell rounded on Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes – Potter – come here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He clapped his hands once and the ropes binding Harry fell off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry got slowly to his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come here,’ Quirrell repeated. ‘Look in the Mirror and tell me </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>212 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">what you see.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry walked towards him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I  must  lie,’  he  thought  desperately.  ‘I  must  look  and  lie  about what I see, that’s all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell moved close behind him. Harry breathed in the funny smell that seemed to come from Quirrell’s turban. He closed his eyes, stepped in front of the Mirror and opened them again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He saw his reflection, pale and scared-looking at first. But a moment later, the reflection smiled at him. It put its hand into its pocket and pulled out a blood-red stone. It winked and put the Stone back in its pocket – and as it did so, Harry felt something heavy drop into his real pocket. Somehow – incredibly –  <i class=\"calibre3\">he’d got</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">the Stone. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well?’ said Quirrell impatiently. ‘What do you see?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry screwed up his courage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see myself shaking hands with Dumbledore,’ he invented. ‘I – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I’ve won the House Cup for Gryffindor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell cursed again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out of the way,’ he said. As Harry moved aside he felt the Philosopher’s Stone against his leg. Dare he make a break for it? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he hadn’t walked five paces before a high voice spoke, though Quirrell wasn’t moving his lips. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He lies … He lies …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter, come back here!’ Quirrell shouted. ‘Tell me the truth! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What did you just see?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The high voice spoke again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let me speak to him … face to face …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Master, you are not strong enough!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have strength enough … for this …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt as if Devil’s Snare was rooting him to the spot. He couldn’t move a muscle. Petrified, he watched as Quirrell reached up and began to unwrap his turban. What was going on? The turban fell away. Quirrell’s head looked strangely small without it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he turned slowly on the spot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry would have screamed, but he couldn’t make a sound. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Where there should have been a back to Quirrell’s head, there was a face, the most terrible face Harry had ever seen. It was chalk white with glaring red eyes and slits for nostrils, like a snake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter …’ it whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to take a step backwards but his legs wouldn’t move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Man with Two Faces 213 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See what I have become?’ the face said. ‘Mere shadow and vapour … I have form only when I can share another’s body … but there have always been those willing to let me into their hearts and minds … Unicorn blood has strengthened me, these past weeks … you saw faithful Quirrell drinking it for me in the Forest </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… and once I have the Elixir of Life, I will be able to create a body of my own … Now … why don’t you give me that Stone in your pocket?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So he knew. The feeling suddenly surged back into Harry’s legs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stumbled backwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be a fool,’ snarled the face. ‘Better save your own life and join me … or you’ll meet the same end as your parents … They died begging me for mercy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘LIAR!’ Harry shouted suddenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell was walking backwards at him, so that Voldemort could still see him. The evil face was now smiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How touching …’ it hissed. ‘I always value bravery … Yes, boy, your parents were brave … I killed your father first and he put up a courageous fight … but your mother needn’t have died … she was trying to protect you … Now give me the Stone, unless you want her to have died in vain.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘NEVER!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sprang towards the flame door, but Voldemort screamed, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘SEIZE HIM!’ and, next second, Harry felt Quirrell’s hand close on his wrist. At once, a needle-sharp pain seared across Harry’s scar; his  head  felt  as  though  it  was  about  to  split  in  two;  he  yelled, struggling with all his might, and to his surprise, Quirrell let go of him. The pain in his head lessened – he looked around wildly to see where Quirrell had gone and saw him hunched in pain, looking at his fingers – they were blistering before his eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Seize him! SEIZE HIM!’ shrieked Voldemort again and Quirrell lunged, knocking Harry clean off his feet, landing on top of him, both hands around Harry’s neck – Harry’s scar was almost blinding him with pain, yet he could see Quirrell howling in agony. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Master, I cannot hold him – my hands – my hands!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Quirrell, though pinning Harry to the ground with his knees, let go of his neck and stared, bewildered, at his own palms </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– Harry could see they looked burnt, raw, red and shiny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then kill him, fool, and be done!’ screeched Voldemort. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell raised his hand to perform a deadly curse, but Harry, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>214 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">by instinct, reached up and grabbed Quirrell’s face – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘AAAARGH!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quirrell rolled off him, his face blistering too, and then Harry knew: Quirrell couldn’t touch his bare skin, not without suffering terrible pain – his only chance was to keep hold of Quirrell, keep him in enough pain to stop him doing a curse. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jumped to his feet, caught Quirrell by the arm and hung on as tight as he could. Quirrell screamed and tried to throw Harry off – the pain in Harry’s head was building – he couldn’t see </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– he could only hear Quirrell’s terrible shrieks and Voldemort’s yells of ‘KILL HIM! KILL HIM!’ and other voices, maybe in Harry’s own head, crying, ‘Harry! Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He felt Quirrell’s arm wrenched from his grasp, knew all was lost, and fell into blackness, down … down … down … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something gold was glinting just above him. The Snitch! He tried to catch it, but his arms were too heavy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He blinked. It wasn’t the Snitch at all. It was a pair of glasses. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">How strange. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He blinked again. The smiling face of Albus Dumbledore swam into view above him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good afternoon, Harry,’ said Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared at him. Then he remembered. ‘Sir! The Stone! It was Quirrell! He’s got the Stone! Sir, quick –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Calm yourself, dear boy, you are a little behind the times,’ said Dumbledore. ‘Quirrell does not have the Stone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then who does? Sir, I –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, please relax, or Madam Pomfrey will have me thrown out.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry swallowed and looked around him. He realised he must be in the hospital wing. He was lying in a bed with white linen sheets and next to him was a table piled high with what looked like half the sweet-shop. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tokens from your friends and admirers,’ said Dumbledore, beaming. ‘What happened down in the dungeons between you and Professor Quirrell is a complete secret, so, naturally, the whole school knows. I believe your friends Misters Fred and George Weasley were responsible for trying to send you a lavatory seat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No doubt they thought it would amuse you. Madam Pomfrey, however, felt it might not be very hygienic, and confiscated it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Man with Two Faces 215 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How long have I been in here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Three days. Mr Ronald Weasley and Miss Granger will be most relieved you have come round, they have been extremely worried.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But sir, the Stone –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see you are not to be distracted. Very well, the Stone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Quirrell did not manage to take it from you. I arrived in time to prevent that, although you were doing very well on your own, I must say.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You got there? You got Hermione’s owl?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We must have crossed in mid-air. No sooner had I reached London than it became clear to me that the place I should be was the one I had just left. I arrived just in time to pull Quirrell off you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was  <i class=\"calibre3\">you. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I feared I might be too late.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You nearly were, I couldn’t have kept him off the Stone much longer –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not the Stone, boy, you – the effort involved nearly killed you. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For one terrible moment there, I was afraid it had. As for the Stone, it has been destroyed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Destroyed?’ said Harry blankly. ‘But your friend – Nicolas Flamel –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, you know about Nicolas?’ said Dumbledore, sounding quite delighted. ‘You  <i class=\"calibre3\">did</i> do the thing properly, didn’t you? Well, Nicolas and I have had a little chat and agreed it’s all for the best.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But that means he and his wife will die, won’t they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They have enough Elixir stored to set their affairs in order and then, yes, they will die.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore smiled at the look of amazement on Harry’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘To one as young as you, I’m sure it seems incredible, but to Nicolas and Perenelle, it really is like going to bed after a very, <i class=\"calibre3\">very</i> long day. After all, to the well-organised mind, death is but the next great adventure. You know, the Stone was really not such a wonderful thing. As much money and life as you could want! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The two things most human beings would choose above all – the trouble is, humans do have a knack of choosing precisely those things which are worst for them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry lay there, lost for words. Dumbledore hummed a little and smiled at the ceiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sir?’ said Harry. ‘I’ve been thinking … Sir – even if the Stone’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>216 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">gone, Vol– … I mean, You-Know-Who –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Call him Voldemort, Harry. Always use the proper name for things. Fear of a name increases fear of the thing itself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, sir. Well, Voldemort’s going to try other ways of coming back, isn’t he? I mean, he hasn’t gone, has he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, Harry, he has not. He is still out there somewhere, perhaps looking for another body to share … not being truly alive, he cannot be killed. He left Quirrell to die; he shows just as little mercy to his followers as his enemies. Nevertheless, Harry, while you may only have delayed his return to power, it will merely take someone else who is prepared to fight what seems a losing battle next time – and if he is delayed again, and again, why, he may never return to power.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry nodded, but stopped quickly, because it made his head hurt. Then he said, ‘Sir, there are some other things I’d like to know, if you can tell me … things I want to know the truth about …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The truth.’ Dumbledore sighed. ‘It is a beautiful and terrible thing, and should therefore be treated with great caution. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">However, I shall answer your questions unless I have a very good reason not to, in which case I beg you’ll forgive me. I shall not, of course, lie.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well … Voldemort said that he only killed my mother because she tried to stop him killing me. But why would he want to kill me in the first place?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore sighed very deeply this time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Alas, the first thing you ask me, I cannot tell you. Not today. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Not now. You will know, one day … put it from your mind for now, Harry. When you are older … I know you hate to hear this … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">when you are ready, you will know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Harry knew it would be no good to argue. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But why couldn’t Quirrell touch me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your mother died to save you. If there is one thing Voldemort cannot understand, it is love. He didn’t realise that love as powerful as your mother’s for you leaves its own mark. Not a scar, no visible sign … to have been loved so deeply, even though the person who loved us is gone, will give us some protection for ever. It is in your very skin. Quirrell, full of hatred, greed and ambition, sharing his soul with Voldemort, could not touch you for this reason. It was agony to touch a person marked by something so good.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Man with Two Faces 217 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore now became very interested in a bird out on the window-sill, which gave Harry time to dry his eyes on the sheet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When he had found his voice again, Harry said, ‘And the Invisibility Cloak – do you know who sent it to me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah – your father happened to leave it in my possession and I thought you might like it.’ Dumbledore’s eyes twinkled. ‘Useful things … your father used it mainly for sneaking off to the kitchens to steal food when he was here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And there’s something else …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fire away.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quirrell said Snape –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Professor</i> Snape, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, him – Quirrell said he hates me because he hated my father. Is that true?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, they did rather detest each other. Not unlike yourself and Mr Malfoy. And then, your father did something Snape could never forgive.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He saved his life.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">What? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes …’ said Dumbledore dreamily. ‘Funny, the way people’s minds work, isn’t it? Professor Snape couldn’t bear being in your father’s debt … I do believe he worked so hard to protect you this year because he felt that would make him and your father quits. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he could go back to hating your father’s memory in peace …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to understand this but it made his head pound, so he stopped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And sir, there’s one more thing …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just the one?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did I get the Stone out of the Mirror?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, now, I’m glad you asked me that. It was one of my more brilliant ideas, and between you and me, that’s saying something. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You see, only one who wanted to  <i class=\"calibre3\">find</i> the Stone – find it, but not use it – would be able to get it, otherwise they’d just see themselves making gold or drinking Elixir of Life. My brain surprises even me sometimes … Now, enough questions. I suggest you make a start on these sweets. Ah! Bertie Bott’s Every-Flavour Beans! I was unfortunate enough in my youth to come across a vomit-flavoured one, and since then I’m afraid I’ve rather lost my liking for them – but I think I’ll be safe with a nice toffee, don’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>218 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He smiled and popped the golden-brown bean into his mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he choked and said, ‘Alas! Earwax!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey, the matron, was a nice woman, but very strict. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just five minutes,’ Harry pleaded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Absolutely not.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You let Professor Dumbledore in …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, of course, that was the Headmaster, quite different. You need  <i class=\"calibre3\">rest</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I am resting, look, lying down and everything. Oh, go on, Madam Pomfrey …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, very well,’ she said. ‘But five minutes  <i class=\"calibre3\">only. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And she let Ron and Hermione in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Harry! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione looked ready to fling her arms around him again, but Harry was glad she held herself in as his head was still very sore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, Harry, we were sure you were going to – Dumbledore was so worried –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The whole school’s talking about it,’ said Ron. ‘What  <i class=\"calibre3\">really</i> happened?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was one of those rare occasions when the true story is even more strange and exciting than the wild rumours. Harry told them everything: Quirrell; the Mirror; the Stone and Voldemort. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione were a very good audience; they gasped in all the right places and, when Harry told them what was under Quirrell’s turban, Hermione screamed out loud. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So the Stone’s gone?’ said Ron finally. ‘Flamel’s just going to <i class=\"calibre3\">die? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s what I said, but Dumbledore thinks that – what was it? – “to the well-organised mind, death is but the next great adventure”.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I always said he was off his rocker,’ said Ron, looking quite impressed at how mad his hero was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So what happened to you two?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I got back all right,’ said Hermione. ‘I brought Ron round </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– that took a while – and we were dashing up to the owlery to contact Dumbledore when we met him in the Entrance Hall. He already knew – he just said, “Harry’s gone after him, hasn’t he?” </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and hurtled off to the third floor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you think he meant you to do it?’ said Ron. ‘Sending you </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Man with Two Faces 219 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">your father’s Cloak and everything?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">Well</i>,’ Hermione exploded, ‘if he did – I mean to say – that’s terrible – you could have been killed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, it isn’t,’ said Harry thoughtfully. ‘He’s a funny man, Dumbledore. I think he sort of wanted to give me a chance. I think he knows more or less everything that goes on here, you know.  I  reckon  he  had  a  pretty  good  idea  we  were  going  to  try, and instead of stopping us, he just taught us enough to help. I don’t think it was an accident he let me find out how the Mirror worked. It’s almost like he thought I had the right to face Voldemort if I could …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, Dumbledore’s barking, all right,’ said Ron proudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Listen, you’ve got to be up for the end-of-year feast tomorrow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The points are all in and Slytherin won, of course – you missed the last Quidditch match, we were steamrollered by Ravenclaw without you – but the food’ll be good.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment, Madam Pomfrey bustled over. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve had nearly fifteen minutes, now OUT,’ she said firmly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After a good night’s sleep, Harry felt nearly back to normal. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I want to go to the feast,’ he told Madam Pomfrey as she straightened his many sweet-boxes. ‘I can, can’t I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore says you are to be allowed to go,’ she said sniffily, as though in her opinion Professor Dumbledore didn’t realise how risky feasts could be. ‘And you have another visitor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh good,’ said Harry. ‘Who is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid sidled through the door as he spoke. As usual when he was indoors, Hagrid looked too big to be allowed. He sat down next to Harry, took one look at him and burst into tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s – all – my – ruddy – fault!’ he sobbed, his face in his hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I told the evil git how ter get past Fluffy! I told him! It was the only thing he didn’t know an’ I told him! Yeh could’ve died! All fer a dragon egg! I’ll never drink again! I should be chucked out an’ made ter live as a Muggle!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid!’ said Harry, shocked to see Hagrid shaking with grief and remorse, great tears leaking down into his beard. ‘Hagrid, he’d have found out somehow, this is Voldemort we’re talking about, he’d have found out even if you hadn’t told him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh could’ve died!’ sobbed Hagrid. ‘An’ don’ say the name!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘VOLDEMORT!’ Harry bellowed, and Hagrid was so shocked, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>220 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he stopped crying. ‘I’ve met him and I’m calling him by his name. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Please cheer up, Hagrid, we saved the Stone, it’s gone, he can’t use it. Have a Chocolate Frog, I’ve got loads …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid wiped his nose on the back of his hand and said, ‘That reminds me. I’ve got yeh a present.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not a stoat sandwich, is it?’ said Harry anxiously and at last Hagrid gave a weak chuckle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nah. Dumbledore gave me the day off yesterday ter fix it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">’Course, he shoulda sacked me instead – anyway, got yeh this …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It seemed to be a handsome, leather-covered book. Harry opened it curiously. It was full of wizard photographs. Smiling and waving at him from every page were his mother and father. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sent owls off ter all yer parents’ old school friends, askin’ fer photos … Knew yeh didn’ have any … D’yeh like it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t speak, but Hagrid understood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry made his way down to the end-of-year feast alone that night. He had been held up by Madam Pomfrey’s fussing-about, insisting on giving him one last check-up, so the Great Hall was already full. It was decked out in the Slytherin colours of green and silver to celebrate Slytherin’s winning the House Cup for the seventh year in a row. A huge banner showing the Slytherin serpent covered the wall behind the High Table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Harry walked in there was a sudden hush and then everybody started talking loudly at once. He slipped into a seat between Ron and Hermione at the Gryffindor table and tried to ignore the fact that people were standing up to look at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fortunately, Dumbledore arrived moments later. The babble died away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Another year gone!’ Dumbledore said cheerfully. ‘And I must trouble you with an old man’s wheezing waffle before we sink our teeth into our delicious feast. What a year it has been! Hopefully your heads are all a little fuller than they were … you have the whole summer ahead to get them nice and empty before next year starts … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, as I understand it, the House Cup here needs awarding and the points stand thus: in fourth place, Gryffindor, with three hundred and twelve points; in third, Hufflepuff, with three hundred and fifty-two; Ravenclaw have four hundred and twenty-six and Slytherin, four hundred and seventy-two.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Man with Two Faces 221 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A storm of cheering and stamping broke out from the Slytherin table. Harry could see Draco Malfoy banging his goblet on the table. It was a sickening sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, yes, well done, Slytherin,’ said Dumbledore. ‘However, recent events must be taken into account.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The room went very still. The Slytherins’ smiles faded a little. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ahem,’ said Dumbledore. ‘I have a few last-minute points to dish out. Let me see. Yes … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘First – to Mr Ronald Weasley …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron went purple in the face; he looked like a radish with bad sunburn. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… for the best-played game of chess Hogwarts has seen in many years, I award Gryffindor house fifty points.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor cheers nearly raised the bewitched ceiling; the stars overhead seemed to quiver. Percy could be heard telling the other Prefects, ‘My brother, you know! My youngest brother! Got past McGonagall’s giant chess set!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last there was silence again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Second – to Miss Hermione Granger … for the use of cool logic in the face of fire, I award Gryffindor house fifty points.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione buried her face in her arms; Harry strongly suspected she had burst into tears. Gryffindors up and down the table were beside themselves – they were a hundred points up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Third – to Mr Harry Potter …’ said Dumbledore. The room went deadly quiet. ‘… for pure nerve and outstanding courage, I award Gryffindor house sixty points.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The din was deafening. Those who could add up while yelling themselves hoarse knew that Gryffindor now had four hundred and seventy-two points – exactly the same as Slytherin. They had drawn for the House Cup – if only Dumbledore had given Harry just one more point. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore raised his hand. The room gradually fell silent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There are all kinds of courage,’ said Dumbledore, smiling. ‘It takes a great deal of bravery to stand up to our enemies, but just as much to stand up to our friends. I therefore award ten points to Mr Neville Longbottom.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000003999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Someone standing outside the Great Hall might well have thought some sort of explosion had taken place, so loud was the noise that erupted from the Gryffindor table. Harry, Ron and Hermione stood up to yell and cheer as Neville, white with shock, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>222 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">disappeared under a pile of people hugging him. He had never won so much as a point for Gryffindor before. Harry, still cheering, nudged Ron in the ribs and pointed at Malfoy, who couldn’t have looked more stunned and horrified if he’d just had the Body-Bind curse put on him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Which means,’ Dumbledore called over the storm of applause, for even Ravenclaw and Hufflepuff were celebrating the downfall of Slytherin, ‘we need a little change of decoration.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He clapped his hands. In an instant, the green hangings became scarlet and the silver became gold; the huge Slytherin serpent vanished and a towering Gryffindor lion took its place. Snape was shaking Professor McGonagall’s hand, with a horrible forced smile. He caught Harry’s eye and Harry knew at once that Snape’s feelings towards him hadn’t changed one jot. This didn’t worry Harry. It seemed as though life would be back to normal next year, or as normal as it ever was at Hogwarts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was the best evening of Harry’s life, better than winning at Quidditch or Christmas or knocking out mountain trolls … he would never, ever forget tonight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had almost forgotten that the exam results were still to come, but come they did. To their great surprise, both he and Ron passed with good marks; Hermione, of course, came top of the year. Even Neville scraped through, his good Herbology mark making up for his abysmal Potions one. They had hoped that Goyle, who was almost as stupid as he was mean, might be thrown out, but he had passed, too. It was a shame, but as Ron said, you couldn’t have everything in life. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And suddenly, their wardrobes were empty, their trunks were packed, Neville’s toad was found lurking in a corner of the toilets; notes were handed out to all students, warning them not to use magic over the holidays (‘I always hope they’ll forget to give us these,’ said Fred Weasley sadly); Hagrid was there to take them down to the fleet of boats that sailed across the lake; they were boarding the Hogwarts Express; talking and laughing as the countryside became greener and tidier; eating Bertie Bott’s Every-Flavour Beans as they sped past Muggle towns; pulling off their wizard robes and putting on jackets and coats; pulling into platform nine and three-quarters at King’s Cross Station. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took quite a while for them all to get off the platform. A </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Man with Two Faces 223 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">wizened old guard was up by the ticket barrier, letting them go through the gate in twos and threes so they didn’t attract attention by all bursting out of a solid wall at once and alarming the Muggles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You must come and stay this summer,’ said Ron, ‘both of you – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I’ll send you an owl.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thanks,’ said Harry. ‘I’ll need something to look forward to.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">People jostled them as they moved forwards towards the gateway back to the Muggle world. Some of them called: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bye, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See you, Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Still famous,’ said Ron, grinning at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not where I’m going, I promise you,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He, Ron and Hermione passed through the gateway together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There he is, Mum, there he is, look!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Ginny Weasley, Ron’s younger sister, but she wasn’t pointing at Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter!’ she squealed. ‘Look, Mum! I can see –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Be quiet, Ginny, and it’s rude to point.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley smiled down at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Busy year?’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very,’ said Harry. ‘Thanks for the fudge and the jumper, Mrs Weasley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, it was nothing, dear.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready, are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Uncle Vernon, still purple-faced, still moustached, still looking furious at the nerve of Harry, carrying an owl in a cage in a station full of ordinary people. Behind him stood Aunt Petunia and Dudley, looking terrified at the very sight of Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You must be Harry’s family!’ said Mrs Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In a manner of speaking,’ said Uncle Vernon. ‘Hurry up, boy, we haven’t got all day.’ He walked away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hung back for a last word with Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See you over the summer, then.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hope you have – er – a good holiday,’ said Hermione, looking uncertainly after Uncle Vernon, shocked that anyone could be so unpleasant. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, I will,’ said Harry, and they were surprised at the grin that was spreading over his face. ‘ <i class=\"calibre3\">They </i> don’t know we’re not allowed to use magic at home. I’m going to have a lot of fun with Dudley this summer …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>\n<a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">J. K. (JOANNE KATHLEEN) ROWLING  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">has written fiction since she was a child. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Born in 1965, she grew up in Chepstow and wrote her first ‘book’ at the age of six  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">- a story about a rabbit called Rabbit. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She studied French and Classics at Exeter University, then moved to London to  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">work at Amnesty International, and then to Portugal to teach English as a foreign language, before settling in Edinburgh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The idea for Harry Potter occurred to her on the train from Manchester to London, where she says Harry Potter ‘just strolled into my head fully formed’, and by the time she had arrived at King’s Cross, many of the characters had taken shape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">During the next five years she outlined the plots for each book and began writing the first in the series,  <i class=\"calibre3\">Harry Potter and</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">the Philosopher’s Stone, </i> which was first published by Bloomsbury in 1997. The  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">other Harry Potter titles:  <i class=\"calibre3\">Harry Potter and</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">the Chamber of Secrets, Harry Potter and the</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Prisoner of Azkaban, Harry Potter and the</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Goblet of Fire, </i> and  <i class=\"calibre3\">Harry Potter and the</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Order of the Phoenix, </i> followed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">J. K. Rowling has also written three other companion books,  <i class=\"calibre3\">Quidditch Through the</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Ages, </i>  <i class=\"calibre3\">Fantastic Beasts and Where to</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Find Them</i> and <i class=\"calibre3\"> The Tales of Beedle the</i> <i class=\"calibre3\">Bard, </i> in aid of Comic Relief. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Jacket Design: William Webb </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2175134d90427c9a-5452b8 twpub-2175134d90427c9a-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Jacket Image: Michael Wildsmith </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/2175134d90427c9a/text/000004051",
